39 
40 CEulerSolver::CEulerSolver(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config,
41  unsigned short iMesh, const bool navier_stokes) :
42  CFVMFlowSolverBase<CEulerVariable, ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE>(*geometry, *config) {
43 
44  /*--- Based on the navier_stokes boolean, determine if this constructor is
45  * being called by itself, or by its derived class CNSSolver. ---*/
46  string description;
47  unsigned short nSecVar;
48  if (navier_stokes) {
49  description = "Navier-Stokes";
50  nSecVar = 8;
51  }
52  else {
53  description = "Euler";
54  nSecVar = 2;
55  }
56 
57  const auto nZone = geometry->GetnZone();
58  const bool restart = (config->GetRestart() || config->GetRestart_Flow());
59  const bool rans = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
60  const auto direct_diff = config->GetDirectDiff();
61  const bool dual_time = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST) ||
62  (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND);
63  const bool time_stepping = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::TIME_STEPPING);
64  const bool adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint() || config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
65 
66  int Unst_RestartIter = 0;
67  unsigned long iPoint, iMarker, counter_local = 0, counter_global = 0;
68  unsigned short iDim;
69  su2double StaticEnergy, Density, Velocity2, Pressure, Temperature;
70 
71  /*--- A grid is defined as dynamic if there's rigid grid movement or grid deformation AND the problem is time domain ---*/
72  dynamic_grid = config->GetDynamic_Grid();
73 
74  /*--- Store the multigrid level. ---*/
75  MGLevel = iMesh;
76 
77  /*--- Check for a restart file to evaluate if there is a change in the angle of attack
78  before computing all the non-dimesional quantities. ---*/
79 
80  if (!(!restart || (iMesh != MESH_0) || nZone > 1) && config->GetFixed_CL_Mode()) {
81 
82  /*--- Modify file name for a dual-time unsteady restart ---*/
83 
84  if (dual_time) {
85  if (adjoint) Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_AdjointIter())-1;
86  else if (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST)
87  Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetRestart_Iter())-1;
88  else Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetRestart_Iter())-2;
89  }
90 
91  /*--- Modify file name for a time stepping unsteady restart ---*/
92 
93  if (time_stepping) {
94  if (adjoint) Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetUnst_AdjointIter())-1;
95  else Unst_RestartIter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetRestart_Iter())-1;
96  }
97 
98  /*--- Read and store the restart metadata. ---*/
99 
100  string filename_ = "flow";
101  filename_ = config->GetFilename(filename_, ".meta", Unst_RestartIter);
102  Read_SU2_Restart_Metadata(geometry, config, adjoint, filename_);
103 
104  }
105 
106  /*--- Set the gamma value ---*/
107 
108  Gamma = config->GetGamma();
109  Gamma_Minus_One = Gamma - 1.0;
110 
111  /*--- Define geometry constants in the solver structure
112  Compressible flow, primitive variables (T, vx, vy, vz, P, rho, h, c, lamMu, EddyMu, ThCond, Cp).
113  ---*/
114 
115  nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
116 
117  nVar = nDim+2;
118  nPrimVar = nDim+9; nPrimVarGrad = nDim+4;
119  nSecondaryVar = nSecVar; nSecondaryVarGrad = 2;
120 
121  /*--- Initialize nVarGrad for deallocation ---*/
122 
123  nVarGrad = nPrimVarGrad;
124 
125  nMarker = config->GetnMarker_All();
126  nPoint = geometry->GetnPoint();
127  nPointDomain = geometry->GetnPointDomain();
128 
129  /*--- Store the number of vertices on each marker for deallocation later ---*/
130 
131  nVertex.resize(nMarker);
132  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++)
133  nVertex[iMarker] = geometry->nVertex[iMarker];
134 
135  /*--- Perform the non-dimensionalization for the flow equations using the
136  specified reference values. ---*/
137 
138  SetNondimensionalization(config, iMesh);
139 
140  /*--- Check if we are executing a verification case. If so, the
141  VerificationSolution object will be instantiated for a particular
142  option from the available library of verification solutions. Note
143  that this is done after SetNondim(), as problem-specific initial
144  parameters are needed by the solution constructors. ---*/
145 
146  SetVerificationSolution(nDim, nVar, config);
147 
148  /*--- Allocate base class members. ---*/
149 
150  Allocate(*config);
151 
152  /*--- MPI + OpenMP initialization. ---*/
153 
154  HybridParallelInitialization(*config, *geometry);
155 
156  /*--- Jacobians and vector structures for implicit computations ---*/
157 
158  if (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme_Flow() == EULER_IMPLICIT) {
159 
160  if (rank == MASTER_NODE)
161  cout << "Initialize Jacobian structure (" << description << "). MG level: " << iMesh <<"." << endl;
162 
163  Jacobian.Initialize(nPoint, nPointDomain, nVar, nVar, true, geometry, config, ReducerStrategy);
164  }
165  else {
166  if (rank == MASTER_NODE)
167  cout << "Explicit scheme. No Jacobian structure (" << description << "). MG level: " << iMesh <<"." << endl;
168  }
169 
170  /*--- Store the value of the primitive variables + 2 turb variables at the boundaries,
171  used for IO with a donor cell ---*/
172 
173  AllocVectorOfMatrices(nVertex, (rans? nPrimVar+2 : nPrimVar), DonorPrimVar);
174 
175  /*--- Store the value of the characteristic primitive variables index at the boundaries ---*/
176 
177  DonorGlobalIndex.resize(nMarker);
178  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++)
179  DonorGlobalIndex[iMarker].resize(nVertex[iMarker],0);
180 
181  /*--- Actuator Disk Radius allocation ---*/
182  ActDisk_R.resize(nMarker);
183 
184  /*--- Actuator Disk Center allocation ---*/
185  ActDisk_C.resize(nMarker, MAXNDIM);
186 
187  /*--- Actuator Disk Axis allocation ---*/
188  ActDisk_Axis.resize(nMarker, MAXNDIM);
189 
190  /*--- Actuator Disk Fa, Fx, Fy and Fz allocations ---*/
191  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fa);
192  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fx);
193  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fy);
194  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_Fz);
195 
196  /*--- Store the value of the Delta P at the Actuator Disk ---*/
197 
198  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_DeltaP);
199 
200  /*--- Store the value of the Delta T at the Actuator Disk ---*/
201 
202  AllocVectorOfVectors(nVertex, ActDisk_DeltaT);
203 
204  /*--- Supersonic coefficients ---*/
205 
206  CEquivArea_Inv.resize(nMarker);
207 
208  /*--- Engine simulation ---*/
209 
210  Inflow_MassFlow.resize(nMarker);
211  Inflow_Pressure.resize(nMarker);
212  Inflow_Mach.resize(nMarker);
213  Inflow_Area.resize(nMarker);
214 
215  Exhaust_Temperature.resize(nMarker);
216  Exhaust_MassFlow.resize(nMarker);
217  Exhaust_Pressure.resize(nMarker);
218  Exhaust_Area.resize(nMarker);
219 
220  /*--- Read farfield conditions from config ---*/
221 
222  Temperature_Inf = config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND();
223  Velocity_Inf = config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND();
224  Pressure_Inf = config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
225  Density_Inf = config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
226  Energy_Inf = config->GetEnergy_FreeStreamND();
227  Mach_Inf = config->GetMach();
228 
229  /*--- Initialize the secondary values for direct derivative approxiations ---*/
230 
231  switch(direct_diff) {
232  case NO_DERIVATIVE:
233  /*--- Default ---*/
234  break;
235  case D_DENSITY:
236  SU2_TYPE::SetDerivative(Density_Inf, 1.0);
237  break;
238  case D_PRESSURE:
239  SU2_TYPE::SetDerivative(Pressure_Inf, 1.0);
240  break;
241  case D_TEMPERATURE:
242  SU2_TYPE::SetDerivative(Temperature_Inf, 1.0);
243  break;
244  case D_MACH: case D_AOA:
245  case D_SIDESLIP: case D_REYNOLDS:
246  case D_TURB2LAM: case D_DESIGN:
247  /*--- Already done in postprocessing of config ---*/
248  break;
249  default:
250  break;
251  }
252 
253  SetReferenceValues(*config);
254 
255  /*--- Initialize fan face pressure, fan face mach number, and mass flow rate ---*/
256 
257  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
258  Inflow_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
259  Inflow_Mach[iMarker] = Mach_Inf;
260  Inflow_Pressure[iMarker] = Pressure_Inf;
261  Inflow_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
262 
263  Exhaust_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
264  Exhaust_Temperature[iMarker] = Temperature_Inf;
265  Exhaust_Pressure[iMarker] = Pressure_Inf;
266  Exhaust_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
267  }
268 
269  /*--- Initialize the solution to the far-field state everywhere. ---*/
270 
271  if (navier_stokes) {
272  nodes = new CNSVariable(Density_Inf, Velocity_Inf, Energy_Inf, nPoint, nDim, nVar, config);
273  } else {
274  nodes = new CEulerVariable(Density_Inf, Velocity_Inf, Energy_Inf, nPoint, nDim, nVar, config);
275  }
276  SetBaseClassPointerToNodes();
277 
278  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
279  nodes->NonPhysicalEdgeCounter.resize(geometry->GetnEdge()) = 0;
280  }
281 
282  /*--- Check that the initial solution is physical, report any non-physical nodes ---*/
283 
284  counter_local = 0;
285 
286  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
287 
288  Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
289 
290  Velocity2 = 0.0;
291  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
292  Velocity2 += pow(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iDim+1)/Density,2);
293 
294  StaticEnergy= nodes->GetEnergy(iPoint) - 0.5*Velocity2;
295 
296  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density, StaticEnergy);
297  Pressure= GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
298  Temperature= GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
299 
300  /*--- Use the values at the infinity ---*/
301 
302  su2double Solution[MAXNVAR] = {0.0};
303  if ((Pressure < 0.0) || (Density < 0.0) || (Temperature < 0.0)) {
304  Solution[0] = Density_Inf;
305  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
306  Solution[iDim+1] = Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Density_Inf;
307  Solution[nDim+1] = Energy_Inf*Density_Inf;
308  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,Solution);
309  nodes->SetSolution_Old(iPoint,Solution);
310  counter_local++;
311  }
312 
313  }
314 
315  /*--- Warning message about non-physical points ---*/
316 
317  if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
318 
319  SU2_MPI::Reduce(&counter_local, &counter_global, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
320 
321  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (counter_global != 0))
322  cout << "Warning. The original solution contains " << counter_global << " points that are not physical." << endl;
323  }
324 
325  /*--- Initial comms. ---*/
326 
327  CommunicateInitialState(geometry, config);
328 
329  /*--- Add the solver name (max 8 characters). ---*/
330  SolverName = "C.FLOW";
331 
332  /*--- Finally, check that the static arrays will be large enough (keep this
333  * check at the bottom to make sure we consider the "final" values). ---*/
334  if((nDim > MAXNDIM) || (nPrimVar > MAXNVAR) || (nSecondaryVar > MAXNVAR))
335  SU2_MPI::Error("Oops! The CEulerSolver static array sizes are not large enough.",CURRENT_FUNCTION);
336 }
337 
338 CEulerSolver::~CEulerSolver(void) {
339 
340  for(auto& model : FluidModel) delete model;
341 }
342 
343 void CEulerSolver::InstantiateEdgeNumerics(const CSolver* const* solver_container, const CConfig* config) {
344 
345  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
346  {
347 
348  if (config->Low_Mach_Correction())
349  SU2_MPI::Error("Low-Mach correction is not supported with vectorization.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
350 
351  if (solver_container[TURB_SOL])
352  edgeNumerics = CNumericsSIMD::CreateNumerics(*config, nDim, MGLevel, solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes());
353  else
354  edgeNumerics = CNumericsSIMD::CreateNumerics(*config, nDim, MGLevel);
355 
356  if (!edgeNumerics)
357  SU2_MPI::Error("The numerical scheme + gas model in use do not "
358  "support vectorization.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
359 
360  }
361  END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
362 }
363 
364 void CEulerSolver::InitTurboContainers(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config){
365 
366  /*--- Initialize quantities for the average process for internal flow ---*/
367 
368  const auto nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanWiseSections();
369 
370  AverageVelocity.resize(nMarker);
371  AverageTurboVelocity.resize(nMarker);
372  OldAverageTurboVelocity.resize(nMarker);
373  ExtAverageTurboVelocity.resize(nMarker);
374  AverageFlux.resize(nMarker);
375  SpanTotalFlux.resize(nMarker);
376  AveragePressure.resize(nMarker,nSpanWiseSections+1) = su2double(0.0);
377  OldAveragePressure = AveragePressure;
378  RadialEquilibriumPressure = AveragePressure;
379  ExtAveragePressure = AveragePressure;
380  AverageDensity = AveragePressure;
381  OldAverageDensity = AveragePressure;
382  ExtAverageDensity = AveragePressure;
383  AverageNu = AveragePressure;
384  AverageKine = AveragePressure;
385  AverageOmega = AveragePressure;
386  ExtAverageNu = AveragePressure;
387  ExtAverageKine = AveragePressure;
388  ExtAverageOmega = AveragePressure;
389 
390  for (unsigned long iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
391  AverageVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
392  AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
393  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
394  ExtAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
395  AverageFlux[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nVar) = su2double(0.0);
396  SpanTotalFlux[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections+1,nVar) = su2double(0.0);
397  }
398 
399  /*--- Initialize primitive quantities for turboperformace ---*/
400 
401  const auto nMarkerTurboPerf = config->GetnMarker_TurboPerformance();
402  const auto nSpanMax = config->GetnSpanMaxAllZones();
403 
404  DensityIn.resize(nMarkerTurboPerf,nSpanMax+1) = su2double(0.0);
405  PressureIn = DensityIn;
406  TurboVelocityIn.resize(nMarkerTurboPerf);
407  DensityOut = DensityIn;
408  PressureOut = DensityIn;
409  TurboVelocityOut.resize(nMarkerTurboPerf);
410  KineIn = DensityIn;
411  OmegaIn = DensityIn;
412  NuIn = DensityIn;
413  KineOut = DensityIn;
414  OmegaOut = DensityIn;
415  NuOut = DensityIn;
416 
417  for (unsigned long iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarkerTurboPerf; iMarker++) {
418  TurboVelocityIn[iMarker].resize(nSpanMax+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
419  TurboVelocityOut[iMarker].resize(nSpanMax+1,nDim) = su2double(0.0);
420  }
421 
422  /*--- Initialize quantities for NR BC ---*/
423 
424  if(config->GetBoolGiles()){
425 
426  CkInflow.resize(nMarker);
427  CkOutflow1.resize(nMarker);
428  CkOutflow2.resize(nMarker);
429 
430  for (unsigned long iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
431  CkInflow[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections,2*geometry->GetnFreqSpanMax(INFLOW)+1) = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
432  CkOutflow1[iMarker].resize(nSpanWiseSections,2*geometry->GetnFreqSpanMax(OUTFLOW)+1) = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
433  CkOutflow2[iMarker] = CkOutflow1[iMarker];
434  }
435  }
436 }
437 
438 void CEulerSolver::Set_MPI_ActDisk(CSolver **solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config) {
439 
440  unsigned long iter, iPoint, iVertex, jVertex, iPointTotal,
441  Buffer_Send_nPointTotal = 0;
442  long iGlobalIndex, iGlobal;
443  unsigned short iVar, iMarker, jMarker;
444  long nDomain = 0, iDomain, jDomain;
445  //bool ActDisk_Perimeter;
446  bool rans = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE) && (solver_container[TURB_SOL] != nullptr);
447 
448  unsigned short nPrimVar_ = nPrimVar;
449  if (rans) nPrimVar_ += 2; // Add two extra variables for the turbulence.
450 
451  /*--- MPI status and request arrays for non-blocking communications ---*/
452 
453  SU2_MPI::Status status;
454  SU2_MPI::Request req;
455 
456  /*--- Define buffer vector interior domain ---*/
457 
458  su2double *Buffer_Send_PrimVar = nullptr;
459  long *Buffer_Send_Data = nullptr;
460 
461  unsigned long *nPointTotal_s = new unsigned long[size];
462  unsigned long *nPointTotal_r = new unsigned long[size];
463  su2double *iPrimVar = new su2double [nPrimVar_];
464 
465  unsigned long Buffer_Size_PrimVar = 0;
466  unsigned long Buffer_Size_Data = 0;
467 
468  unsigned long PointTotal_Counter = 0;
469 
470  /*--- Allocate the memory that we only need if we have MPI support ---*/
471 
472  su2double *Buffer_Receive_PrimVar = nullptr;
473  long *Buffer_Receive_Data = nullptr;
474 
475  /*--- Basic dimensionalization ---*/
476 
477  nDomain = size;
478 
479  /*--- This loop gets the array sizes of points for each
480  rank to send to each other rank. ---*/
481 
482  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
483 
484  /*--- Loop over the markers to perform the dimensionalizaton
485  of the domain variables ---*/
486 
487  Buffer_Send_nPointTotal = 0;
488 
489  /*--- Loop over all of the markers and count the number of each
490  type of point and element that needs to be sent. ---*/
491 
492  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
493  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
494  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
495  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
496  //ActDisk_Perimeter = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetActDisk_Perimeter();
497  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
498  jDomain = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorProcessor();
499 // if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) && (!ActDisk_Perimeter)) {
500  if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))) {
501  Buffer_Send_nPointTotal++;
502  }
503  }
504  }
505  }
506 
507  /*--- Store the counts on a partition by partition basis. ---*/
508 
509  nPointTotal_s[iDomain] = Buffer_Send_nPointTotal;
510 
511  /*--- Total counts for allocating send buffers below ---*/
512 
513  Buffer_Size_PrimVar += nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_);
514  Buffer_Size_Data += nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3);
515 
516  }
517 
518  /*--- Allocate the buffer vectors in the appropiate domain (master, iDomain) ---*/
519 
520  Buffer_Send_PrimVar = new su2double[Buffer_Size_PrimVar];
521  Buffer_Send_Data = new long[Buffer_Size_Data];
522 
523  /*--- Now that we know the sizes of the point, we can
524  allocate and send the information in large chunks to all processors. ---*/
525 
526  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
527 
528  /*--- A rank does not communicate with itself through MPI ---*/
529 
530  if (rank != iDomain) {
531 
532  /*--- Communicate the counts to iDomain with non-blocking sends ---*/
533 
534  SU2_MPI::Isend(&nPointTotal_s[iDomain], 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, iDomain, iDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
535  SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
536 
537  } else {
538 
539  /*--- If iDomain = rank, we simply copy values into place in memory ---*/
540 
541  nPointTotal_r[iDomain] = nPointTotal_s[iDomain];
542 
543  }
544 
545  /*--- Receive the counts. All processors are sending their counters to
546  iDomain up above, so only iDomain needs to perform the recv here from
547  all other ranks. ---*/
548 
549  if (rank == iDomain) {
550 
551  for (jDomain = 0; jDomain < size; jDomain++) {
552 
553  /*--- A rank does not communicate with itself through MPI ---*/
554 
555  if (rank != jDomain) {
556 
557  /*--- Recv the data by probing for the current sender, jDomain,
558  first and then receiving the values from it. ---*/
559 
560  SU2_MPI::Recv(&nPointTotal_r[jDomain], 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, jDomain, rank, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
561 
562  }
563  }
564 
565  }
566  }
567 
568  /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
569 
570  SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
571 
572  /*--- Initialize the counters for the larger send buffers (by domain) ---*/
573 
574  PointTotal_Counter = 0;
575 
576  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < nDomain; iDomain++) {
577 
578  /*--- Set the value of the interior geometry. Initialize counters. ---*/
579 
580  iPointTotal = 0;
581 
582  /*--- Load up the actual values into the buffers for sending. ---*/
583 
584  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
585 
586  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
587  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
588  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
589  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
590 
591  jDomain = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorProcessor();
592  //ActDisk_Perimeter = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetActDisk_Perimeter();
593 
594 // if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) && (!ActDisk_Perimeter)) {
595  if ((iDomain == jDomain) && (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))) {
596 
597  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) {
598  Buffer_Send_PrimVar[(nPrimVar_)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+iVar] = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint,iVar);
599  }
600  if (rans) {
601  Buffer_Send_PrimVar[(nPrimVar_)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+nPrimVar] = solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
602  Buffer_Send_PrimVar[(nPrimVar_)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(nPrimVar+1)] = 0.0;
603  }
604 
605  iGlobalIndex = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint);
606  jVertex = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorVertex();
607  jMarker = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetDonorMarker();
608 
609  Buffer_Send_Data[(3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(0)] = iGlobalIndex;
610  Buffer_Send_Data[(3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(1)] = jVertex;
611  Buffer_Send_Data[(3)*(PointTotal_Counter+iPointTotal)+(2)] = jMarker;
612 
613  iPointTotal++;
614 
615  }
616 
617  }
618 
619  }
620 
621  }
622 
623  /*--- Send the buffers with the geometrical information ---*/
624 
625  if (iDomain != rank) {
626 
627  /*--- Communicate the coordinates, global index, colors, and element
628  date to iDomain with non-blocking sends. ---*/
629 
630  SU2_MPI::Isend(&Buffer_Send_PrimVar[PointTotal_Counter*(nPrimVar_)],
631  nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_), MPI_DOUBLE, iDomain,
632  iDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
633  SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
634 
635  SU2_MPI::Isend(&Buffer_Send_Data[PointTotal_Counter*(3)],
636  nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3), MPI_LONG, iDomain,
637  iDomain+nDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &req);
638  SU2_MPI::Request_free(&req);
639  }
640 
641  else {
642 
643  /*--- Allocate local memory for the local recv of the elements ---*/
644 
645  Buffer_Receive_PrimVar = new su2double[nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_)];
646  Buffer_Receive_Data = new long[nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3)];
647 
648  for (iter = 0; iter < nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_); iter++)
649  Buffer_Receive_PrimVar[iter] = Buffer_Send_PrimVar[PointTotal_Counter*(nPrimVar_)+iter];
650 
651  for (iter = 0; iter < nPointTotal_s[iDomain]*(3); iter++)
652  Buffer_Receive_Data[iter] = Buffer_Send_Data[PointTotal_Counter*(3)+iter];
653 
654 
655  /*--- Recv the point data from ourselves (same procedure as above) ---*/
656 
657  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointTotal_r[iDomain]; iPoint++) {
658 
659  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++)
660  iPrimVar[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_PrimVar[iPoint*(nPrimVar_)+iVar];
661 
662  iGlobal = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(0)];
663  iVertex = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(1)];
664  iMarker = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(2)];
665 
666  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++)
667  DonorPrimVar[iMarker][iVertex][iVar] = iPrimVar[iVar];
668 
669  SetDonorGlobalIndex(iMarker, iVertex, iGlobal);
670 
671  }
672 
673  /*--- Delete memory for recv the point stuff ---*/
674 
675  delete [] Buffer_Receive_PrimVar;
676  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Data;
677 
678  }
679 
680  /*--- Increment the counters for the send buffers (iDomain loop) ---*/
681 
682  PointTotal_Counter += iPointTotal;
683 
684  }
685 
686  /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
687 
688  SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
689 
690  /*--- The next section begins the recv of all data for the interior
691  points/elements in the mesh. First, create the domain structures for
692  the points on this rank. First, we recv all of the point data ---*/
693 
694  for (iDomain = 0; iDomain < size; iDomain++) {
695 
696  if (rank != iDomain) {
697 
698 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
699 
700  /*--- Allocate the receive buffer vector. Send the colors so that we
701  know whether what we recv is an owned or halo node. ---*/
702 
703  Buffer_Receive_PrimVar = new su2double [nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_)];
704  Buffer_Receive_Data = new long [nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(3)];
705 
706  /*--- Receive the buffers with the coords, global index, and colors ---*/
707 
708  SU2_MPI::Recv(Buffer_Receive_PrimVar, nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(nPrimVar_) , MPI_DOUBLE,
709  iDomain, rank, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
710 
711  SU2_MPI::Recv(Buffer_Receive_Data, nPointTotal_r[iDomain]*(3) , MPI_LONG,
712  iDomain, rank+nDomain, SU2_MPI::GetComm(), &status);
713 
714  /*--- Loop over all of the points that we have recv'd and store the
715  coords, global index vertex and markers ---*/
716 
717  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointTotal_r[iDomain]; iPoint++) {
718 
719  iGlobal = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(0)];
720  iVertex = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(1)];
721  iMarker = Buffer_Receive_Data[iPoint*(3)+(2)];
722 
723  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++)
724  iPrimVar[iVar] = Buffer_Receive_PrimVar[iPoint*(nPrimVar_)+iVar];
725 
726  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar_; iVar++) {
727  DonorPrimVar[iMarker][iVertex][iVar] = iPrimVar[iVar];
728  }
729 
730  SetDonorGlobalIndex(iMarker, iVertex, iGlobal);
731 
732  }
733 
734  /*--- Delete memory for recv the point stuff ---*/
735 
736  delete [] Buffer_Receive_PrimVar;
737  delete [] Buffer_Receive_Data;
738 
739 #endif
740 
741  }
742 
743  }
744 
745  /*--- Wait for the non-blocking sends to complete. ---*/
746 
747  SU2_MPI::Barrier(SU2_MPI::GetComm());
748 
749  /*--- Free all of the memory used for communicating points and elements ---*/
750 
751  delete[] Buffer_Send_PrimVar;
752  delete[] Buffer_Send_Data;
753 
754  /*--- Release all of the temporary memory ---*/
755 
756  delete [] nPointTotal_s;
757  delete [] nPointTotal_r;
758  delete [] iPrimVar;
759 
760 }
761 
762 void CEulerSolver::SetNondimensionalization(CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
763 
764  su2double Temperature_FreeStream = 0.0, Mach2Vel_FreeStream = 0.0, ModVel_FreeStream = 0.0,
765  Energy_FreeStream = 0.0, ModVel_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Velocity_Reynolds = 0.0,
766  Omega_FreeStream = 0.0, Omega_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Viscosity_FreeStream = 0.0,
767  Density_FreeStream = 0.0, Pressure_FreeStream = 0.0, Tke_FreeStream = 0.0, Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = 0.0,
768  Length_Ref = 0.0, Density_Ref = 0.0, Pressure_Ref = 0.0, Velocity_Ref = 0.0,
769  Temperature_Ref = 0.0, Time_Ref = 0.0, Omega_Ref = 0.0, Force_Ref = 0.0,
770  Gas_Constant_Ref = 0.0, Viscosity_Ref = 0.0, Conductivity_Ref = 0.0, Energy_Ref= 0.0,
771  Froude = 0.0, Pressure_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Density_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
772  Temperature_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Gas_ConstantND = 0.0,
773  Velocity_FreeStreamND[3] = {0.0, 0.0, 0.0}, Viscosity_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
774  Tke_FreeStreamND = 0.0, Energy_FreeStreamND = 0.0,
775  Total_UnstTimeND = 0.0, Delta_UnstTimeND = 0.0, TgammaR = 0.0, Heat_Flux_Ref = 0.0;
776 
777  unsigned short iDim;
778 
779  /*--- Local variables ---*/
780 
781  su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
782  su2double Beta = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
783  su2double Mach = config->GetMach();
784  su2double Reynolds = config->GetReynolds();
785  bool unsteady = (config->GetTime_Marching() != TIME_MARCHING::STEADY);
786  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
787  bool gravity = config->GetGravityForce();
788  bool turbulent = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
789  bool tkeNeeded = (turbulent && config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
790  bool free_stream_temp = (config->GetKind_FreeStreamOption() == FREESTREAM_OPTION::TEMPERATURE_FS);
791  bool reynolds_init = (config->GetKind_InitOption() == REYNOLDS);
792  bool aeroelastic = config->GetAeroelastic_Simulation();
793 
794  /*--- Set temperature via the flutter speed index ---*/
795  if (aeroelastic) {
796  su2double vf = config->GetAeroelastic_Flutter_Speed_Index();
797  su2double w_alpha = config->GetAeroelastic_Frequency_Pitch();
798  su2double b = config->GetLength_Reynolds()/2.0; // airfoil semichord, Reynolds length is by defaul 1.0
799  su2double mu = config->GetAeroelastic_Airfoil_Mass_Ratio();
800  // The temperature times gamma times the gas constant. Depending on the FluidModel temp is calculated below.
801  TgammaR = ((vf*vf)*(b*b)*(w_alpha*w_alpha)*mu) / (Mach*Mach);
802  }
803 
804  /*--- Compressible non dimensionalization ---*/
805 
806  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
807 
808  Pressure_FreeStream = config->GetPressure_FreeStream();
809  Density_FreeStream = config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
810  Temperature_FreeStream = config->GetTemperature_FreeStream();
811 
812  /*--- The dimensional viscosity is needed to determine the free-stream conditions.
813  To accomplish this, simply set the non-dimensional coefficients to the
814  dimensional ones. This will be overruled later.---*/
815 
816  config->SetTemperature_Ref(1.0);
817  config->SetViscosity_Ref(1.0);
818  config->SetConductivity_Ref(1.0);
819 
820  CFluidModel* auxFluidModel = nullptr;
821 
822  switch (config->GetKind_FluidModel()) {
823 
824  case STANDARD_AIR:
825 
826  switch (config->GetSystemMeasurements()) {
827  case SI: config->SetGas_Constant(287.058); break;
828  case US: config->SetGas_Constant(1716.49); break;
829  }
830 
831  auxFluidModel = new CIdealGas(1.4, config->GetGas_Constant());
832 
833  if (free_stream_temp && aeroelastic) {
834  Temperature_FreeStream = TgammaR / (config->GetGas_Constant()*1.4);
835  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
836  }
837  break;
838 
839  case IDEAL_GAS:
840 
841  auxFluidModel = new CIdealGas(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant());
842  break;
843 
844  case VW_GAS:
845 
846  auxFluidModel = new CVanDerWaalsGas(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant(),
847  config->GetPressure_Critical(), config->GetTemperature_Critical());
848  break;
849 
850  case PR_GAS:
851 
852  auxFluidModel = new CPengRobinson(Gamma, config->GetGas_Constant(), config->GetPressure_Critical(),
853  config->GetTemperature_Critical(), config->GetAcentric_Factor());
854  break;
855  case COOLPROP:
856 
857  auxFluidModel = new CCoolProp(config->GetFluid_Name());
858  break;
859 
860  default:
861  SU2_MPI::Error("Unknown fluid model.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
862  break;
863  }
864 
865  if (free_stream_temp) {
866  auxFluidModel->SetTDState_PT(Pressure_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
867  Density_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetDensity();
868  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
869  }
870  else {
871  auxFluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_FreeStream, Density_FreeStream );
872  Temperature_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetTemperature();
873  config->SetTemperature_FreeStream(Temperature_FreeStream);
874  }
875 
876  Mach2Vel_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
877 
878  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
879 
880  if (nDim == 2) {
881  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] = cos(Alpha)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
882  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] = sin(Alpha)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
883  }
884  if (nDim == 3) {
885  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
886  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] = sin(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
887  config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
888  }
889 
890  /*--- Compute the modulus of the free stream velocity ---*/
891 
892  ModVel_FreeStream = 0.0;
893  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
894  ModVel_FreeStream += config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim];
895  ModVel_FreeStream = sqrt(ModVel_FreeStream); config->SetModVel_FreeStream(ModVel_FreeStream);
896 
897  /*--- Viscous initialization ---*/
898 
899  if (viscous) {
900 
901  /*--- Check if there is mesh motion. If yes, use the Mach
902  number relative to the body to initialize the flow. ---*/
903 
904  if (dynamic_grid) Velocity_Reynolds = config->GetMach_Motion()*Mach2Vel_FreeStream;
905  else Velocity_Reynolds = ModVel_FreeStream;
906 
907  /*--- Reynolds based initialization ---*/
908 
909  if (reynolds_init) {
910 
911  /*--- For viscous flows, pressure will be computed from a density
912  that is found from the Reynolds number. The viscosity is computed
913  from the dimensional version of Sutherland's law or the constant
914  viscosity, depending on the input option.---*/
915 
916  auxFluidModel->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
917 
918  Viscosity_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetLaminarViscosity();
919  config->SetViscosity_FreeStream(Viscosity_FreeStream);
920 
921  Density_FreeStream = Reynolds*Viscosity_FreeStream/(Velocity_Reynolds*config->GetLength_Reynolds());
922  config->SetDensity_FreeStream(Density_FreeStream);
923  auxFluidModel->SetTDState_rhoT(Density_FreeStream, Temperature_FreeStream);
924  Pressure_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetPressure();
925  config->SetPressure_FreeStream(Pressure_FreeStream);
926  Energy_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
927 
928  }
929 
930  /*--- Thermodynamics quantities based initialization ---*/
931 
932  else {
933 
934  auxFluidModel->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
935  Viscosity_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetLaminarViscosity();
936  config->SetViscosity_FreeStream(Viscosity_FreeStream);
937  Energy_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
938 
939  /*--- Compute Reynolds number ---*/
940  Reynolds = (Density_FreeStream*Velocity_Reynolds*config->GetLength_Reynolds())/Viscosity_FreeStream;
941  config->SetReynolds(Reynolds);
942  }
943 
944  /*--- Turbulence kinetic energy ---*/
945 
946  Tke_FreeStream = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
947 
948  }
949  else {
950 
951  /*--- For inviscid flow, energy is calculated from the specified
952  FreeStream quantities using the proper gas law. ---*/
953 
954  Energy_FreeStream = auxFluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream;
955 
956  }
957 
958  /*-- Compute the freestream energy. ---*/
959 
960  if (tkeNeeded) { Energy_FreeStream += Tke_FreeStream; }; config->SetEnergy_FreeStream(Energy_FreeStream);
961 
962  /*--- Compute non dimensional quantities. By definition,
963  Lref is one because we have converted the grid to meters. ---*/
964 
965  if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == DIMENSIONAL) {
966  Pressure_Ref = 1.0;
967  Density_Ref = 1.0;
968  Temperature_Ref = 1.0;
969  }
970  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_PRESS_EQ_ONE) {
971  Pressure_Ref = Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0
972  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
973  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temperature_FreeStream = 1.0
974  }
975  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_VEL_EQ_MACH) {
976  Pressure_Ref = Gamma*Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0/Gamma
977  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
978  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temp_FreeStream = 1.0
979  }
980  else if (config->GetRef_NonDim() == FREESTREAM_VEL_EQ_ONE) {
981  Pressure_Ref = Mach*Mach*Gamma*Pressure_FreeStream; // Pressure_FreeStream = 1.0/(Gamma*(M_inf)^2)
982  Density_Ref = Density_FreeStream; // Density_FreeStream = 1.0
983  Temperature_Ref = Temperature_FreeStream; // Temp_FreeStream = 1.0
984  }
985  config->SetPressure_Ref(Pressure_Ref);
986  config->SetDensity_Ref(Density_Ref);
987  config->SetTemperature_Ref(Temperature_Ref);
988 
989  Length_Ref = 1.0; config->SetLength_Ref(Length_Ref);
990  Velocity_Ref = sqrt(config->GetPressure_Ref()/config->GetDensity_Ref()); config->SetVelocity_Ref(Velocity_Ref);
991  Time_Ref = Length_Ref/Velocity_Ref; config->SetTime_Ref(Time_Ref);
992  Omega_Ref = Velocity_Ref/Length_Ref; config->SetOmega_Ref(Omega_Ref);
993  Force_Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref()*Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref*Length_Ref*Length_Ref; config->SetForce_Ref(Force_Ref);
994  Heat_Flux_Ref = Density_Ref*Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref; config->SetHeat_Flux_Ref(Heat_Flux_Ref);
995  Gas_Constant_Ref = Velocity_Ref*Velocity_Ref/config->GetTemperature_Ref(); config->SetGas_Constant_Ref(Gas_Constant_Ref);
996  Viscosity_Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref()*Velocity_Ref*Length_Ref; config->SetViscosity_Ref(Viscosity_Ref);
997  Conductivity_Ref = Viscosity_Ref*Gas_Constant_Ref; config->SetConductivity_Ref(Conductivity_Ref);
998  Froude = ModVel_FreeStream/sqrt(STANDARD_GRAVITY*Length_Ref); config->SetFroude(Froude);
999 
1000  /*--- Divide by reference values, to compute the non-dimensional free-stream values ---*/
1001 
1002  Pressure_FreeStreamND = Pressure_FreeStream/config->GetPressure_Ref(); config->SetPressure_FreeStreamND(Pressure_FreeStreamND);
1003  Density_FreeStreamND = Density_FreeStream/config->GetDensity_Ref(); config->SetDensity_FreeStreamND(Density_FreeStreamND);
1004 
1005  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1006  Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim] = config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[iDim]/Velocity_Ref; config->SetVelocity_FreeStreamND(Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim], iDim);
1007  }
1008 
1009  Temperature_FreeStreamND = Temperature_FreeStream/config->GetTemperature_Ref(); config->SetTemperature_FreeStreamND(Temperature_FreeStreamND);
1010 
1011  Gas_ConstantND = config->GetGas_Constant()/Gas_Constant_Ref; config->SetGas_ConstantND(Gas_ConstantND);
1012 
1013 
1014  ModVel_FreeStreamND = 0.0;
1015  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) ModVel_FreeStreamND += Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim]*Velocity_FreeStreamND[iDim];
1016  ModVel_FreeStreamND = sqrt(ModVel_FreeStreamND); config->SetModVel_FreeStreamND(ModVel_FreeStreamND);
1017 
1018  Viscosity_FreeStreamND = Viscosity_FreeStream / Viscosity_Ref; config->SetViscosity_FreeStreamND(Viscosity_FreeStreamND);
1019 
1020  Tke_FreeStream = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStream*ModVel_FreeStream*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
1021  config->SetTke_FreeStream(Tke_FreeStream);
1022 
1023  Tke_FreeStreamND = 3.0/2.0*(ModVel_FreeStreamND*ModVel_FreeStreamND*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream()*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream());
1024  config->SetTke_FreeStreamND(Tke_FreeStreamND);
1025 
1026  Omega_FreeStream = Density_FreeStream*Tke_FreeStream/(Viscosity_FreeStream*config->GetTurb2LamViscRatio_FreeStream());
1027  config->SetOmega_FreeStream(Omega_FreeStream);
1028 
1029  Omega_FreeStreamND = Density_FreeStreamND*Tke_FreeStreamND/(Viscosity_FreeStreamND*config->GetTurb2LamViscRatio_FreeStream());
1030  config->SetOmega_FreeStreamND(Omega_FreeStreamND);
1031 
1032  if (config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100 <= 1.3) {
1033  if (config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100 >=0.027) {
1034  Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = (1173.51-589.428*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100+0.2196/
1035  (config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100));
1036  }
1037  else {
1038  Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = (1173.51-589.428*config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100+0.2196/(0.27*0.27));
1039  }
1040  }
1041  else {
1042  Re_ThetaT_FreeStream = 331.5*pow(config->GetTurbulenceIntensity_FreeStream() *100-0.5658,-0.671);
1043  }
1044  config->SetReThetaT_FreeStream(Re_ThetaT_FreeStream);
1045 
1046  const su2double MassDiffusivityND = config->GetDiffusivity_Constant() / (Velocity_Ref * Length_Ref);
1047  config->SetDiffusivity_ConstantND(MassDiffusivityND);
1048 
1049  /*--- Initialize the dimensionless Fluid Model that will be used to solve the dimensionless problem ---*/
1050 
1051  /*--- Auxilary (dimensional) FluidModel no longer needed. ---*/
1052  delete auxFluidModel;
1053 
1054  /*--- Create one final fluid model object per OpenMP thread to be able to use them in parallel.
1055  * GetFluidModel() should be used to automatically access the "right" object of each thread. ---*/
1056 
1057  assert(FluidModel.empty() && "Potential memory leak!");
1058  FluidModel.resize(omp_get_max_threads());
1059 
1060  SU2_OMP_PARALLEL
1061  {
1062  const int thread = omp_get_thread_num();
1063 
1064  switch (config->GetKind_FluidModel()) {
1065 
1066  case STANDARD_AIR:
1067  FluidModel[thread] = new CIdealGas(1.4, Gas_ConstantND);
1068  break;
1069 
1070  case IDEAL_GAS:
1071  FluidModel[thread] = new CIdealGas(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND);
1072  break;
1073 
1074  case VW_GAS:
1075  FluidModel[thread] = new CVanDerWaalsGas(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND,
1076  config->GetPressure_Critical() / config->GetPressure_Ref(),
1077  config->GetTemperature_Critical() / config->GetTemperature_Ref());
1078  break;
1079 
1080  case PR_GAS:
1081  FluidModel[thread] = new CPengRobinson(Gamma, Gas_ConstantND,
1082  config->GetPressure_Critical() / config->GetPressure_Ref(),
1083  config->GetTemperature_Critical() / config->GetTemperature_Ref(),
1084  config->GetAcentric_Factor());
1085  break;
1086 
1087  case COOLPROP:
1088  FluidModel[thread] = new CCoolProp(config->GetFluid_Name());
1089  break;
1090  }
1091 
1092  GetFluidModel()->SetEnergy_Prho(Pressure_FreeStreamND, Density_FreeStreamND);
1093  if (viscous) {
1094  GetFluidModel()->SetLaminarViscosityModel(config);
1095  GetFluidModel()->SetThermalConductivityModel(config);
1096  }
1097 
1098  }
1099  END_SU2_OMP_PARALLEL
1100 
1101  Energy_FreeStreamND = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*ModVel_FreeStreamND*ModVel_FreeStreamND;
1102 
1103  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_FreeStreamND += Tke_FreeStreamND;
1104 
1105  config->SetEnergy_FreeStreamND(Energy_FreeStreamND);
1106 
1107  Energy_Ref = Energy_FreeStream/Energy_FreeStreamND; config->SetEnergy_Ref(Energy_Ref);
1108 
1109  Total_UnstTimeND = config->GetTotal_UnstTime() / Time_Ref; config->SetTotal_UnstTimeND(Total_UnstTimeND);
1110  Delta_UnstTimeND = config->GetDelta_UnstTime() / Time_Ref; config->SetDelta_UnstTimeND(Delta_UnstTimeND);
1111 
1112  /*--- Write output to the console if this is the master node and first domain ---*/
1113 
1114  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (MGLevel == MESH_0)) {
1115 
1116  cout.precision(6);
1117 
1118  if (viscous) {
1119  cout << "Viscous flow: Computing pressure using the ideal gas law" << endl;
1120  cout << "based on the free-stream temperature and a density computed" << endl;
1121  cout << "from the Reynolds number." << endl;
1122  } else {
1123  cout << "Inviscid flow: Computing density based on free-stream" << endl;
1124  cout << "temperature and pressure using the ideal gas law." << endl;
1125  }
1126 
1127  if (dynamic_grid) cout << "Force coefficients computed using MACH_MOTION." << endl;
1128  else cout << "Force coefficients computed using free-stream values." << endl;
1129 
1130  stringstream NonDimTableOut, ModelTableOut;
1131  stringstream Unit;
1132 
1133  cout << endl;
1134  PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter ModelTable(&ModelTableOut);
1135  ModelTableOut <<"-- Models:"<< endl;
1136 
1137  ModelTable.AddColumn("Viscosity Model", 25);
1138  ModelTable.AddColumn("Conductivity Model", 26);
1139  ModelTable.AddColumn("Fluid Model", 25);
1140  ModelTable.SetAlign(PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter::RIGHT);
1141  ModelTable.PrintHeader();
1142 
1143  PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter NonDimTable(&NonDimTableOut);
1144  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Name", 22);
1145  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Dim. value", 14);
1146  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Ref. value", 14);
1147  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Unit", 10);
1148  NonDimTable.AddColumn("Non-dim. value", 14);
1149  NonDimTable.SetAlign(PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter::RIGHT);
1150 
1151  NonDimTableOut <<"-- Fluid properties:"<< endl;
1152 
1153  NonDimTable.PrintHeader();
1154 
1155  if (viscous) {
1156 
1157  switch(config->GetKind_ViscosityModel()){
1158  case VISCOSITYMODEL::CONSTANT:
1159  ModelTable << "CONSTANT_VISCOSITY";
1160  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1161  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1162  NonDimTable << "Viscosity" << config->GetMu_Constant() << config->GetMu_Constant()/config->GetMu_ConstantND() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_ConstantND();
1163  Unit.str("");
1164  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1165  break;
1166 
1167  case VISCOSITYMODEL::COOLPROP:
1168  ModelTable << "COOLPROP";
1169  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1170  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1171  NonDimTable << "Viscosity" << "--" << "--" << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_ConstantND();
1172  Unit.str("");
1173  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1174  break;
1175 
1176  case VISCOSITYMODEL::SUTHERLAND:
1177  ModelTable << "SUTHERLAND";
1178  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1179  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1180  NonDimTable << "Ref. Viscosity" << config->GetMu_Ref() << config->GetViscosity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_RefND();
1181  Unit.str("");
1182  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "K";
1183  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "R";
1184  NonDimTable << "Sutherland Temp." << config->GetMu_Temperature_Ref() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_Temperature_RefND();
1185  Unit.str("");
1186  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "K";
1187  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "R";
1188  NonDimTable << "Sutherland Const." << config->GetMu_S() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetMu_SND();
1189  Unit.str("");
1190  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1191  break;
1192 
1193  default:
1194  break;
1195 
1196  }
1197  switch(config->GetKind_ConductivityModel()){
1198  case CONDUCTIVITYMODEL::CONSTANT_PRANDTL:
1199  ModelTable << "CONSTANT_PRANDTL";
1200  NonDimTable << "Prandtl (Lam.)" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetPrandtl_Lam();
1201  Unit.str("");
1202  NonDimTable << "Prandtl (Turb.)" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetPrandtl_Turb();
1203  Unit.str("");
1204  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1205  break;
1206 
1207  case CONDUCTIVITYMODEL::CONSTANT:
1208  ModelTable << "CONSTANT";
1209  Unit << "W/m^2.K";
1210  NonDimTable << "Molecular Cond." << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_Constant() << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_Constant()/config->GetThermal_Conductivity_ConstantND() << Unit.str() << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_ConstantND();
1211  Unit.str("");
1212  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1213  break;
1214 
1215  case CONDUCTIVITYMODEL::COOLPROP:
1216  ModelTable << "COOLPROP";
1217  Unit << "W/m^2.K";
1218  NonDimTable << "Molecular Cond." << "--" << "--" << Unit.str() << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_ConstantND();
1219  Unit.str("");
1220  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1221  break;
1222 
1223  default:
1224  break;
1225 
1226  }
1227  } else {
1228  ModelTable << "-" << "-";
1229  }
1230 
1231  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.m/kg.K";
1232  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.ft/slug.R";
1233  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == COOLPROP) {
1234  CCoolProp auxFluidModel(config->GetFluid_Name());
1235  NonDimTable << "Gas Constant" << auxFluidModel.GetGas_Constant() << config->GetGas_Constant_Ref() << Unit.str() << auxFluidModel.GetGas_Constant()/config->GetGas_Constant_Ref();
1236  }
1237  else {
1238  NonDimTable << "Gas Constant" << config->GetGas_Constant() << config->GetGas_Constant_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetGas_ConstantND();
1239  }
1240  Unit.str("");
1241  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.m/kg.K";
1242  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.ft/slug.R";
1243  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == COOLPROP) {
1244  NonDimTable << "Spec. Heat Ratio" << "-" << "-" << "-" << "-";
1245  }
1246  else {
1247  NonDimTable << "Spec. Heat Ratio" << "-" << "-" << "-" << Gamma;
1248  }
1249  Unit.str("");
1250 
1251  switch(config->GetKind_FluidModel()){
1252  case STANDARD_AIR:
1253  ModelTable << "STANDARD_AIR";
1254  break;
1255  case IDEAL_GAS:
1256  ModelTable << "IDEAL_GAS";
1257  break;
1258  case VW_GAS:
1259  ModelTable << "VW_GAS";
1260  break;
1261  case PR_GAS:
1262  ModelTable << "PR_GAS";
1263  break;
1264  case COOLPROP:
1265  ModelTable << "CoolProp library";
1266  break;
1267  }
1268 
1269  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == VW_GAS || config->GetKind_FluidModel() == PR_GAS){
1270  NonDimTable << "Critical Pressure" << config->GetPressure_Critical() << config->GetPressure_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref();
1271  Unit.str("");
1272  Unit << "K";
1273  NonDimTable << "Critical Temperature" << config->GetTemperature_Critical() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetTemperature_Critical() /config->GetTemperature_Ref();
1274  Unit.str("");
1275  }
1276  if (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == COOLPROP) {
1277  CCoolProp auxFluidModel(config->GetFluid_Name());
1278  NonDimTable << "Critical Pressure" << auxFluidModel.GetPressure_Critical() << config->GetPressure_Ref() << Unit.str() << auxFluidModel.GetPressure_Critical() /config->GetPressure_Ref();
1279  Unit.str("");
1280  Unit << "K";
1281  NonDimTable << "Critical Temperature" << auxFluidModel.GetTemperature_Critical() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << auxFluidModel.GetTemperature_Critical() /config->GetTemperature_Ref();
1282  Unit.str("");
1283  }
1284  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1285 
1286  NonDimTableOut <<"-- Initial and free-stream conditions:"<< endl;
1287 
1288  NonDimTable.PrintHeader();
1289 
1290  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "Pa";
1291  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "psf";
1292  NonDimTable << "Static Pressure" << config->GetPressure_FreeStream() << config->GetPressure_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
1293  Unit.str("");
1294  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "kg/m^3";
1295  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "slug/ft^3";
1296  NonDimTable << "Density" << config->GetDensity_FreeStream() << config->GetDensity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetDensity_FreeStreamND();
1297  Unit.str("");
1298  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "K";
1299  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "R";
1300  NonDimTable << "Temperature" << config->GetTemperature_FreeStream() << config->GetTemperature_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND();
1301  Unit.str("");
1302  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m^2/s^2";
1303  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft^2/s^2";
1304  NonDimTable << "Total Energy" << config->GetEnergy_FreeStream() << config->GetEnergy_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetEnergy_FreeStreamND();
1305  Unit.str("");
1306  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m/s";
1307  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft/s";
1308  NonDimTable << "Velocity-X" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[0] << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[0];
1309  NonDimTable << "Velocity-Y" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[1] << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[1];
1310  if (nDim == 3){
1311  NonDimTable << "Velocity-Z" << config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()[2] << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[2];
1312  }
1313  NonDimTable << "Velocity Magnitude" << config->GetModVel_FreeStream() << config->GetVelocity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetModVel_FreeStreamND();
1314  Unit.str("");
1315 
1316  if (viscous){
1317  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1318  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "N.s/m^2";
1319  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf.s/ft^2";
1320  NonDimTable << "Viscosity" << config->GetViscosity_FreeStream() << config->GetViscosity_Ref() << Unit.str() << config->GetViscosity_FreeStreamND();
1321  Unit.str("");
1322  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "W/m^2.K";
1323  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "lbf/ft.s.R";
1324  NonDimTable << "Conductivity" << "-" << config->GetThermal_Conductivity_Ref() << Unit.str() << "-";
1325  Unit.str("");
1326  if (turbulent){
1327  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m^2/s^2";
1328  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft^2/s^2";
1329  NonDimTable << "Turb. Kin. Energy" << config->GetTke_FreeStream() << config->GetTke_FreeStream()/config->GetTke_FreeStreamND() << Unit.str() << config->GetTke_FreeStreamND();
1330  Unit.str("");
1331  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "1/s";
1332  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "1/s";
1333  NonDimTable << "Spec. Dissipation" << config->GetOmega_FreeStream() << config->GetOmega_FreeStream()/config->GetOmega_FreeStreamND() << Unit.str() << config->GetOmega_FreeStreamND();
1334  Unit.str("");
1335  if (config-> GetKind_Trans_Model() == TURB_TRANS_MODEL::LM) {
1336  NonDimTable << "Intermittency" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetIntermittency_FreeStream();
1337  Unit.str("");
1338  NonDimTable << "Moment. Thick. Re" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetReThetaT_FreeStream();
1339  Unit.str("");
1340  }
1341  }
1342  if (config->GetKind_Species_Model() != SPECIES_MODEL::NONE) {
1343  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Unit << "m^2/s";
1344  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Unit << "ft^2/s";
1345  NonDimTable << "Mass Diffusivity" << config->GetDiffusivity_Constant() << config->GetDiffusivity_Constant()/config->GetDiffusivity_ConstantND() << Unit.str() << config->GetDiffusivity_ConstantND();
1346  Unit.str("");
1347  }
1348  }
1349 
1350  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1351  NonDimTable << "Mach Number" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetMach();
1352  if (viscous){
1353  NonDimTable << "Reynolds Number" << "-" << "-" << "-" << config->GetReynolds();
1354  }
1355  if (gravity) {
1356  NonDimTable << "Froude Number" << "-" << "-" << "-" << Froude;
1357  NonDimTable << "Wave Length" << "-" << "-" << "-" << 2.0*PI_NUMBER*Froude*Froude;
1358  }
1359  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1360  ModelTable.PrintFooter();
1361 
1362  if (unsteady){
1363  NonDimTableOut << "-- Unsteady conditions" << endl;
1364  NonDimTable.PrintHeader();
1365  NonDimTable << "Total Time" << config->GetMax_Time() << config->GetTime_Ref() << "s" << config->GetMax_Time()/config->GetTime_Ref();
1366  Unit.str("");
1367  NonDimTable << "Time Step" << config->GetTime_Step() << config->GetTime_Ref() << "s" << config->GetDelta_UnstTimeND();
1368  Unit.str("");
1369  NonDimTable.PrintFooter();
1370  }
1371 
1372  cout << ModelTableOut.str();
1373  cout << NonDimTableOut.str();
1374 
1375  }
1376
