1378 
1379 void CEulerSolver::SetReferenceValues(const CConfig& config) {
1380 
1381  /*--- Evaluate reference values for non-dimensionalization. For dynamic meshes,
1382  use the motion Mach number as a reference value for computing the force coefficients.
1383  Otherwise, use the freestream values, which is the standard convention. ---*/
1384 
1385  su2double RefVel2;
1386 
1387  if (dynamic_grid && !config.GetFSI_Simulation()) {
1388  su2double Gas_Constant = config.GetGas_ConstantND();
1389  su2double Mach2Vel = sqrt(Gamma * Gas_Constant * Temperature_Inf);
1390  su2double Mach_Motion = config.GetMach_Motion();
1391  RefVel2 = pow(Mach_Motion * Mach2Vel, 2);
1392  }
1393  else {
1394  RefVel2 = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, Velocity_Inf);
1395  }
1396 
1397  DynamicPressureRef = 0.5 * Density_Inf * RefVel2;
1398  AeroCoeffForceRef = DynamicPressureRef * config.GetRefArea();
1399 
1400 }
1401 
1402 void CEulerSolver::SetInitialCondition(CGeometry **geometry, CSolver ***solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned long TimeIter) {
1403 
1404  const bool restart = (config->GetRestart() || config->GetRestart_Flow());
1405  const bool SubsonicEngine = config->GetSubsonicEngine();
1406 
1407  /*--- Use default implementation, then add solver-specifics. ---*/
1408 
1409  BaseClass::SetInitialCondition(geometry, solver_container, config, TimeIter);
1410 
1411  /*--- Set subsonic initial condition for engine intakes at iteration 0 ---*/
1412 
1413  if (!SubsonicEngine || (TimeIter != 0) || restart) return;
1414 
1415  /*--- Start OpenMP parallel region. ---*/
1416 
1417  SU2_OMP_PARALLEL {
1418 
1419  unsigned long iPoint;
1420  unsigned short iMesh, iDim;
1421  su2double X0[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X1[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X2[MAXNDIM] = {0.0},
1422  X1_X0[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X2_X0[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, X2_X1[MAXNDIM] = {0.0},
1423  CP[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, Distance, DotCheck, Radius;
1424 
1425  su2double Velocity_Cyl[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, Velocity_CylND[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, Viscosity_Cyl,
1426  Density_Cyl, Density_CylND, Pressure_CylND, ModVel_Cyl, ModVel_CylND, Energy_CylND,
1427  T_ref = 0.0, S = 0.0, Mu_ref = 0.0;
1428  const su2double *Coord, *SubsonicEngine_Cyl, *SubsonicEngine_Values;
1429 
1430  SubsonicEngine_Values = config->GetSubsonicEngine_Values();
1431  su2double Mach_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[0];
1432  su2double Alpha_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[1];
1433  su2double Beta_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[2];
1434  su2double Pressure_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[3];
1435  su2double Temperature_Cyl = SubsonicEngine_Values[4];
1436 
1437  su2double Alpha = Alpha_Cyl*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
1438  su2double Beta = Beta_Cyl*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
1439 
1440  su2double Gamma_Minus_One = Gamma - 1.0;
1441  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_Constant();
1442 
1443  su2double Mach2Vel_Cyl = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*Temperature_Cyl);
1444 
1445  for (iMesh = 0; iMesh <= config->GetnMGLevels(); iMesh++) {
1446 
1447  auto FlowNodes = solver_container[iMesh][FLOW_SOL]->GetNodes();
1448 
1449  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
1450  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry[iMesh]->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
1451 
1452  Velocity_Cyl[0] = cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach_Cyl*Mach2Vel_Cyl;
1453  Velocity_Cyl[1] = sin(Beta)*Mach_Cyl*Mach2Vel_Cyl;
1454  Velocity_Cyl[2] = sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta)*Mach_Cyl*Mach2Vel_Cyl;
1455 
1456  ModVel_Cyl = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Velocity_Cyl);
1457 
1458  if (config->GetViscous()) {
1459  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) { T_ref = 273.15; S = 110.4; Mu_ref = 1.716E-5; }
1460  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
1461  T_ref = (273.15 - 273.15) * 1.8 + 491.67;
1462  S = (110.4 - 273.15) * 1.8 + 491.67;
1463  Mu_ref = 1.716E-5/47.88025898;
1464  }
1465  Viscosity_Cyl = Mu_ref*(pow(Temperature_Cyl/T_ref, 1.5) * (T_ref+S)/(Temperature_Cyl+S));
1466  Density_Cyl = config->GetReynolds()*Viscosity_Cyl/(ModVel_Cyl*config->GetLength_Reynolds());
1467  Pressure_Cyl = Density_Cyl*Gas_Constant*Temperature_Cyl;
1468  }
1469  else {
1470  Density_Cyl = Pressure_Cyl/(Gas_Constant*Temperature_Cyl);
1471  }
1472 
1473  Density_CylND = Density_Cyl/config->GetDensity_Ref();
1474  Pressure_CylND = Pressure_Cyl/config->GetPressure_Ref();
1475 
1476  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1477  Velocity_CylND[iDim] = Velocity_Cyl[iDim]/config->GetVelocity_Ref();
1478  }
1479 
1480  ModVel_CylND = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Velocity_CylND);
1481 
1482  Energy_CylND = Pressure_CylND/(Density_CylND*Gamma_Minus_One)+0.5*ModVel_CylND*ModVel_CylND;
1483 
1484  Coord = geometry[iMesh]->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
1485 
1486  SubsonicEngine_Cyl = config->GetSubsonicEngine_Cyl();
1487 
1488  X0[0] = Coord[0]; X0[1] = Coord[1]; if (nDim==3) X0[2] = Coord[2];
1489  X1[0] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[0]; X1[1] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[1]; X1[2] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[2];
1490  X2[0] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[3]; X2[1] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[4]; X2[2] = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[5];
1491  Radius = SubsonicEngine_Cyl[6];
1492 
1493  GeometryToolbox::Distance(3, X1, X2, X2_X1);
1494  GeometryToolbox::Distance(3, X0, X1, X1_X0);
1495  GeometryToolbox::Distance(3, X0, X2, X2_X0);
1496 
1497  GeometryToolbox::CrossProduct(X2_X1, X1_X0, CP);
1498 
1499  Distance = sqrt(GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(3,CP) / GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(3,X2_X1));
1500 
1501  DotCheck = -GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(3, X1_X0, X2_X1);
1502  if (DotCheck < 0.0) Distance = GeometryToolbox::Norm(3, X1_X0);
1503 
1504  DotCheck = GeometryToolbox::DotProduct(3, X2_X0, X2_X1);
1505  if (DotCheck < 0.0) Distance = GeometryToolbox::Norm(3, X2_X0);
1506 
1507  if (Distance < Radius) {
1508  FlowNodes->SetSolution(iPoint, 0, Density_CylND);
1509  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1510  FlowNodes->SetSolution(iPoint, iDim+1, Density_CylND*Velocity_CylND[iDim]);
1511  FlowNodes->SetSolution(iPoint, nVar-1, Density_CylND*Energy_CylND);
1512  }
1513 
1514  }
1515  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1516 
1517  FlowNodes->Set_OldSolution();
1518 
1519  }
1520 
1521  }
1522  END_SU2_OMP_PARALLEL
1523 
1524 }
1525 
1526 void CEulerSolver::CommonPreprocessing(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh,
1527  unsigned short iRKStep, unsigned short RunTime_EqSystem, bool Output) {
1528 
1529  bool cont_adjoint = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint();
1530  bool disc_adjoint = config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
1531  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1532  bool center = (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_Flow() == SPACE_CENTERED);
1533  bool center_jst = (config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == CENTERED::JST) && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1534  bool center_jst_ke = (config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == CENTERED::JST_KE) && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1535  bool center_jst_mat = (config->GetKind_Centered_Flow() == CENTERED::JST_MAT) && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1536  bool engine = ((config->GetnMarker_EngineInflow() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust() != 0));
1537  bool actuator_disk = ((config->GetnMarker_ActDiskInlet() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_ActDiskOutlet() != 0));
1538  bool fixed_cl = config->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
1539  unsigned short kind_row_dissipation = config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss();
1540  bool roe_low_dissipation = (kind_row_dissipation != NO_ROELOWDISS) &&
1541  (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::ROE ||
1542  config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::SLAU ||
1543  config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::SLAU2);
1544 
1545  /*--- Set the primitive variables ---*/
1546 
1547  ompMasterAssignBarrier(ErrorCounter, 0);
1548 
1549  SU2_OMP_ATOMIC
1550  ErrorCounter += SetPrimitive_Variables(solver_container, config);
1551 
1552  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
1553  { /*--- Ops that are not OpenMP parallel go in this block. ---*/
1554 
1555  if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL)) {
1556  unsigned long tmp = ErrorCounter;
1557  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &ErrorCounter, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1558  config->SetNonphysical_Points(ErrorCounter);
1559  }
1560 
1561  /*--- Update the angle of attack at the far-field for fixed CL calculations (only direct problem). ---*/
1562 
1563  if (fixed_cl && !disc_adjoint && !cont_adjoint) {
1564  SetFarfield_AoA(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output);
1565  }
1566 
1567  /*--- Compute the engine properties ---*/
1568 
1569  if (engine) GetPower_Properties(geometry, config, iMesh, Output);
1570 
1571  /*--- Compute the actuator disk properties and distortion levels ---*/
1572 
1573  if (actuator_disk) {
1574  Set_MPI_ActDisk(solver_container, geometry, config);
1575  GetPower_Properties(geometry, config, iMesh, Output);
1576  SetActDisk_BCThrust(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output);
1577  }
1578 
1579  }
1580  END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
1581 
1582  /*--- Artificial dissipation ---*/
1583 
1584  if (center && !Output) {
1585  if (!center_jst_mat) SetMax_Eigenvalue(geometry, config);
1586  if (center_jst || center_jst_ke || center_jst_mat) {
1587  SetCentered_Dissipation_Sensor(geometry, config);
1588  if (!center_jst_ke) SetUndivided_Laplacian(geometry, config);
1589  }
1590  }
1591 
1592  /*--- Roe Low Dissipation Sensor ---*/
1593 
1594  if (roe_low_dissipation) {
1595  SetRoe_Dissipation(geometry, config);
1596  if (kind_row_dissipation == FD_DUCROS || kind_row_dissipation == NTS_DUCROS){
1597  SetUpwind_Ducros_Sensor(geometry, config);
1598  }
1599  }
1600 
1601  /*--- Initialize the Jacobian matrix and residual, not needed for the reducer strategy
1602  * as we set blocks (including diagonal ones) and completely overwrite. ---*/
1603 
1604  if(!ReducerStrategy && !Output) {
1605  LinSysRes.SetValZero();
1606  if (implicit) Jacobian.SetValZero();
1607  else {SU2_OMP_BARRIER} // because of "nowait" in LinSysRes
1608  }
1609 
1610 }
1611 
1612 void CEulerSolver::Preprocessing(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh,
1613  unsigned short iRKStep, unsigned short RunTime_EqSystem, bool Output) {
1614  const auto InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
1615  const bool muscl = config->GetMUSCL_Flow() && (iMesh == MESH_0);
1616  const bool center = (config->GetKind_ConvNumScheme_Flow() == SPACE_CENTERED);
1617  const bool limiter = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() != LIMITER::NONE) && (InnerIter <= config->GetLimiterIter());
1618  const bool van_albada = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() == LIMITER::VAN_ALBADA_EDGE);
1619 
1620  /*--- Common preprocessing steps. ---*/
1621 
1622  CommonPreprocessing(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, iRKStep, RunTime_EqSystem, Output);
1623 
1624  /*--- Upwind second order reconstruction ---*/
1625 
1626  if (!Output && muscl && !center) {
1627 
1628  /*--- Gradient computation for MUSCL reconstruction. ---*/
1629 
1630  switch (config->GetKind_Gradient_Method_Recon()) {
1631  case GREEN_GAUSS:
1632  SetPrimitive_Gradient_GG(geometry, config, true); break;
1633  case LEAST_SQUARES:
1634  case WEIGHTED_LEAST_SQUARES:
1635  SetPrimitive_Gradient_LS(geometry, config, true); break;
1636  default: break;
1637  }
1638 
1639  /*--- Limiter computation ---*/
1640 
1641  if (limiter && !van_albada) SetPrimitive_Limiter(geometry, config);
1642  }
1643 }
1644 
1645 unsigned long CEulerSolver::SetPrimitive_Variables(CSolver **solver_container, const CConfig *config) {
1646 
1647  /*--- Number of non-physical points, local to the thread, needs
1648  * further reduction if function is called in parallel ---*/
1649  unsigned long nonPhysicalPoints = 0;
1650 
1651  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
1652 
1653  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
1654  for (unsigned long iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint ++) {
1655 
1656  /*--- Compressible flow, primitive variables nDim+9, (T, vx, vy, vz, P, rho, h, c, lamMu, eddyMu, ThCond, Cp) ---*/
1657 
1658  bool physical = nodes->SetPrimVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
1659  nodes->SetSecondaryVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
1660 
1661  /* Check for non-realizable states for reporting. */
1662 
1663  if (!physical) nonPhysicalPoints++;
1664  }
1665  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1666 
1667  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
1668 
1669  return nonPhysicalPoints;
1670 }
1671 
1672 void CEulerSolver::SetTime_Step(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CConfig *config,
1673  unsigned short iMesh, unsigned long Iteration) {
1674 
1675  /*--- Define an object to compute the speed of sound. ---*/
1676  struct SoundSpeed {
1677  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint, unsigned long jPoint) const {
1678  return 0.5 * (nodes.GetSoundSpeed(iPoint) + nodes.GetSoundSpeed(jPoint));
1679  }
1680 
1681  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint) const {
1682  return nodes.GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
1683  }
1684 
1685  } soundSpeed;
1686 
1687  /*--- Define an object to compute the viscous eigenvalue. ---*/
1688  struct LambdaVisc {
1689  const su2double gamma, prandtlLam, prandtlTurb;
1690 
1691  LambdaVisc(su2double g, su2double pl, su2double pt) : gamma(g), prandtlLam(pl), prandtlTurb(pt) {}
1692 
1693  FORCEINLINE su2double lambda(su2double laminarVisc, su2double eddyVisc, su2double density) const {
1694  su2double Lambda_1 = (4.0/3.0)*(laminarVisc + eddyVisc);
1695  /// TODO: (REAL_GAS) removing gamma as it cannot work with FLUIDPROP
1696  su2double Lambda_2 = (1.0 + (prandtlLam/prandtlTurb)*(eddyVisc/laminarVisc))*(gamma*laminarVisc/prandtlLam);
1697  return (Lambda_1 + Lambda_2) / density;
1698  }
1699 
1700  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint, unsigned long jPoint) const {
1701  su2double laminarVisc = 0.5*(nodes.GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint) + nodes.GetLaminarViscosity(jPoint));
1702  su2double eddyVisc = 0.5*(nodes.GetEddyViscosity(iPoint) + nodes.GetEddyViscosity(jPoint));
1703  su2double density = 0.5*(nodes.GetDensity(iPoint) + nodes.GetDensity(jPoint));
1704  return lambda(laminarVisc, eddyVisc, density);
1705  }
1706 
1707  FORCEINLINE su2double operator() (const CEulerVariable& nodes, unsigned long iPoint) const {
1708  su2double laminarVisc = nodes.GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
1709  su2double eddyVisc = nodes.GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
1710  su2double density = nodes.GetDensity(iPoint);
1711  return lambda(laminarVisc, eddyVisc, density);
1712  }
1713 
1714  } lambdaVisc(Gamma, Prandtl_Lam, Prandtl_Turb);
1715 
1716  /*--- Now instantiate the generic implementation with the two functors above. ---*/
1717 
1718  SetTime_Step_impl(soundSpeed, lambdaVisc, geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Iteration);
1719 
1720 }
1721 
1722 void CEulerSolver::Centered_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics **numerics_container,
1723  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, unsigned short iRKStep) {
1724 
1725  EdgeFluxResidual(geometry, solver_container, config);
1726 }
1727 
1728 void CEulerSolver::Upwind_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
1729  CNumerics **numerics_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
1730 
1731  const bool ideal_gas = (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == STANDARD_AIR) ||
1732  (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == IDEAL_GAS);
1733  const bool low_mach_corr = config->Low_Mach_Correction();
1734 
1735  /*--- Use vectorization if the scheme supports it. ---*/
1736  if (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::ROE && ideal_gas && !low_mach_corr) {
1737  EdgeFluxResidual(geometry, solver_container, config);
1738  return;
1739  }
1740 
1741  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
1742 
1743  const bool roe_turkel = (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::TURKEL);
1744  const auto kind_dissipation = config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss();
1745 
1746  const bool muscl = (config->GetMUSCL_Flow() && (iMesh == MESH_0));
1747  const bool limiter = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() != LIMITER::NONE);
1748  const bool van_albada = (config->GetKind_SlopeLimit_Flow() == LIMITER::VAN_ALBADA_EDGE);
1749 
1750  /*--- Non-physical counter. ---*/
1751  unsigned long counter_local = 0;
1752  SU2_OMP_MASTER
1753  ErrorCounter = 0;
1754  END_SU2_OMP_MASTER
1755 
1756  /*--- Pick one numerics object per thread. ---*/
1757  CNumerics* numerics = numerics_container[CONV_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS];
1758 
1759  /*--- Static arrays of MUSCL-reconstructed primitives and secondaries (thread safety). ---*/
1760  su2double Primitive_i[MAXNVAR] = {0.0}, Primitive_j[MAXNVAR] = {0.0};
1761  su2double Secondary_i[MAXNVAR] = {0.0}, Secondary_j[MAXNVAR] = {0.0};
1762 
1763  /*--- For hybrid parallel AD, pause preaccumulation if there is shared reading of
1764  * variables, otherwise switch to the faster adjoint evaluation mode. ---*/
1765  bool pausePreacc = false;
1766  if (ReducerStrategy) pausePreacc = AD::PausePreaccumulation();
1767  else AD::StartNoSharedReading();
1768 
1769  /*--- Loop over edge colors. ---*/
1770  for (auto color : EdgeColoring)
1771  {
1772  /*--- Chunk size is at least OMP_MIN_SIZE and a multiple of the color group size. ---*/
1773  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(nextMultiple(OMP_MIN_SIZE, color.groupSize))
1774  for(auto k = 0ul; k < color.size; ++k) {
1775 
1776  auto iEdge = color.indices[k];
1777 
1778  unsigned short iDim, iVar;
1779 
1780  /*--- Points in edge and normal vectors ---*/
1781 
1782  auto iPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,0);
1783  auto jPoint = geometry->edges->GetNode(iEdge,1);
1784 
1785  numerics->SetNormal(geometry->edges->GetNormal(iEdge));
1786 
1787  auto Coord_i = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
1788  auto Coord_j = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(jPoint);
1789 
1790  /*--- Roe Turkel preconditioning ---*/
1791 
1792  if (roe_turkel) {
1793  numerics->SetVelocity2_Inf(GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, config->GetVelocity_FreeStream()));
1794  }
1795 
1796  /*--- Grid movement ---*/
1797 
1798  if (dynamic_grid) {
1799  numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
1800  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(jPoint));
1801  }
1802 
1803  /*--- Get primitive and secondary variables ---*/
1804 
1805  auto V_i = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint); auto V_j = nodes->GetPrimitive(jPoint);
1806  auto S_i = nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint); auto S_j = nodes->GetSecondary(jPoint);
1807 
1808  /*--- Set them with or without high order reconstruction using MUSCL strategy. ---*/
1809 
1810  if (!muscl) {
1811 
1812  numerics->SetPrimitive(V_i, V_j);
1813  numerics->SetSecondary(S_i, S_j);
1814 
1815  }
1816  else {
1817  /*--- Reconstruction ---*/
1818 
1819  su2double Vector_ij[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
1820  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1821  Vector_ij[iDim] = 0.5*(Coord_j[iDim] - Coord_i[iDim]);
1822  }
1823 
1824  auto Gradient_i = nodes->GetGradient_Reconstruction(iPoint);
1825  auto Gradient_j = nodes->GetGradient_Reconstruction(jPoint);
1826 
1827  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVarGrad; iVar++) {
1828 
1829  su2double Project_Grad_i = 0.0;
1830  su2double Project_Grad_j = 0.0;
1831 
1832  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1833  Project_Grad_i += Vector_ij[iDim]*Gradient_i[iVar][iDim];
1834  Project_Grad_j -= Vector_ij[iDim]*Gradient_j[iVar][iDim];
1835  }
1836 
1837  su2double lim_i = 1.0;
1838  su2double lim_j = 1.0;
1839 
1840  if (van_albada) {
1841  su2double V_ij = V_j[iVar] - V_i[iVar];
1842  lim_i = LimiterHelpers<>::vanAlbadaFunction(Project_Grad_i, V_ij, EPS);
1843  lim_j = LimiterHelpers<>::vanAlbadaFunction(-Project_Grad_j, V_ij, EPS);
1844  }
1845  else if (limiter) {
1846  lim_i = nodes->GetLimiter_Primitive(iPoint, iVar);
1847  lim_j = nodes->GetLimiter_Primitive(jPoint, iVar);
1848  }
1849 
1850  Primitive_i[iVar] = V_i[iVar] + lim_i * Project_Grad_i;
1851  Primitive_j[iVar] = V_j[iVar] + lim_j * Project_Grad_j;
1852 
1853  }
1854 
1855  /*--- Recompute the reconstructed quantities in a thermodynamically consistent way. ---*/
1856 
1857  if (!ideal_gas || low_mach_corr) {
1858  ComputeConsistentExtrapolation(GetFluidModel(), nDim, Primitive_i, Secondary_i);
1859  ComputeConsistentExtrapolation(GetFluidModel(), nDim, Primitive_j, Secondary_j);
1860  }
1861 
1862  /*--- Low-Mach number correction. ---*/
1863 
1864  if (low_mach_corr) {
1865  LowMachPrimitiveCorrection(GetFluidModel(), nDim, Primitive_i, Primitive_j);
1866  }
1867 
1868  /*--- Check for non-physical solutions after reconstruction. If found, use the
1869  cell-average value of the solution. This is a locally 1st order approximation,
1870  which is typically only active during the start-up of a calculation. ---*/
1871 
1872  bool neg_pres_or_rho_i = (Primitive_i[prim_idx.Pressure()] < 0.0) || (Primitive_i[prim_idx.Density()] < 0.0);
1873  bool neg_pres_or_rho_j = (Primitive_j[prim_idx.Pressure()] < 0.0) || (Primitive_j[prim_idx.Density()] < 0.0);
1874 
1875  su2double R = sqrt(fabs(Primitive_j[prim_idx.Density()]/Primitive_i[prim_idx.Density()]));
1876  su2double sq_vel = 0.0;
1877  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1878  su2double RoeVelocity = (R * Primitive_j[iDim + prim_idx.Velocity()] +
1879  Primitive_i[iDim + prim_idx.Velocity()]) / (R+1);
1880  sq_vel += pow(RoeVelocity, 2);
1881  }
1882  su2double RoeEnthalpy = (R * Primitive_j[prim_idx.Enthalpy()] + Primitive_i[prim_idx.Enthalpy()]) / (R+1);
1883 
1884  const bool neg_sound_speed = ((Gamma-1)*(RoeEnthalpy-0.5*sq_vel) < 0.0);
1885  bool bad_recon = neg_sound_speed || neg_pres_or_rho_i || neg_pres_or_rho_j;
1886  bad_recon = nodes->UpdateNonPhysicalEdgeCounter(iEdge, bad_recon);
1887  counter_local += bad_recon;
1888 
1889  numerics->SetPrimitive(bad_recon? V_i : Primitive_i, bad_recon? V_j : Primitive_j);
1890  numerics->SetSecondary(bad_recon? S_i : Secondary_i, bad_recon? S_j : Secondary_j);
1891 
1892  }
1893 
1894  /*--- Roe Low Dissipation Scheme ---*/
1895 
1896  if (kind_dissipation != NO_ROELOWDISS) {
1897 
1898  numerics->SetDissipation(nodes->GetRoe_Dissipation(iPoint),
1899  nodes->GetRoe_Dissipation(jPoint));
1900 
1901  if (kind_dissipation == FD_DUCROS || kind_dissipation == NTS_DUCROS){
1902  numerics->SetSensor(nodes->GetSensor(iPoint),
1903  nodes->GetSensor(jPoint));
1904  }
1905  if (kind_dissipation == NTS || kind_dissipation == NTS_DUCROS){
1906  numerics->SetCoord(Coord_i, Coord_j);
1907  }
1908  }
1909 
1910  /*--- Compute the residual ---*/
1911 
1912  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
1913 
1914  /*--- Set the final value of the Roe dissipation coefficient ---*/
1915 
1916  if ((kind_dissipation != NO_ROELOWDISS) && (MGLevel != MESH_0)) {
1917  nodes->SetRoe_Dissipation(iPoint,numerics->GetDissipation());
1918  nodes->SetRoe_Dissipation(jPoint,numerics->GetDissipation());
1919  }
1920 
1921  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
1922 
1923  if (ReducerStrategy) {
1924  EdgeFluxes.SetBlock(iEdge, residual);
1925  if (implicit)
1926  Jacobian.SetBlocks(iEdge, residual.jacobian_i, residual.jacobian_j);
1927  }
1928  else {
1929  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
1930  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(jPoint, residual);
1931 
1932  /*--- Set implicit computation ---*/
1933  if (implicit)
1934  Jacobian.UpdateBlocks(iEdge, iPoint, jPoint, residual.jacobian_i, residual.jacobian_j);
1935  }
1936 
1937  /*--- Viscous contribution. ---*/
1938 
1939  Viscous_Residual(iEdge, geometry, solver_container,
1940  numerics_container[VISC_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS], config);
1941  }
1942  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
1943  } // end color loop
1944 
1945  FinalizeResidualComputation(geometry, pausePreacc, counter_local, config);
1946 }
1947 
1948 void CEulerSolver::ComputeConsistentExtrapolation(CFluidModel *fluidModel, unsigned short nDim,
1949  su2double *primitive, su2double *secondary) {
1950  const CEulerVariable::CIndices<unsigned short> prim_idx(nDim, 0);
1951  const su2double density = primitive[prim_idx.Density()];
1952  const su2double pressure = primitive[prim_idx.Pressure()];
1953  const su2double velocity2 = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(nDim, &primitive[prim_idx.Velocity()]);
1954 
1955  fluidModel->SetTDState_Prho(pressure, density);
1956 
1957  primitive[prim_idx.Temperature()] = fluidModel->GetTemperature();
1958  primitive[prim_idx.Enthalpy()] = fluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + pressure / density + 0.5*velocity2;
1959  primitive[prim_idx.SoundSpeed()] = fluidModel->GetSoundSpeed();
1960  secondary[0] = fluidModel->GetdPdrho_e();
1961  secondary[1] = fluidModel->GetdPde_rho();
1962 
1963 }
1964 
1965 void CEulerSolver::LowMachPrimitiveCorrection(CFluidModel *fluidModel, unsigned short nDim,
1966  su2double *primitive_i, su2double *primitive_j) {
1967  unsigned short iDim;
1968 
1969  su2double velocity2_i = 0.0;
1970  su2double velocity2_j = 0.0;
1971 
1972  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1973  velocity2_i += pow(primitive_i[iDim+1], 2);
1974  velocity2_j += pow(primitive_j[iDim+1], 2);
1975  }
1976  su2double mach_i = sqrt(velocity2_i)/primitive_i[nDim+4];
1977  su2double mach_j = sqrt(velocity2_j)/primitive_j[nDim+4];
1978 
1979  su2double z = min(max(mach_i,mach_j),1.0);
1980  velocity2_i = 0.0;
1981  velocity2_j = 0.0;
1982  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
1983  su2double vel_i_corr = ( primitive_i[iDim+1] + primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0
1984  + z * ( primitive_i[iDim+1] - primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0;
1985  su2double vel_j_corr = ( primitive_i[iDim+1] + primitive_j[iDim+1] )/2.0
1986  + z * ( primitive_j[iDim+1] - primitive_i[iDim+1] )/2.0;
1987 
1988  velocity2_i += pow(vel_i_corr, 2);
1989  velocity2_j += pow(vel_j_corr, 2);
1990 
1991  primitive_i[iDim+1] = vel_i_corr;
1992  primitive_j[iDim+1] = vel_j_corr;
1993  }
1994 
1995  fluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(primitive_i[nDim+1], primitive_i[nDim+2]);
1996  primitive_i[nDim+3]= fluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + primitive_i[nDim+1]/primitive_i[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_i;
1997 
1998  fluidModel->SetEnergy_Prho(primitive_j[nDim+1], primitive_j[nDim+2]);
1999  primitive_j[nDim+3]= fluidModel->GetStaticEnergy() + primitive_j[nDim+1]/primitive_j[nDim+2] + 0.5*velocity2_j;
2000 
2001 }
2002 
2003 void CEulerSolver::Source_Residual(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
2004  CNumerics **numerics_container, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh) {
2005 
2006  const bool implicit = config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT;
2007  const bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
2008  const bool rotating_frame = config->GetRotating_Frame();
2009  const bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
2010  const bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce() == YES);
2011  const bool harmonic_balance = (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::HARMONIC_BALANCE);
2012  const bool windgust = config->GetWind_Gust();
2013  const bool body_force = config->GetBody_Force();
2014  const bool vorticity_confinement = config->GetVorticityConfinement();
2015  const bool ideal_gas = (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == STANDARD_AIR) ||
2016  (config->GetKind_FluidModel() == IDEAL_GAS);
2017  const bool rans = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
2018 
2019  /*--- Pick one numerics object per thread. ---*/
2020  CNumerics* numerics = numerics_container[SOURCE_FIRST_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS];
2021 
2022  unsigned short iVar;
2023  unsigned long iPoint;
2024 
2025  if (body_force) {
2026 
2027  /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
2028  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2029  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2030  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2031 
2032  /*--- Load the conservative variables ---*/
2033  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint),
2034  nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2035 
2036  /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
2037  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2038 
2039  /*--- Compute the rotating frame source residual ---*/
2040  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2041 
2042  /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
2043  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2044 
2045  }
2046  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2047  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2048  }
2049 
2050  if (rotating_frame) {
2051 
2052  /*--- Include the residual contribution from GCL due to the static
2053  mesh movement that is set for rotating frame. ---*/
2054 
2055  SetRotatingFrame_GCL(geometry, config);
2056 
2057  /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
2058  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2059  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2060  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2061 
2062  /*--- Load the conservative variables ---*/
2063  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint),
2064  nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2065 
2066  /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
2067  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2068 
2069  /*--- Compute the rotating frame source residual ---*/
2070  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2071 
2072  /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
2073  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2074 
2075  /*--- Add the implicit Jacobian contribution ---*/
2076  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
2077 
2078  }
2079  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2080  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2081  }
2082 
2083  if (axisymmetric) {
2084 
2085  /*--- For viscous problems, we need an additional gradient. ---*/
2086  if (viscous) {
2087  ComputeAxisymmetricAuxGradients(geometry, config);
2088  }
2089 
2090  /*--- loop over points ---*/
2091  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2092  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2093  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2094 
2095  /*--- Set solution ---*/
2096  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint), nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2097 
2098  /*--- Set control volume ---*/
2099  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2100 
2101  /*--- Set y coordinate ---*/
2102  numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint));
2103 
2104  /*--- Set primitive variables for viscous terms and/or generalised source ---*/
2105  if (!ideal_gas || viscous) numerics->SetPrimitive(nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint), nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint));
2106 
2107  /*--- Set secondary variables for generalised source ---*/
2108  if (!ideal_gas) numerics->SetSecondary(nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint), nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint));
2109 
2110  if (viscous) {
2111 
2112  /*--- Set gradient of primitive variables ---*/
2113  numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
2114 
2115  /*--- Set gradient of auxillary variables ---*/
2116  numerics->SetAuxVarGrad(nodes->GetAuxVarGradient(iPoint), nullptr);
2117 
2118  /*--- Set turbulence kinetic energy ---*/
2119  if (rans){
2120  CVariable* turbNodes = solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes();
2121  numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(turbNodes->GetSolution(iPoint,0), turbNodes->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
2122  }
2123  }
2124 
2125  /*--- Compute Source term Residual ---*/
2126  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2127 
2128  /*--- Add Residual ---*/
2129  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2130 
2131  /*--- Implicit part ---*/
2132  if (implicit)
2133  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
2134  }
2135  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2136 
2137  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2138  }
2139 
2140  AD::StartNoSharedReading();
2141 
2142  if (gravity) {
2143 
2144  /*--- loop over points ---*/
2145  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2146  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2147 
2148  /*--- Set solution ---*/
2149  numerics->SetConservative(nodes->GetSolution(iPoint), nodes->GetSolution(iPoint));
2150 
2151  /*--- Set control volume ---*/
2152  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2153 
2154  /*--- Compute Source term Residual ---*/
2155  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2156 
2157  /*--- Add Residual ---*/
2158  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2159 
2160  }
2161  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2162 
2163  }
2164 
2165  if (harmonic_balance) {
2166 
2167  /*--- loop over points ---*/
2168  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2169  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2170 
2171  /*--- Get control volume ---*/
2172  su2double Volume = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
2173 
2174  /*--- Get stored time spectral source term and add to residual ---*/
2175  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
2176  LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) += Volume * nodes->GetHarmonicBalance_Source(iPoint,iVar);
2177  }
2178  }
2179  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2180  }
2181 
2182  if (windgust) {
2183 
2184  /*--- Loop over all points ---*/
2185  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2186  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2187 
2188  /*--- Load the wind gust ---*/
2189  numerics->SetWindGust(nodes->GetWindGust(iPoint), nodes->GetWindGust(iPoint));
2190 
2191  /*--- Load the wind gust derivatives ---*/
2192  numerics->SetWindGustDer(nodes->GetWindGustDer(iPoint), nodes->GetWindGustDer(iPoint));
2193 
2194  /*--- Load the primitive variables ---*/
2195  numerics->SetPrimitive(nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint), nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint));
2196 
2197  /*--- Load the volume of the dual mesh cell ---*/
2198  numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2199 
2200  /*--- Compute the rotating frame source residual ---*/
2201  auto residual = numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2202 
2203  /*--- Add the source residual to the total ---*/
2204  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2205 
2206  /*--- Add the implicit Jacobian contribution ---*/
2207  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
2208 
2209  }
2210  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2211  }
2212 
2213  if (vorticity_confinement) {
2214 
2215  CNumerics* second_numerics = numerics_container[SOURCE_SECOND_TERM + omp_get_thread_num()*MAX_TERMS];
2216 
2217  /*--- calculate and set the average volume ---*/
2218  const su2double AvgVolume = config->GetDomainVolume() / geometry->GetGlobal_nPointDomain();
2219  second_numerics->SetAvgVolume(AvgVolume);
2220 
2221  /*--- set vorticity magnitude as auxilliary variable ---*/
2222  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2223  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
2224  const su2double VorticityMag = max(GeometryToolbox::Norm(3, nodes->GetVorticity(iPoint)), 1e-12);
2225  nodes->SetAuxVar(iPoint, 0, VorticityMag);
2226  }
2227  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2228 
2229  /*--- calculate the gradient of the vorticity magnitude (AuxVarGradient) ---*/
2230  SetAuxVar_Gradient_GG(geometry, config);
2231 
2232  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2233  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2234  second_numerics->SetPrimitive(nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint), nullptr);
2235  second_numerics->SetVorticity(nodes->GetVorticity(iPoint), nullptr);
2236  second_numerics->SetAuxVarGrad(nodes->GetAuxVarGradient(iPoint), nullptr);
2237  second_numerics->SetDistance(geometry->nodes->GetWall_Distance(iPoint), 0);
2238  second_numerics->SetVolume(geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint));
2239  auto residual = second_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
2240 
2241  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
2242 
2243  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
2244  }
2245  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2246 
2247  }
2248 
2249  /*--- Check if a verification solution is to be computed. ---*/
2250 
2251  if ( VerificationSolution ) {
2252  if ( VerificationSolution->IsManufacturedSolution() ) {
2253 
2254  /*--- Get the physical time. ---*/
2255  su2double time = 0.0;
2256  if (config->GetTime_Marching() != TIME_MARCHING::STEADY) time = config->GetPhysicalTime();
2257 
2258  /*--- Loop over points ---*/
2259  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2260  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; iPoint++) {
2261 
2262  /*--- Get control volume size. ---*/
2263  su2double Volume = geometry->nodes->GetVolume(iPoint);
2264 
2265  /*--- Get the current point coordinates. ---*/
2266  const su2double *coor = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
2267 
2268  /*--- Get the MMS source term. ---*/
2269  vector<su2double> sourceMan(nVar,0.0);
2270  VerificationSolution->GetMMSSourceTerm(coor, time, sourceMan.data());
2271 
2272  /*--- Compute the residual for this control volume and subtract. ---*/
2273  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
2274  LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar) -= sourceMan[iVar]*Volume;
2275  }
2276  }
2277  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2278  }
2279  }
2280 
2281  AD::EndNoSharedReading();
2282 }

2318 void CEulerSolver::SetUndivided_Laplacian(CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig *config) {
2319 
2320  /*--- Loop domain points. ---*/
2321 
2322  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(omp_chunk_size)
2323  for (unsigned long iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointDomain; ++iPoint) {
2324 
2325  const bool boundary_i = geometry->nodes->GetPhysicalBoundary(iPoint);
2326  const su2double Pressure_i = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
2327 
2328  /*--- Initialize. ---*/
2329  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
2330  nodes->SetUnd_Lapl(iPoint, iVar, 0.0);
2331 
2332  /*--- Loop over the neighbors of point i. ---*/
2333  for (auto jPoint : geometry->nodes->GetPoints(iPoint)) {
2334 
2335  bool boundary_j = geometry->nodes->GetPhysicalBoundary(jPoint);
2336 
2337  /*--- If iPoint is boundary it only takes contributions from other boundary points. ---*/
2338  if (boundary_i && !boundary_j) continue;
2339 
2340  /*--- Add solution differences, with correction for compressible flows which use the enthalpy. ---*/
2341 
2342  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
2343  nodes->AddUnd_Lapl(iPoint, iVar, nodes->GetSolution(jPoint,iVar)-nodes->GetSolution(iPoint,iVar));
2344 
2345  su2double Pressure_j = nodes->GetPressure(jPoint);
2346  nodes->AddUnd_Lapl(iPoint, nVar-1, Pressure_j-Pressure_i);
2347  }
2348  }
2349  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2350 
2351  /*--- Correct the Laplacian across any periodic boundaries. ---*/
2352 
2353  for (unsigned short iPeriodic = 1; iPeriodic <= config->GetnMarker_Periodic()/2; iPeriodic++) {
2354  InitiatePeriodicComms(geometry, config, iPeriodic, PERIODIC_LAPLACIAN);
2355  CompletePeriodicComms(geometry, config, iPeriodic, PERIODIC_LAPLACIAN);
2356  }
2357 
2358  /*--- MPI parallelization ---*/
2359 
2360  InitiateComms(geometry, config, UNDIVIDED_LAPLACIAN);
2361  CompleteComms(geometry, config, UNDIVIDED_LAPLACIAN);
2362 
2363 }

2378 void CEulerSolver::SetUpwind_Ducros_Sensor(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config){
2379 
2380  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
2381  for (unsigned long iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
2382 
2383  /*---- Ducros sensor for iPoint and its neighbor points to avoid lower dissipation near shocks. ---*/
2384 
2385  su2double Ducros_i = 0.0;
2386  const auto nNeigh = geometry->nodes->GetnPoint(iPoint);
2387 
2388  for (unsigned short iNeigh = 0; iNeigh <= nNeigh; iNeigh++) {
2389 
2390  auto jPoint = iPoint; // when iNeigh == nNeigh
2391  if (iNeigh < nNeigh) jPoint = geometry->nodes->GetPoint(iPoint, iNeigh);
2392 
2393  /*---- Dilatation for jPoint ---*/
2394 
2395  su2double uixi=0.0;
2396  for(unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
2397  uixi += nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(jPoint,iDim+1, iDim);
2398  }
2399 
2400  /*--- Compute norm of vorticity ---*/
2401 
2402  const su2double* Vorticity = nodes->GetVorticity(jPoint);
2403  su2double Omega = 0.0;
2404  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2405  Omega += pow(Vorticity[iDim], 2);
2406  }
2407  Omega = sqrt(Omega);
2408 
2409  su2double Ducros_j = 0.0;
2410 
2411  if (config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss() == FD_DUCROS) {
2412  Ducros_j = -uixi / (fabs(uixi) + Omega + 1e-20);
2413  }
2414  else if (config->GetKind_RoeLowDiss() == NTS_DUCROS) {
2415  Ducros_j = pow(uixi,2.0) /(pow(uixi,2.0)+ pow(Omega,2.0) + 1e-20);
2416  }
2417  Ducros_i = max(Ducros_i, Ducros_j);
2418  }
2419 
2420  nodes->SetSensor(iPoint, Ducros_i);
2421  }
2422  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
2423 
2424  InitiateComms(geometry, config, SENSOR);
2425  CompleteComms(geometry, config, SENSOR);
2426 
2427 }

2446 void CEulerSolver::PrepareImplicitIteration(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver**, CConfig *config) {

2448  struct LowMachPrec {
2449  const CEulerSolver* solver;
2450  const bool active;
2451  su2activematrix matrix;
2452 
2453  LowMachPrec(const CEulerSolver* s, bool a, unsigned short nVar) : solver(s), active(a) {

2455  }

2458  solver->SetPreconditioner(config, iPoint, delta, matrix);
2459  return matrix;
2460  }
2461 
2462  } precond(this, config->Low_Mach_Preconditioning() || (config->GetKind_Upwind_Flow() == UPWIND::TURKEL), nVar);

2471 
2472 void CEulerSolver::SetPreconditioner(const CConfig *config, unsigned long iPoint,
2473  su2double delta, su2activematrix& preconditioner) const {
2474 
2475  unsigned short iDim, jDim, iVar, jVar;
2476  su2double local_Mach, rho, enthalpy, soundspeed, sq_vel;
2477  su2double *U_i = nullptr;
2478  su2double Beta_max = config->GetmaxTurkelBeta();
2479  su2double Mach_infty2, Mach_lim2, aux, parameter;
2480 
2481  /*--- Variables to calculate the preconditioner parameter Beta ---*/
2482  local_Mach = sqrt(nodes->GetVelocity2(iPoint))/nodes->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
2483 
2484  /*--- Weiss and Smith Preconditioning---*/
2485  Mach_infty2 = pow(config->GetMach(),2.0);
2486  Mach_lim2 = pow(0.00001,2.0);
2487  aux = max(pow(local_Mach,2.0),Mach_lim2);
2488  parameter = min(1.0, max(aux,Beta_max*Mach_infty2));
2489 
2490  U_i = nodes->GetSolution(iPoint);
2491 
2492  rho = U_i[0];
2493  enthalpy = nodes->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
2494  soundspeed = nodes->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
2495  sq_vel = nodes->GetVelocity2(iPoint);
2496 
2497  /*---Calculating the inverse of the preconditioning matrix that multiplies the time derivative */
2498  preconditioner[0][0] = 0.5*sq_vel;
2499  preconditioner[0][nVar-1] = 1.0;
2500  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++)
2501  preconditioner[0][1+iDim] = -1.0*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2502 
2503  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++) {
2504  preconditioner[iDim+1][0] = 0.5*sq_vel*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2505  preconditioner[iDim+1][nVar-1] = U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2506  for (jDim = 0; jDim < nDim; jDim ++) {
2507  preconditioner[iDim+1][1+jDim] = -1.0*U_i[jDim+1]/rho*U_i[iDim+1]/rho;
2508  }
2509  }
2510 
2511  preconditioner[nVar-1][0] = 0.5*sq_vel*enthalpy;
2512  preconditioner[nVar-1][nVar-1] = enthalpy;
2513  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim ++)
2514  preconditioner[nVar-1][1+iDim] = -1.0*U_i[iDim+1]/rho*enthalpy;
2515 
2516 
2517  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar ++ ) {
2518  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar ++ ) {
2519  preconditioner[iVar][jVar] = (parameter - 1.0) * ((Gamma-1.0)/(soundspeed*soundspeed))*preconditioner[iVar][jVar];
2520  if (iVar == jVar)
2521  preconditioner[iVar][iVar] += 1.0;
2522 
2523  preconditioner[iVar][jVar] *= delta;
2524  }
2525  }
2526 
2527 }
2528 
2529 void CEulerSolver::GetPower_Properties(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
2530 
2531  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, jMarker;
2532  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
2533  su2double *V_inlet = nullptr, *V_outlet = nullptr, Pressure, Temperature, Velocity[3], Vn,
2534  Velocity2, Density, Area, SoundSpeed, TotalPressure, Vel_Infty2, RamDrag,
2535  TotalTemperature, VelocityJet,
2536  Vel_Infty, MaxPressure, MinPressure, MFR, InfVel2;

2538  string Inlet_TagBound, Outlet_TagBound;
2539  su2double DeltaPress = 0.0, DeltaTemp = 0.0, TotalPressRatio = 0.0, TotalTempRatio = 0.0, StaticPressRatio = 0.0, StaticTempRatio = 0.0,
2540  NetThrust = 0.0, GrossThrust = 0.0, Power = 0.0, MassFlow = 0.0, Mach = 0.0, Force = 0.0;

2545  su2double Cp = Gas_Constant*Gamma / (Gamma-1.0);

2556  else { nMarker_Inlet = config->GetnMarker_ActDiskInlet(); nMarker_Outlet = config->GetnMarker_ActDiskOutlet(); }
2557 
2558  /*--- Evaluate the MPI for the actuator disk IO ---*/
2559 
2560  if (Evaluate_BC) {
2561 
2562  su2double *Inlet_MassFlow = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2563  su2double *Inlet_ReverseMassFlow = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();

2567  su2double *Inlet_MinPressure = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();

2569  su2double *Inlet_Temperature = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();

2578

2584  su2double *Outlet_Area = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();

2587  su2double *Outlet_Power = new su2double [config->GetnMarker_All()]();
2588 
2589  /*--- Comute MassFlow, average temp, press, etc. ---*/
2590 
2591  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
2592 
2593  MinPressure = +1E10; MaxPressure = -1E10;
2594 
2595  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
2596  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW)) {
2597 
2598  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2599 
2600  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2601 
2602  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2603 
2604  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
2605 
2606  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
2607 
2608  Temperature = V_inlet[0];
2609  Pressure = V_inlet[nDim+1];
2610 
2611  Density = V_inlet[nDim+2];
2612  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
2613 
2614  Velocity2 = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0; Vel_Infty2 =0.0;
2615  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2616  Velocity[iDim] = V_inlet[iDim+1];
2617  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
2618  Vel_Infty2 += GetVelocity_Inf(iDim)*GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
2619  MassFlow -= Vector[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]*Density;
2620  }
2621 
2622  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Vector);
2623  Vn = 0.0; ReverseFlow = false;
2624  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) { Vn -= Velocity[iDim]*Vector[iDim]/Area; }
2625  if (Vn < 0.0) { ReverseFlow = true; }
2626 
2627  Vel_Infty = sqrt (Vel_Infty2);
2628  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
2629  TotalPressure = Pressure * pow( 1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
2630  TotalTemperature = Temperature * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
2631  MinPressure = min(MinPressure, TotalPressure);
2632  MaxPressure = max(MaxPressure, TotalPressure);
2633 
2634  RamDrag = MassFlow * Vel_Infty;
2635 
2636  Inlet_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
2637  Inlet_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*MassFlow;
2638  Inlet_Mach[iMarker] += Mach*MassFlow;
2639  Inlet_MinPressure[iMarker] = min (MinPressure, Inlet_MinPressure[iMarker]);
2640  Inlet_MaxPressure[iMarker] = max(MaxPressure, Inlet_MaxPressure[iMarker]);
2641  Inlet_TotalPressure[iMarker] += TotalPressure*MassFlow;
2642  Inlet_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*MassFlow;
2643  Inlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker] += TotalTemperature*MassFlow;
2644  Inlet_Area[iMarker] += Area;
2645  Inlet_RamDrag[iMarker] += RamDrag;
2646  Inlet_Power[iMarker] += MassFlow*Cp*TotalTemperature;
2647  if (ReverseFlow) Inlet_ReverseMassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
2648 
2649  su2double Inlet_ForceX = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[0] + MassFlow*Velocity[0];
2650  su2double Inlet_ForceY = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[1] + MassFlow*Velocity[1];
2651  su2double Inlet_ForceZ = 0.0;
2652  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ForceZ = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[2] + MassFlow*Velocity[2];
2653  Inlet_Force[iMarker] += Inlet_ForceX*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta) + Inlet_ForceY*sin(Beta) +Inlet_ForceZ*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta);
2654 
2655  Inlet_XCG[iMarker] += geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 0)*Area;
2656  Inlet_YCG[iMarker] += geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1)*Area;
2657  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG[iMarker] += geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 2)*Area;
2658 
2659  }
2660  }
2661 
2662  }
2663 
2664  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) ||
2665  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST)) {
2666 
2667  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
2668 
2669  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
2670 
2671  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
2672 
2673  V_outlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
2674 
2675  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
2676 
2677  Temperature = V_outlet[0];
2678  Pressure = V_outlet[nDim+1];
2679 
2680  Density = V_outlet[nDim+2];
2681  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
2682 
2683  Velocity2 = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0; Vel_Infty2 = 0.0;
2684  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
2685  Velocity[iDim] = V_outlet[iDim+1];
2686  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
2687  Vel_Infty2 += GetVelocity_Inf(iDim)*GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
2688  MassFlow += Vector[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]*Density;
2689  }
2690 
2691  Vel_Infty = sqrt (Vel_Infty2);
2692  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Vector);
2693  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
2694  TotalPressure = Pressure * pow( 1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
2695  TotalTemperature = Temperature * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
2696  VelocityJet = sqrt(Velocity2) ;
2697 
2698  GrossThrust = MassFlow * VelocityJet;
2699 
2700  Outlet_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
2701  Outlet_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*MassFlow;
2702  Outlet_TotalPressure[iMarker] += TotalPressure*MassFlow;
2703  Outlet_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*MassFlow;
2704  Outlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker] += TotalTemperature*MassFlow;
2705  Outlet_Area[iMarker] += Area;
2706  Outlet_GrossThrust[iMarker] += GrossThrust;
2707  Outlet_Power[iMarker] += MassFlow*Cp*TotalTemperature;
2708 
2709  su2double Outlet_ForceX = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[0] -MassFlow*Velocity[0];
2710  su2double Outlet_ForceY = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[1] -MassFlow*Velocity[1];
2711  su2double Outlet_ForceZ = 0.0;
2712  if (nDim == 3) Outlet_ForceZ = -(Pressure - Pressure_Inf)*Vector[2] -MassFlow*Velocity[2];
2713 
2714  if (nDim == 2) Outlet_Force[iMarker] += Outlet_ForceX*cos(Alpha) + Outlet_ForceY*sin(Alpha);
2715  if (nDim == 3) Outlet_Force[iMarker] += Outlet_ForceX*cos(Alpha)*cos(Beta) + Outlet_ForceY*sin(Beta) + Outlet_ForceZ*sin(Alpha)*cos(Beta);
2716 
2717  }
2718  }
2719 
2720  }
2721 
2722  }
2723 
2724  /*--- Copy to the appropriate structure ---*/
2725 
2726  su2double *Inlet_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2727  su2double *Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2728  su2double *Inlet_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2729  su2double *Inlet_TotalTemperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2730  su2double *Inlet_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2731  su2double *Inlet_Mach_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2732  su2double *Inlet_MinPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2733  su2double *Inlet_MaxPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2734  su2double *Inlet_Power_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2735  su2double *Inlet_TotalPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2736  su2double *Inlet_RamDrag_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2737  su2double *Inlet_Force_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2738  su2double *Inlet_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2739  su2double *Inlet_XCG_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2740  su2double *Inlet_YCG_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2741  su2double *Inlet_ZCG_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2742 
2743  su2double *Inlet_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2744  su2double *Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2745  su2double *Inlet_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2746  su2double *Inlet_Mach_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2747  su2double *Inlet_MinPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2748  su2double *Inlet_MaxPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2749  su2double *Inlet_Power_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2750  su2double *Inlet_TotalPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2751  su2double *Inlet_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2752  su2double *Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2753  su2double *Inlet_RamDrag_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2754  su2double *Inlet_Force_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2755  su2double *Inlet_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2756  su2double *Inlet_XCG_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2757  su2double *Inlet_YCG_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2758  su2double *Inlet_ZCG_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Inlet]();
2759 
2760  su2double *Outlet_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2761  su2double *Outlet_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2762  su2double *Outlet_TotalPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2763  su2double *Outlet_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2764  su2double *Outlet_TotalTemperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2765  su2double *Outlet_GrossThrust_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2766  su2double *Outlet_Force_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2767  su2double *Outlet_Power_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2768  su2double *Outlet_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2769 
2770  su2double *Outlet_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2771  su2double *Outlet_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2772  su2double *Outlet_TotalPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2773  su2double *Outlet_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2774  su2double *Outlet_TotalTemperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2775  su2double *Outlet_GrossThrust_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2776  su2double *Outlet_Force_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2777  su2double *Outlet_Power_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2778  su2double *Outlet_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Outlet]();
2779 
2780  /*--- Copy the values to the local array for MPI ---*/
2781 
2782  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
2783 
2784  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) || (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW)) {
2785  for (iMarker_Inlet = 0; iMarker_Inlet < nMarker_Inlet; iMarker_Inlet++) {
2786 
2787  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) Inlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_ActDiskInlet_TagBound(iMarker_Inlet);
2788  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW) Inlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_EngineInflow_TagBound(iMarker_Inlet);
2789 
2790  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == Inlet_TagBound) {
2791  Inlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_MassFlow[iMarker];
2792  Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_ReverseMassFlow[iMarker];
2793  Inlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Pressure[iMarker];
2794  Inlet_Mach_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Mach[iMarker];
2795  Inlet_MinPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_MinPressure[iMarker];
2796  Inlet_MaxPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_MaxPressure[iMarker];
2797  Inlet_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_TotalPressure[iMarker];
2798  Inlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Temperature[iMarker];
2799  Inlet_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker];
2800  Inlet_RamDrag_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_RamDrag[iMarker];
2801  Inlet_Force_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Force[iMarker];
2802  Inlet_Power_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Power[iMarker];
2803  Inlet_Area_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_Area[iMarker];
2804  Inlet_XCG_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_XCG[iMarker];
2805  Inlet_YCG_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_YCG[iMarker];
2806  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG_Local[iMarker_Inlet] += Inlet_ZCG[iMarker];
2807  }
2808 
2809  }
2810  }
2811 
2812  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) || (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST)) {
2813  for (iMarker_Outlet= 0; iMarker_Outlet < nMarker_Outlet; iMarker_Outlet++) {
2814 
2815  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET) Outlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_ActDiskOutlet_TagBound(iMarker_Outlet);
2816  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_EXHAUST) Outlet_TagBound = config->GetMarker_EngineExhaust_TagBound(iMarker_Outlet);
2817 
2818  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == Outlet_TagBound) {
2819  Outlet_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_MassFlow[iMarker];
2820  Outlet_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Pressure[iMarker];
2821  Outlet_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_TotalPressure[iMarker];
2822  Outlet_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Temperature[iMarker];
2823  Outlet_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_TotalTemperature[iMarker];
2824  Outlet_GrossThrust_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_GrossThrust[iMarker];
2825  Outlet_Force_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Force[iMarker];
2826  Outlet_Power_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Power[iMarker];
2827  Outlet_Area_Local[iMarker_Outlet] += Outlet_Area[iMarker];
2828  }
2829 
2830  }
2831  }
2832 
2833  }
2834 
2835  /*--- Correct the min max values for the MPI ---*/
2836 
2837  bool ActDisk = false;
2838  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
2839  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
2840  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ENGINE_INFLOW)) { ActDisk = true; break; }
2841  }
2842 
2843  if (!ActDisk) {
2844  for (iMarker_Inlet = 0; iMarker_Inlet < nMarker_Inlet; iMarker_Inlet++) {
2845  Inlet_MinPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] = 1E10;
2846  Inlet_MaxPressure_Local[iMarker_Inlet] = -1E10;
2847  }
2848  }
2849 
2850  /*--- All the ranks to compute the total value ---*/
2851 
2852  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_MassFlow_Local, Inlet_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2853  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Local, Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2854  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Pressure_Local, Inlet_Pressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2855  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Mach_Local, Inlet_Mach_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2856  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_MinPressure_Local, Inlet_MinPressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MIN, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2857  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_MaxPressure_Local, Inlet_MaxPressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MAX, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2858  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_TotalPressure_Local, Inlet_TotalPressure_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2859  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Temperature_Local, Inlet_Temperature_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2860  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_TotalTemperature_Local, Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2861  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_RamDrag_Local, Inlet_RamDrag_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2862  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Force_Local, Inlet_Force_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2863  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Power_Local, Inlet_Power_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2864  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_Area_Local, Inlet_Area_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2865  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_XCG_Local, Inlet_XCG_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2866  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_YCG_Local, Inlet_YCG_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2867  if (nDim == 3) SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Inlet_ZCG_Local, Inlet_ZCG_Total, nMarker_Inlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2868 
2869  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_MassFlow_Local, Outlet_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2870  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Pressure_Local, Outlet_Pressure_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2871  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_TotalPressure_Local, Outlet_TotalPressure_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2872  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Temperature_Local, Outlet_Temperature_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2873  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_TotalTemperature_Local, Outlet_TotalTemperature_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2874  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_GrossThrust_Local, Outlet_GrossThrust_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2875  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Force_Local, Outlet_Force_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2876  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Power_Local, Outlet_Power_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2877  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Outlet_Area_Local, Outlet_Area_Total, nMarker_Outlet, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2878 
2879  /*--- Compute the value of the average surface temperature and pressure and
2880  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
2881 
2882  for (iMarker_Inlet = 0; iMarker_Inlet < nMarker_Inlet; iMarker_Inlet++) {
2883  if (Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet] != 0.0) {
2884  Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2885  Inlet_Mach_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2886  Inlet_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2887  Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2888  Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2889  Inlet_XCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2890  Inlet_YCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2891  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] /= Inlet_Area_Total[iMarker_Inlet];
2892  }
2893  else {
2894  Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2895  Inlet_Mach_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2896  Inlet_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2897  Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2898  Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2899  Inlet_XCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2900  Inlet_YCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2901  if (nDim == 3) Inlet_ZCG_Total[iMarker_Inlet] = 0.0;
2902  }
2903 
2904  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
2905 
2906  if (Engine) {
2907  config->SetInflow_MassFlow(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2908  config->SetInflow_ReverseMassFlow(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2909  config->SetInflow_Pressure(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2910  config->SetInflow_TotalPressure(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2911  config->SetInflow_Temperature(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2912  config->SetInflow_TotalTemperature(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2913  config->SetInflow_RamDrag(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_RamDrag_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2914  config->SetInflow_Force(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Force_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2915  config->SetInflow_Power(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Power_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2916  }
2917  else {
2918  config->SetActDiskInlet_MassFlow(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2919  config->SetActDiskInlet_ReverseMassFlow(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_ReverseMassFlow_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2920  config->SetActDiskInlet_Pressure(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2921  config->SetActDiskInlet_TotalPressure(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2922  config->SetActDiskInlet_Temperature(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2923  config->SetActDiskInlet_TotalTemperature(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2924  config->SetActDiskInlet_RamDrag(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_RamDrag_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2925  config->SetActDiskInlet_Force(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Force_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2926  config->SetActDiskInlet_Power(iMarker_Inlet, Inlet_Power_Total[iMarker_Inlet]);
2927  }
2928 
2929  }
2930

3110  su2double Factor = (0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);

3312  cout << setprecision(5) << -NetThrust * Ref << ". Net CT: " << CT;
3313 
3314  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) {
3315  cout << ". Power (W): ";
3316  cout << setprecision(1) << Power * Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() << "." << endl;
3317  }
3318  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
3319  cout << ". Power (HP): ";
3320  cout << setprecision(1) << Power * Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() / 550.0 << "." << endl;
3321  }
3322 
3323  }
3324 
3325  }
3326 
3327  if (write_heads && Output && !config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()) cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl << endl;
3328 
3329  }
3330 
3331  }
