3417 
3418 void CEulerSolver::SetActDisk_BCThrust(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
3419  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
3420 
3421  su2double Massflow = 0.0 , Target_Massflow = 0.0, DragMinusThrust = 0.0 ,
3422  Target_DragMinusThrust = 0.0, Target_NetThrust = 0.0, BCThrust = 0.0, BCThrust_inc = 0.0;
3423  unsigned short iDim, iMarker;
3424  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
3425  su2double *V_inlet = nullptr, Pressure,
3426  Density, T0_Ti, ATerm, BTerm, LHS, RHS, RHS_PDelta, RHS_MDelta, F, DF_DLa, CTerm_, DTerm_,
3427  ETerm, La, La_old, TotalArea, To_Ti, DeltaT, Po_Pi, DeltaP, Area, Velocity_Normal,
3428  SoundSpeed2, Force_Normal,
3429  RefDensity, RefArea, RefVel2, Factor, Ref;
3430  unsigned short iter;
3431  string Marker_Tag;
3432  su2double Target_Force, Force, Target_Power, Power, NetThrust, BCThrust_old, Initial_BCThrust;
3433  bool ActDisk_Info;
3434  su2double MyBCThrust, BCThrust_Init;
3435  su2double Vector[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
3436 
3437  su2double dNetThrust_dBCThrust = config->GetdNetThrust_dBCThrust();
3438  unsigned short Kind_ActDisk = config->GetKind_ActDisk();
3439  bool ratio = (config->GetActDisk_Jump() == RATIO);
3440  unsigned long Update_BCThrust = config->GetUpdate_BCThrust();
3441  unsigned long Iter_Fixed_NetThrust = config->GetIter_Fixed_NetThrust();
3442  unsigned long InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
3443  bool Update_BCThrust_Bool = false;
3444  bool restart = (config->GetRestart() || config->GetRestart_Flow());
3445  su2double Fan_Poly_Eff = config->GetFan_Poly_Eff();
3446  su2double PolyCoeff = 1.0/(1.0-((Gamma-1.0)/Gamma)/Fan_Poly_Eff);
3447 
3448  RefDensity = Density_Inf;
3449  RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
3450  RefVel2 = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
3451 
3452  Factor = (0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);
3453  Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * 1.0 * 1.0;
3454 
3455  /*--- Variable load distribution is in input file. ---*/
3456  if (Kind_ActDisk == VARIABLE_LOAD) {
3457  if(InnerIter == 0) {
3458  ReadActDisk_InputFile(geometry, solver_container, config, iMesh, Output);
3459  }
3460  }
3461  /*--- Delta P and delta T are inputs ---*/
3462 
3463  else if (Kind_ActDisk == VARIABLES_JUMP) {
3464 
3465  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3466 
3467  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3468  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3469 
3470  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3471 
3472  if (ratio) {
3473  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) {
3474  DeltaP = config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0);
3475  DeltaT = config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 0);
3476  }
3477  else {
3478  DeltaP = config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1);
3479  DeltaT = config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 1);
3480  }
3481  }
3482  else {
3483  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) {
3484  DeltaP = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / config->GetPressure_Ref());
3485  DeltaT = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / config->GetTemperature_Ref());
3486  }
3487  else {
3488  DeltaP = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / config->GetPressure_Ref());
3489  DeltaT = max(0.0, config->GetActDisk_TempJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / config->GetTemperature_Ref());
3490  }
3491  }
3492 
3493  /*--- Set the Delta P, Delta T values at each discrete point (uniform distribution) ---*/
3494 
3495  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
3496  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3497  ActDisk_DeltaP[iMarker][iVertex] = DeltaP;
3498  ActDisk_DeltaT[iMarker][iVertex] = DeltaT;
3499  }
3500  }
3501  }
3502  }
3503 
3504  /*--- Iteration using BCThrust ---*/
3505 
3506  else {
3507 
3508  if (InnerIter == 0) BCThrust_Counter = 0;
3509 
3510  /*--- Only the fine mesh level should check the convergence criteria ---*/
3511 
3512  if ((iMesh == MESH_0) && Output) {
3513 
3514  /*--- Initialize the update flag to false ---*/
3515 
3516  Update_BCThrust_Bool = false;
3517 
3518  /*--- Reevaluate BCThrust at a fix number of iterations ---*/
3519 
3520  if ((InnerIter % Iter_Fixed_NetThrust == 0) && (InnerIter != 0)) {
3521  BCThrust_Counter++;
3522  if ((BCThrust_Counter != 0) &&
3523  (BCThrust_Counter != 1) &&
3524  (BCThrust_Counter != Update_BCThrust) &&
3525  (BCThrust_Counter != Update_BCThrust + 2) &&
3526  (BCThrust_Counter != Update_BCThrust + 4) ) Update_BCThrust_Bool = true;
3527  else Update_BCThrust_Bool = false;
3528  }
3529 
3530  /*--- Store the update boolean for use on other mesh levels in the MG ---*/
3531 
3532  config->SetUpdate_BCThrust_Bool(Update_BCThrust_Bool);
3533 
3534  }
3535 
3536  else {
3537  Update_BCThrust_Bool = config->GetUpdate_BCThrust_Bool();
3538  }
3539 
3540 
3541  /*--- If it is the first iteration, set the BCThrust to a meaning full target value,
3542  * this can be done at an initialization level, for the time being it is OK here ---*/
3543 
3544  if (InnerIter == 0) {
3545  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3546  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3547  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3548  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3549 
3550  if (Kind_ActDisk == NET_THRUST) {
3551  if (restart)
3552  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3553  else {
3554  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3555  else Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3556  }
3557  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3558  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3559  }
3560 
3561  if (Kind_ActDisk == BC_THRUST) {
3562  if (restart)
3563  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3564  else {
3565  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3566  else Initial_BCThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3567  }
3568  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3569  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3570  }
3571 
3572  if (Kind_ActDisk == POWER) {
3573  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3574  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3575  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3576  }
3577 
3578  if (Kind_ActDisk == DRAG_MINUS_THRUST) {
3579  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3580  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3581  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3582  }
3583 
3584  if (Kind_ActDisk == MASSFLOW) {
3585  Initial_BCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust() / Ref;
3586  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3587  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, Initial_BCThrust);
3588  }
3589 
3590  }
3591  }
3592  }
3593 
3594  /*--- Typical iteration to set the value of BC Thrust at each actuator disk ---*/
3595 
3596  if (Update_BCThrust_Bool && Output) {
3597 
3598  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3599 
3600  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3601  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3602 
3603  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3604 
3605  if (Kind_ActDisk == NET_THRUST) {
3606 
3607  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_NetThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3608  else Target_NetThrust = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3609  NetThrust = config->GetActDisk_NetThrust(Marker_Tag);
3610  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3611  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_NetThrust - NetThrust);
3612 
3613  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3614  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3615 
3616  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3617  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3618  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3619  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3620  }
3621 
3622  }
3623 
3624  if (Kind_ActDisk == BC_THRUST) {
3625 
3626  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_Force = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / Ref);
3627  else Target_Force = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / Ref);
3628  Force = -config->GetActDisk_Force(Marker_Tag);
3629  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3630  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_Force - Force);
3631 
3632  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3633  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3634 
3635  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3636  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3637  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3638  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3639  }
3640 
3641  }
3642 
3643  if (Kind_ActDisk == POWER) {
3644 
3645  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_Power = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / (Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() / 550.0));
3646  else Target_Power = fabs( config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / (Ref * config->GetVelocity_Ref() / 550.0));
3647  Power = config->GetActDisk_Power(Marker_Tag);
3648  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3649  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_Power - Power);
3650 
3651  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3652  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3653 
3654  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3655  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3656  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3657  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3658  }
3659 
3660  }
3661 
3662  if (Kind_ActDisk == DRAG_MINUS_THRUST) {
3663 
3664  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) Target_DragMinusThrust = -fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0)) * Factor;
3665  else Target_DragMinusThrust = -fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1)) * Factor;
3666  DragMinusThrust = GetTotal_CD() * Factor;
3667  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3668  BCThrust_inc = -(1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_DragMinusThrust - DragMinusThrust);
3669 
3670  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3671  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3672 
3673  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3674  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3675  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3676  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3677  }
3678 
3679  }
3680 
3681  if (Kind_ActDisk == MASSFLOW) {
3682 
3683  if (config->GetMach() < 0.5) {
3684  Target_Massflow = fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 0) / (config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref()));
3685  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Target_Massflow /= 32.174;
3686  }
3687  else {
3688  Target_Massflow = fabs(config->GetActDisk_PressJump(Marker_Tag, 1) / (config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref()));
3689  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Target_Massflow /= 32.174;
3690  }
3691 
3692  Massflow = config->GetActDisk_MassFlow(Marker_Tag);
3693  BCThrust_old = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag);
3694  BCThrust_inc = (1.0/dNetThrust_dBCThrust)*(Target_Massflow - Massflow);
3695  if (iMesh == MESH_0) BCThrust = max(0.0,(BCThrust_old + BCThrust_inc));
3696  else BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3697  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
3698  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3699  BCThrust_Init = BCThrust*Ref;
3700  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust_Init);
3701  }
3702 
3703  }
3704 
3705  }
3706 
3707  }
3708 
3709  /*--- After a complete update of BC_Thrust
3710  update the value of BC Thrust (old) for future iterations ---*/
3711 
3712  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3713  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3714  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3715  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3716  if ((Kind_ActDisk == NET_THRUST) || (Kind_ActDisk == BC_THRUST) ||
3717  (Kind_ActDisk == POWER) || (Kind_ActDisk == DRAG_MINUS_THRUST) ||
3718  (Kind_ActDisk == MASSFLOW)) {
3719  BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3720  config->SetActDisk_BCThrust_Old(Marker_Tag, BCThrust);
3721  }
3722  }
3723  }
3724  }
3725 
3726  /*--- Evaluate the pressure jump at each node using the total thrust ---*/
3727 
3728  if ((Update_BCThrust_Bool && Output) || (InnerIter == 0)) {
3729 
3730  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3731 
3732  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3733  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3734 
3735  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3736  RefDensity = Density_Inf;
3737  RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
3738  RefVel2 = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
3739 
3740  Factor = (0.5*RefDensity*RefArea*RefVel2);
3741  Ref = config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref() * 1.0 * 1.0;
3742  BCThrust = config->GetActDisk_BCThrust(Marker_Tag);
3743 
3744  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
3745 
3746  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
3747 
3748  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
3749 
3750  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
3751 
3752  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) {
3753  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) { Vector[iDim] = -Vector[iDim]; }
3754  }
3755 
3756  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Vector);
3757 
3758  /*--- Use the inlet state to compute the Pressure and Temperature jumps ---*/
3759 
3760  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET)
3761  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
3762  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)
3763  V_inlet = DonorPrimVar[iMarker][iVertex];
3764 
3765  Density = V_inlet[nDim+2];
3766  Pressure = V_inlet[nDim+1];
3767  SoundSpeed2 = Pressure*Gamma/Density;
3768  TotalArea = config->GetActDisk_Area(Marker_Tag);
3769  Force_Normal = Area*(BCThrust/TotalArea);
3770 
3771 
3772  Velocity_Normal = 0.0;
3773  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
3774  Velocity_Normal += V_inlet[iDim+1]*Vector[iDim]/Area;
3775  }
3776 
3777 
3778  if (Velocity_Normal > EPS) {
3779 
3780  /*--- Ratio of the total temperature to the temperature at the inflow ---*/
3781 
3782  T0_Ti = 1.0 + ((Gamma-1.0)/SoundSpeed2)*(0.5*Velocity_Normal*Velocity_Normal + Force_Normal/(Density*Area));
3783 
3784 
3785  ATerm = 2.0*T0_Ti/(Gamma+1.0);
3786  BTerm = 0.5*(Gamma+1.0)/(Gamma-1.0);
3787  LHS = fabs(Velocity_Normal)/(sqrt(SoundSpeed2)*pow(ATerm,BTerm));
3788 
3789  CTerm_ = (PolyCoeff-1.0)/(PolyCoeff+1.0);
3790  DTerm_ = 1.0/(PolyCoeff-1.0);
3791 
3792  La = EPS; La_old = EPS;
3793 
3794  for (iter = 0; iter < 100; iter++) {
3795 
3796  ETerm = ((1.0-CTerm_*La*La)/(1.0-CTerm_+EPS));
3797 
3798  RHS = La*pow(ETerm, DTerm_);
3799 
3800  ETerm = ((1.0-CTerm_*(La+1E-6)*(La+1E-6))/(1.0-CTerm_+EPS));
3801  RHS_PDelta = (La+1E-6)*pow(ETerm, DTerm_);
3802 
3803  ETerm = ((1.0-CTerm_*(La-1E-6)*(La-1E-6))/(1.0-CTerm_+EPS));
3804  RHS_MDelta = (La-1E-6)*pow(ETerm, DTerm_);
3805 
3806  /*--- Objective function and finitte differences derivative ---*/
3807 
3808  F = RHS - LHS;
3809  DF_DLa = (RHS_PDelta - RHS_MDelta)/2E-6;
3810 
3811  /*--- Newton's step ---*/
3812 
3813  La_old = La;
3814  La = La_old - 0.75*(F/DF_DLa);
3815 
3816  if (fabs(F) < 1E-10) break;
3817 
3818  }
3819 
3820  if (iter == 99) cout << "The laval number evaluation is not converging." << endl;
3821 
3822  /*--- Laval is bounded ---*/
3823 
3824  La = min(La, sqrt(6.0)); La = max(La, 0.0);
3825 
3826  To_Ti = max(1.0, T0_Ti*(1.0-CTerm_*La*La));
3827  ActDisk_DeltaT[iMarker][iVertex] = To_Ti;
3828 
3829  Po_Pi = max(1.0, pow(To_Ti, PolyCoeff*DTerm_));
3830  ActDisk_DeltaP[iMarker][iVertex] = Po_Pi;
3831 
3832  }
3833  else {
3834  ActDisk_DeltaT[iMarker][iVertex] = 1.0;
3835  ActDisk_DeltaP[iMarker][iVertex] = 1.0;
3836  }
3837  }
3838  }
3839  }
3840  }
3841  }
3842  }
3843 
3844  /*--- Broadcast some information to the master node ---*/
3845 
3846  ActDisk_Info = false;
3847  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3848  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3849  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3850  ActDisk_Info = true;
3851  }
3852  }
3853  if (!ActDisk_Info) config->SetInitial_BCThrust(0.0);
3854 
3855  MyBCThrust = config->GetInitial_BCThrust();
3856  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyBCThrust, &BCThrust, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_MAX, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
3857  config->SetInitial_BCThrust(BCThrust);
3858 
3859 }
3860 
3861 void CEulerSolver::ReadActDisk_InputFile(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
3862  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
3863  /*--- Input file provides force coefficients distributions along disk radius. Initialization
3864  necessary only at initial iteration. ---*/
3865 
3866  unsigned short iDim, iMarker;
3867  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
3868  string Marker_Tag;
3869  int iRow, nRow, iEl;
3870  std::vector<su2double> rad_v, dCt_v, dCp_v, dCr_v;
3871  su2double r_ = 0.0, r[MAXNDIM] = {0.0},
3872  AD_Center[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, AD_Axis[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, AD_Radius = 0.0, AD_J = 0.0;
3873  std::vector<su2double> Fa, Ft, Fr;
3874  su2double Fx = 0.0, Fy = 0.0, Fz = 0.0,
3875  Fx_inf = 0.0, Fy_inf = 0.0, Fz_inf = 0.0, Fx_sup = 0.0, Fy_sup = 0.0, Fz_sup = 0.0, h = 0.0;
3876  const su2double *P = nullptr;
3877 
3878  su2double Dens_FreeStream = config->GetDensity_FreeStream();
3879  const su2double *Vel_FreeStream = config->GetVelocity_FreeStream();
3880 
3881  /*--- Get the file name that contains the propeller data. ---*/
3882  string ActDisk_filename = config->GetActDisk_FileName();
3883  /*--- Loop over the markers. ---*/
3884  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
3885  if ((config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_INLET) ||
3886  (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == ACTDISK_OUTLET)) {
3887 
3888  /*--- Get the marker tag of the current BC marker. ---*/
3889  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
3890  ifstream ActDisk_file;
3891  /*--- Open the file that contains the propeller data. ---*/
3892  ActDisk_file.open(ActDisk_filename.data(), ios::in);
3893 
3894  /*--- Error message if the propeller data input file fails to open. ---*/
3895  if (ActDisk_file.fail()) SU2_MPI::Error("Unable to open Actuator Disk Input File", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
3896 
3897  string text_line, text_line_appo, name[2];
3898  string::size_type position;
3899 
3900  while (getline (ActDisk_file, text_line)) {
3901  /*--- Check if there is the "MARKER_ACTDISK=" string in the current line. If not keep on reading. ---*/
3902  position = text_line.find ("MARKER_ACTDISK=");
3903  if(position == string::npos){continue;}
3904  text_line.erase (0,15);
3905  /*--- Read the names of the two faces of the actuator disk and assign them to the name[] array. ---*/
3906  istringstream NameID(text_line);
3907  for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++){
3908  NameID >> name[i];
3909  }
3910 
3911  /*--- Check if the propeller data correspond to the actual BC marker. ---*/
3912  if (Marker_Tag == name[0] || Marker_Tag == name[1]){
3913  /*--- Read and assign the coordinates of the actuator disk center. ---*/
3914  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3915  text_line_appo.erase (0,7);
3916  istringstream C_value(text_line_appo);
3917  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
3918  C_value >> AD_Center[iDim];
3919  }
3920 
3921  /*--- Read and assign the components of the actuator disk axis versor pointing backward. ---*/
3922  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3923  text_line_appo.erase (0,5);
3924  istringstream axis_value(text_line_appo);
3925  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
3926  axis_value >> AD_Axis[iDim];
3927  }
3928 
3929  /*--- Read and assign the value of the actuator disk radius. ---*/
3930  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3931  text_line_appo.erase (0,7);
3932  istringstream R_value(text_line_appo);
3933  R_value >> AD_Radius;
3934 
3935  /*--- Read and assign the value of the actuator disk advance ratio. ---*/
3936  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3937  text_line_appo.erase (0,10);
3938  istringstream J_value(text_line_appo);
3939  J_value >> AD_J;
3940 
3941  /*--- Read and assign the number of radial stations contained in the propeller data file. ---*/
3942  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3943  text_line_appo.erase (0,5);
3944  istringstream row_value(text_line_appo);
3945  row_value >> nRow;
3946 
3947  /*--- Assign the vectors dimension. ---*/
3948  rad_v.resize(nRow);
3949  dCt_v.resize(nRow);
3950  dCp_v.resize(nRow);
3951  dCr_v.resize(nRow);
3952 
3953  Fa.resize(nRow);
3954  Ft.resize(nRow);
3955  Fr.resize(nRow);
3956 
3957  /*--- Read and assign the values of the non-dimensional radius, thrust coefficient, power coefficient
3958  and radial force coefficient. ---*/
3959  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3960  for (iRow = 0; iRow < nRow; iRow++){
3961  getline (ActDisk_file, text_line_appo);
3962  istringstream row_val_value(text_line_appo);
3963  row_val_value >> rad_v[iRow] >> dCt_v[iRow] >> dCp_v[iRow] >> dCr_v[iRow];
3964  }
3965 
3966  /*--- Set the actuator disk radius value, center coordiantes values and axis coordinates values. ---*/
3967  ActDisk_R(iMarker) = AD_Radius;
3968  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
3969  ActDisk_C(iMarker, iDim) = AD_Center[iDim];
3970  ActDisk_Axis(iMarker, iDim) = AD_Axis[iDim];
3971  }
3972 
3973  /*--- If the first radial station corresponds to the actuator disk center, the radial and tangential forces
3974  per unit area (Fr and Ft) are equal to zero, while the axial force per unit area (Fa) is computed using
3975  a linear interpolation in order to avoid a mathematical singularity at actuator disk center. ---*/
3976  if (rad_v[0] == 0.0){
3977  Fa[0] = (((2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
3978  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER))*((dCt_v[1] - dCt_v[0])/rad_v[1])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
3979  Ft[0] = 0.0;
3980  Fr[0] = 0.0;
3981  }
3982  else {
3983  Fa[0] = (dCt_v[0]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
3984  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
3985  Ft[0] = (dCp_v[0]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
3986  ((AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0])*(AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0]))) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
3987  Fr[0] = (dCr_v[0]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
3988  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[0])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
3989  }
3990 
3991  /*--- Loop over the radial stations. Computation of Fa (axial force per unit area), Ft (tangential force per unit area)
3992  and Fr (radial force per unit area).
3993  These equations are not valid if the freestream velocity is equal to zero (hovering condition not enabled yet). ---*/
3994  for (iEl = 1; iEl < nRow; iEl++){
3995  Fa[iEl] = (dCt_v[iEl]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
3996  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
3997  Ft[iEl] = (dCp_v[iEl]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
3998  ((AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl])*(AD_J*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl]))) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
3999  Fr[iEl] = (dCr_v[iEl]*(2*Dens_FreeStream*pow(Vel_FreeStream[0],2))/
4000  (pow(AD_J,2)*PI_NUMBER*rad_v[iEl])) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
4001  }
4002 
4003  /*--- Loop over the marker nodes. ---*/
4004  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
4005  /*--- Get the coordinates of the current node. ---*/
4006  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4007  P = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
4008 
4009  /*--- Computation of the radius coordinates for the current node. ---*/
4010  GeometryToolbox::Distance(nDim, P, AD_Center, r);
4011 
4012  /*--- Computation of the non-dimensional radius for the current node. ---*/
4013  r_ = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, r) / AD_Radius;
4014 
4015  /*--- Loop over the actuator disk radial stations. ---*/
4016  for (iEl = 0; iEl < nRow; iEl++){
4017  /*--- Check if the current node is located between rad_v[iEl] and rad_v[iEl-1]. ---*/
4018  if (r_ <= rad_v[iEl]){
4019  /*--- h is the dinstance of the current node from the previous radial element (iEl-1)
4020  divided by the length of the radial element in which the node is contained. ---*/
4021  h = (r_-rad_v[iEl-1])/(rad_v[iEl]-rad_v[iEl-1]);
4022  /*--- Fx, Fy and Fz are the x, y and z components of the tangential and radial forces
4023  per unit area resultant. ---*/
4024  if(r_ == 0.0){
4025  Fx = 0.0;
4026  Fy = 0.0;
4027  Fz = 0.0;
4028  }
4029  /*--- _inf is the value of the previous radial element. _sup is the value of the
4030  following radial element. ---*/
4031  else{
4032  Fx_inf = (Ft[iEl-1]+Fr[iEl-1])*(r[0]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4033  Fy_inf = (Ft[iEl-1]+Fr[iEl-1])*(r[2]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4034  Fz_inf = -(Ft[iEl-1]+Fr[iEl-1])*(r[1]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4035  Fx_sup = (Ft[iEl]+Fr[iEl])*(r[0]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4036  Fy_sup = (Ft[iEl]+Fr[iEl])*(r[2]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4037  Fz_sup = -(Ft[iEl]+Fr[iEl])*(r[1]/(r_*AD_Radius));
4038 
4039  /*--- Fx, Fy and Fz at the current node are evaluated using a linear interpolation between
4040  the end vaues of the radial element in which the current node is contained. ---*/
4041  Fx = Fx_inf + (Fx_sup - Fx_inf)*h;
4042  Fy = Fy_inf + (Fy_sup - Fy_inf)*h;
4043  Fz = Fz_inf + (Fz_sup - Fz_inf)*h;
4044  }
4045  /*--- Set the values of Fa, Fx, Fy and Fz. Fa is evaluated using a linear interpolation. ---*/
4046  ActDisk_Fa[iMarker][iVertex] = Fa[iEl-1] + (Fa[iEl]-Fa[iEl-1])*h;
4047  ActDisk_Fx[iMarker][iVertex] = Fx;
4048  ActDisk_Fy[iMarker][iVertex] = Fy;
4049  ActDisk_Fz[iMarker][iVertex] = Fz;
4050 
4051  break;
4052  }
4053  }
4054  }
4055  }
4056  }
4057  }
4058  }
4059 }
4060 
4061 void CEulerSolver::SetFarfield_AoA(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
4062  CConfig *config, unsigned short iMesh, bool Output) {
4063 
4064  const auto InnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
4065  const su2double AoS = config->GetAoS()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
4066 
4067  /* --- Initialize values at first iteration --- */
4068 
4069  if (InnerIter == 0) {
4070  Total_CD_Prev = 0.0;
4071  Total_CL_Prev = 0.0;
4072  Total_CMx_Prev = 0.0;
4073  Total_CMy_Prev = 0.0;
4074  Total_CMz_Prev = 0.0;
4075  AoA_Prev = config->GetAoA();
4076  dCL_dAlpha = config->GetdCL_dAlpha();
4077  AoA_inc = 0.0;
4078  }
4079 
4080  /*--- Retrieve the AoA (degrees) ---*/
4081 
4082  su2double AoA = config->GetAoA();
4083 
4084  /* --- Set new AoA if needed --- */
4085 
4086  if (fabs(AoA_inc) > 0.0 && Output) {
4087 
4088  /* --- Update *_Prev values with current coefficients --- */
4089 
4090  SetCoefficient_Gradients(config);
4091 
4092  Total_CD_Prev = TotalCoeff.CD;
4093  Total_CL_Prev = TotalCoeff.CL;
4094  Total_CMx_Prev = TotalCoeff.CMx;
4095  Total_CMy_Prev = TotalCoeff.CMy;
4096  Total_CMz_Prev = TotalCoeff.CMz;
4097  AoA_Prev = AoA;
4098 
4099  /*--- Compute a new value for AoA on the fine mesh only (degrees)---*/
4100 
4101  if (iMesh == MESH_0) {
4102  AoA = AoA + AoA_inc;
4103  config->SetAoA(AoA);
4104  }
4105 
4106  AoA *= PI_NUMBER/180.0;
4107 
4108  /*--- Update the freestream velocity vector at the farfield
4109  * Compute the new freestream velocity with the updated AoA,
4110  * "Velocity_Inf" is shared with config. ---*/
4111 
4112  const su2double Vel_Infty_Mag = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Velocity_Inf);
4113 
4114  if (nDim == 2) {
4115  Velocity_Inf[0] = cos(AoA)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
4116  Velocity_Inf[1] = sin(AoA)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
4117  }
4118  else {
4119  Velocity_Inf[0] = cos(AoA)*cos(AoS)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
4120  Velocity_Inf[1] = sin(AoS)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
4121  Velocity_Inf[2] = sin(AoA)*cos(AoS)*Vel_Infty_Mag;
4122  }
4123  }
4124 }
4125 
4126 bool CEulerSolver::FixedCL_Convergence(CConfig* config, bool convergence) {
4127  const su2double Target_CL = config->GetTarget_CL();
4128  const auto curr_iter = config->GetInnerIter();
4129  const auto Iter_dCL_dAlpha = config->GetIter_dCL_dAlpha();
4130  bool fixed_cl_conv = false;
4131  AoA_inc = 0.0;
4132 
4133  /*--- if in Fixed CL mode, before finite differencing --- */
4134 
4135  if (!Start_AoA_FD){
4136  if (convergence){
4137 
4138  /* --- C_L and solution are converged, start finite differencing --- */
4139 
4140  if (fabs(TotalCoeff.CL-Target_CL) < (config->GetCauchy_Eps()/2)) {
4141 
4142  /* --- If no finite differencing required --- */
4143 
4144  if (Iter_dCL_dAlpha == 0){
4145  fixed_cl_conv = true;
4146  return fixed_cl_conv;
4147  }
4148 
4149  /* --- Else, set up finite differencing routine ---*/
4150 
4151  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4152  Start_AoA_FD = true;
4153  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4154  AoA_inc = 0.001;
4155  }
4156 
4157  /* --- C_L is not converged to target value and some iterations
4158  have passed since last update, so update AoA --- */
4159 
4160  else if ((curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA) > config->GetStartConv_Iter()){
4161  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4162  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4163  if (fabs(TotalCoeff.CL-Target_CL) > (config->GetCauchy_Eps()/2)) {
4164  AoA_inc = (1.0/dCL_dAlpha)*(Target_CL - TotalCoeff.CL);
4165  }
4166  }
4167  }
4168 
4169  /* --- If the iteration limit between AoA updates is met, so update AoA --- */
4170 
4171  else if ((curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA) == config->GetUpdate_AoA_Iter_Limit()) {
4172  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4173  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4174  if (fabs(TotalCoeff.CL-Target_CL) > (config->GetCauchy_Eps()/2)) {
4175  AoA_inc = (1.0/dCL_dAlpha)*(Target_CL - TotalCoeff.CL);
4176  }
4177  }
4178 
4179  /* --- If the total iteration limit is reached, start finite differencing --- */
4180 
4181  if (curr_iter == config->GetnInner_Iter() - Iter_dCL_dAlpha){
4182  if (Iter_dCL_dAlpha == 0){
4183  End_AoA_FD = true;
4184  }
4185  Iter_Update_AoA = curr_iter;
4186  Start_AoA_FD = true;
4187  fixed_cl_conv = false;
4188  AoA_inc = 0.001;
4189  }
4190  }
4191 
4192  /* --- If Finite Difference Mode has ended, end simulation --- */
4193 
4194  if (End_AoA_FD){
4195  //fixed_cl_conv = true;
4196  return true;
4197  }
4198 
4199  /* --- If starting Finite Difference Mode --- */
4200 
4201  if (Start_AoA_FD){
4202 
4203  /* --- Disable history writing --- */
4204 
4205  config->SetHistory_Wrt_Freq(2, 0);
4206 
4207  /* --- End Finite Difference Mode if iteration limit is reached, so simualtion is converged --- */
4208 
4209  End_AoA_FD = ((curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA - 2) == Iter_dCL_dAlpha ||
4210  curr_iter == config->GetnInner_Iter()- 2 );
4211 
4212  if (convergence && (curr_iter - Iter_Update_AoA) > config->GetStartConv_Iter())
4213  End_AoA_FD = true;
4214 
4215  /* --- If Finite Difference mode is ending, reset AoA and calculate Coefficient Gradients --- */
4216 
4217  if (End_AoA_FD){
4218  SetCoefficient_Gradients(config);
4219  config->SetAoA(AoA_Prev);
4220  }
4221  }
4222 
4223  return fixed_cl_conv;
4224 
4225 }
4226 
4227 void CEulerSolver::SetCoefficient_Gradients(CConfig *config) const{
4228 
4229  const su2double AoA = config->GetAoA();
4230 
4231  if (AoA == AoA_Prev) return;
4232 
4233  /*--- Calculate gradients of coefficients w.r.t. CL ---*/
4234 
4235  const su2double dCL = TotalCoeff.CL - Total_CL_Prev;
4236  const su2double dCL_dAlpha_ = dCL / (AoA - AoA_Prev);
4237  const su2double dCD_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CD-Total_CD_Prev) / dCL;
4238  const su2double dCMx_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CMx-Total_CMx_Prev) / dCL;
4239  const su2double dCMy_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CMy-Total_CMy_Prev) / dCL;
4240  const su2double dCMz_dCL_ = (TotalCoeff.CMz-Total_CMz_Prev) / dCL;
4241 
4242  /*--- Set the value of the dOF/dCL in the config file ---*/
4243 
4244  config->SetdCD_dCL(dCD_dCL_);
4245  config->SetdCMx_dCL(dCMx_dCL_);
4246  config->SetdCMy_dCL(dCMy_dCL_);
4247  config->SetdCMz_dCL(dCMz_dCL_);
4248  config->SetdCL_dAlpha(dCL_dAlpha_);
4249 }

4251 void CEulerSolver::UpdateCustomBoundaryConditions(CGeometry **geometry_container, CConfig *config){
4252 
4253  unsigned short nMGlevel;
4254  unsigned long iMarker;
4255 
4256  // TODO: Update the fluid boundary conditions for MG
4257  nMGlevel = config->GetnMGLevels();
4258  if (nMGlevel > 1) {
4259  for (iMarker=0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
4260  bool isCustomizable = config->GetMarker_All_PyCustom(iMarker);
4261  bool isInlet = (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == INLET_FLOW);
4262  if (isCustomizable && isInlet)
4263  SU2_MPI::Error("Custom inlet BCs are not currently compatible with multigrid.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
4264  }
4265  }
