4267 
4268 void CEulerSolver::Evaluate_ObjFunc(const CConfig *config, CSolver**) {
4269 
4270  unsigned short iMarker_Monitoring, Kind_ObjFunc;
4271  su2double Weight_ObjFunc;
4272 
4273  Total_ComboObj = EvaluateCommonObjFunc(*config);
4274 
4275  /*--- Loop over all monitored markers, add to the 'combo' objective ---*/
4276 
4277  if (config->GetFixed_CL_Mode()) {
4278  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
4279 
4280  Weight_ObjFunc = config->GetWeight_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
4281  Kind_ObjFunc = config->GetKind_ObjFunc(iMarker_Monitoring);
4282 
4283  switch(Kind_ObjFunc) {
4284  case DRAG_COEFFICIENT:
4285  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCD_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4286  break;
4287  case MOMENT_X_COEFFICIENT:
4288  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCMx_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4289  break;
4290  case MOMENT_Y_COEFFICIENT:
4291  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCMy_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4292  break;
4293  case MOMENT_Z_COEFFICIENT:
4294  Total_ComboObj -= Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetdCMz_dCL()*(SurfaceCoeff.CL[iMarker_Monitoring]);
4295  break;
4296  default:
4297  break;
4298  }
4299  }
4300  }
4301 
4302  /*--- The following are not per-surface, and so to avoid that they are
4303  double-counted when multiple surfaces are specified, they have been
4304  placed outside of the loop above. In addition, multi-objective mode is
4305  also disabled for these objective functions (error thrown at start). ---*/
4306 
4307  Weight_ObjFunc = config->GetWeight_ObjFunc(0);
4308  Kind_ObjFunc = config->GetKind_ObjFunc(0);
4309 
4310  switch(Kind_ObjFunc) {
4311  case NEARFIELD_PRESSURE:
4312  Total_ComboObj+=Weight_ObjFunc*Total_CNearFieldOF;
4313  break;
4314  case SURFACE_MACH:
4315  Total_ComboObj+=Weight_ObjFunc*config->GetSurface_Mach(0);
4316  break;
4317  default:
4318  break;
4319  }
4320 }
4321 
4322 void CEulerSolver::BC_Far_Field(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics,
4323  CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
4324 
4325  unsigned short iDim;
4326  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
4327 
4328  su2double *GridVel;
4329  su2double Area, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4330  su2double Density, Pressure, Energy, Velocity[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4331  su2double Density_Bound, Pressure_Bound, Vel_Bound[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4332  su2double Density_Infty, Pressure_Infty, Vel_Infty[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
4333  su2double SoundSpeed, Entropy, Velocity2, Vn;
4334  su2double SoundSpeed_Bound, Entropy_Bound, Vel2_Bound, Vn_Bound;
4335  su2double SoundSpeed_Infty, Entropy_Infty, Vel2_Infty, Vn_Infty, Qn_Infty;
4336  su2double RiemannPlus, RiemannMinus;
4337  su2double *V_infty, *V_domain;
4338 
4339  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
4340 
4341  bool implicit = config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT;
4342  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
4343  bool tkeNeeded = config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST;
4344 
4345  su2double *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
4346 
4347  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
4348 
4349  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
4350  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
4351  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4352 
4353  /*--- Allocate the value at the infinity ---*/
4354  V_infty = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
4355 
4356  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
4357 
4358  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
4359 
4360  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
4361 
4362  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
4363 
4364  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
4365 
4366  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
4367  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
4368  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
4369 
4370  /*--- Retrieve solution at the farfield boundary node ---*/
4371  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
4372 
4373  /*--- Construct solution state at infinity for compressible flow by
4374  using Riemann invariants, and then impose a weak boundary condition
4375  by computing the flux using this new state for U. See CFD texts by
4376  Hirsch or Blazek for more detail. Adapted from an original
4377  implementation in the Stanford University multi-block (SUmb) solver
4378  in the routine bcFarfield.f90 written by Edwin van der Weide,
4379  last modified 06-12-2005. First, compute the unit normal at the
4380  boundary nodes. ---*/
4381 
4382  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
4383  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4384  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
4385 
4386  /*--- Store primitive variables (density, velocities, velocity squared,
4387  energy, pressure, and sound speed) at the boundary node, and set some
4388  other quantities for clarity. Project the current flow velocity vector
4389  at this boundary node into the local normal direction, i.e. compute
4390  v_bound.n. ---*/
4391 
4392  Density_Bound = V_domain[nDim+2];
4393  Vel2_Bound = 0.0; Vn_Bound = 0.0;
4394  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4395  Vel_Bound[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
4396  Vel2_Bound += Vel_Bound[iDim]*Vel_Bound[iDim];
4397  Vn_Bound += Vel_Bound[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4398  }
4399  Pressure_Bound = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
4400  SoundSpeed_Bound = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_Bound/Density_Bound);
4401  Entropy_Bound = pow(Density_Bound, Gamma)/Pressure_Bound;
4402 
4403  /*--- Store the primitive variable state for the freestream. Project
4404  the freestream velocity vector into the local normal direction,
4405  i.e. compute v_infty.n. ---*/
4406 
4407  Density_Infty = GetDensity_Inf();
4408  Vel2_Infty = 0.0; Vn_Infty = 0.0;
4409  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4410  Vel_Infty[iDim] = GetVelocity_Inf(iDim);
4411  Vel2_Infty += Vel_Infty[iDim]*Vel_Infty[iDim];
4412  Vn_Infty += Vel_Infty[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4413  }
4414  Pressure_Infty = GetPressure_Inf();
4415  SoundSpeed_Infty = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_Infty/Density_Infty);
4416  Entropy_Infty = pow(Density_Infty, Gamma)/Pressure_Infty;
4417 
4418  /*--- Adjust the normal freestream velocity for grid movement ---*/
4419 
4420  Qn_Infty = Vn_Infty;
4421  if (dynamic_grid) {
4422  GridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
4423  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4424  Qn_Infty -= GridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4425  }
4426 
4427  /*--- Compute acoustic Riemann invariants: R = u.n +/- 2c/(gamma-1).
4428  These correspond with the eigenvalues (u+c) and (u-c), respectively,
4429  which represent the acoustic waves. Positive characteristics are
4430  incoming, and a physical boundary condition is imposed (freestream
4431  state). This occurs when either (u.n+c) > 0 or (u.n-c) > 0. Negative
4432  characteristics are leaving the domain, and numerical boundary
4433  conditions are required by extrapolating from the interior state
4434  using the Riemann invariants. This occurs when (u.n+c) < 0 or
4435  (u.n-c) < 0. Note that grid movement is taken into account when
4436  checking the sign of the eigenvalue. ---*/
4437 
4438  /*--- Check whether (u.n+c) is greater or less than zero ---*/
4439 
4440  if (Qn_Infty > -SoundSpeed_Infty) {
4441  /*--- Subsonic inflow or outflow ---*/
4442  RiemannPlus = Vn_Bound + 2.0*SoundSpeed_Bound/Gamma_Minus_One;
4443  } else {
4444  /*--- Supersonic inflow ---*/
4445  RiemannPlus = Vn_Infty + 2.0*SoundSpeed_Infty/Gamma_Minus_One;
4446  }
4447 
4448  /*--- Check whether (u.n-c) is greater or less than zero ---*/
4449 
4450  if (Qn_Infty > SoundSpeed_Infty) {
4451  /*--- Supersonic outflow ---*/
4452  RiemannMinus = Vn_Bound - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Bound/Gamma_Minus_One;
4453  } else {
4454  /*--- Subsonic outflow ---*/
4455  RiemannMinus = Vn_Infty - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Infty/Gamma_Minus_One;
4456  }
4457 
4458  /*--- Compute a new value for the local normal velocity and speed of
4459  sound from the Riemann invariants. ---*/
4460 
4461  Vn = 0.5 * (RiemannPlus + RiemannMinus);
4462  SoundSpeed = 0.25 * (RiemannPlus - RiemannMinus)*Gamma_Minus_One;
4463 
4464  /*--- Construct the primitive variable state at the boundary for
4465  computing the flux for the weak boundary condition. The values
4466  that we choose to construct the solution (boundary or freestream)
4467  depend on whether we are at an inflow or outflow. At an outflow, we
4468  choose boundary information (at most one characteristic is incoming),
4469  while at an inflow, we choose infinity values (at most one
4470  characteristic is outgoing). ---*/
4471 
4472  if (Qn_Infty > 0.0) {
4473  /*--- Outflow conditions ---*/
4474  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4475  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Bound[iDim] + (Vn-Vn_Bound)*UnitNormal[iDim];
4476  Entropy = Entropy_Bound;
4477  } else {
4478  /*--- Inflow conditions ---*/
4479  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4480  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Infty[iDim] + (Vn-Vn_Infty)*UnitNormal[iDim];
4481  Entropy = Entropy_Infty;
4482  }
4483 
4484  /*--- Recompute the primitive variables. ---*/
4485 
4486  Density = pow(Entropy*SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma,1.0/Gamma_Minus_One);
4487  Velocity2 = 0.0;
4488  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4489  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
4490  }
4491  Pressure = Density*SoundSpeed*SoundSpeed/Gamma;
4492  Energy = Pressure/(Gamma_Minus_One*Density) + 0.5*Velocity2;
4493  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
4494 
4495  /*--- Store new primitive state for computing the flux. ---*/
4496 
4497  V_infty[0] = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Density);
4498  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4499  V_infty[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
4500  V_infty[nDim+1] = Pressure;
4501  V_infty[nDim+2] = Density;
4502  V_infty[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
4503 
4504 
4505 
4506  /*--- Set various quantities in the numerics class ---*/
4507 
4508  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_infty);
4509 
4510  if (dynamic_grid) {
4511  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
4512  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
4513  }
4514 
4515  /*--- Compute the convective residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
4516 
4517  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
4518 
4519  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
4520 
4521  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
4522 
4523  /*--- Convective Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
4524 
4525  if (implicit)
4526  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
4527 
4528  /*--- Viscous residual contribution ---*/
4529 
4530  if (viscous) {
4531 
4532  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
4533 
4534  V_infty[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
4535  V_infty[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
4536 
4537  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
4538 
4539  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
4540  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
4541  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
4542  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
4543  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
4544 
4545  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
4546 
4547  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_infty);
4548  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint),
4549  nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
4550 
4551  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
4552 
4553  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
4554  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
4555  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
4556 
4557  /*--- Compute and update viscous residual ---*/
4558 
4559  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
4560  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
4561 
4562  /*--- Viscous Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
4563 
4564  if (implicit)
4565  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
4566 
4567  }
4568 
4569  }
4570  }
4571  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
4572 
4573  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
4574  delete [] Normal;
4575 
4576 }
4577 
4578 void CEulerSolver::BC_Riemann(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
4579  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
4580  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
4581 
4582  unsigned short iDim, iVar, jVar, kVar;
4583  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Point_Normal;
4584  const su2double *Flow_Dir, *Mach;
4585  su2double P_Total, T_Total, P_static, T_static, Rho_static, Area, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM];
4586  su2double *Velocity_b, Velocity2_b, Enthalpy_b, Energy_b, StaticEnergy_b, Density_b, Kappa_b, Chi_b, Pressure_b, Temperature_b;
4587  su2double *Velocity_e, Velocity2_e, VelMag_e, Enthalpy_e, Entropy_e, Energy_e = 0.0, StaticEnthalpy_e, StaticEnergy_e, Density_e = 0.0, Pressure_e;
4588  su2double *Velocity_i, Velocity2_i, Enthalpy_i, Energy_i, StaticEnergy_i, Density_i, Kappa_i, Chi_i, Pressure_i, SoundSpeed_i;
4589  su2double ProjVelocity_i;
4590  su2double **P_Tensor, **invP_Tensor, *Lambda_i, **Jacobian_b, **Jacobian_i, **DubDu, *dw, *u_e, *u_i, *u_b;
4591  su2double *gridVel, *Residual;
4592  su2double *V_boundary, *V_domain, *S_boundary, *S_domain;
4593 
4594  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
4595  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
4596  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
4597  bool gravity = config->GetGravityForce();
4598  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
4599 
4600  su2double *Normal, *FlowDirMix, TangVelocity, NormalVelocity;
4601  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
4602 
4603  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
4604  Velocity_b = new su2double[nDim];
4605  Velocity_e = new su2double[nDim];
4606  FlowDirMix = new su2double[nDim];
4607  Lambda_i = new su2double[nVar];
4608  u_i = new su2double[nVar];
4609  u_e = new su2double[nVar];
4610  u_b = new su2double[nVar];
4611  dw = new su2double[nVar];
4612 
4613  Residual = new su2double[nVar];
4614 
4615  S_boundary = new su2double[8];
4616 
4617  P_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
4618  invP_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
4619  Jacobian_i = new su2double*[nVar];
4620  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
4621  {
4622  P_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
4623  invP_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
4624  Jacobian_i[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
4625  }
4626 
4627  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
4628 
4629  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
4630  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
4631 
4632  V_boundary= GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
4633 
4634  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4635 
4636  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
4637  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
4638 
4639  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
4640  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
4641 
4642  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
4643  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
4644  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
4645  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
4646 
4647  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
4648 
4649  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4650  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
4651 
4652  /*--- Retrieve solution at this boundary node ---*/
4653  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
4654 
4655  /*--- Compute the internal state u_i ---*/
4656  Velocity2_i = 0;
4657  for (iDim=0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4658  {
4659  Velocity_i[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
4660  Velocity2_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*Velocity_i[iDim];
4661  }
4662 
4663 
4664  Density_i = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
4665 
4666  Energy_i = nodes->GetEnergy(iPoint);
4667  StaticEnergy_i = Energy_i - 0.5*Velocity2_i;
4668 
4669  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_i, StaticEnergy_i);
4670 
4671  Pressure_i = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
4672  Enthalpy_i = Energy_i + Pressure_i/Density_i;
4673 
4674  SoundSpeed_i = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
4675 
4676  Kappa_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_i;
4677  Chi_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_i * StaticEnergy_i;
4678 
4679  ProjVelocity_i = 0.0;
4680  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4681  ProjVelocity_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4682 
4683  /*--- Build the external state u_e from boundary data and internal node ---*/
4684 
4685  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Riemann(Marker_Tag))
4686  {
4687  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT:
4688 
4689  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
4690  if (gravity) P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
4691  else P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
4692  T_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
4693  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
4694 
4695  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
4696  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
4697  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
4698 
4699  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
4700  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
4701  Enthalpy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy()+ GetFluidModel()->GetPressure()/GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
4702  Entropy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
4703 
4704  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
4705  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
4706  if (nDim == 2){
4707  NormalVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[0];
4708  TangVelocity= -sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[1];
4709  Velocity_e[0]= UnitNormal[0]*NormalVelocity - UnitNormal[1]*TangVelocity;
4710  Velocity_e[1]= UnitNormal[1]*NormalVelocity + UnitNormal[0]*TangVelocity;
4711  }else{
4712  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4713  Velocity_e[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[iDim];
4714  }
4715  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
4716  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
4717  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
4718  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
4719  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
4720  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
4721  break;
4722 
4723  case STATIC_SUPERSONIC_INFLOW_PT:
4724 
4725  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
4726  if (gravity) P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
4727  else P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
4728  T_static = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
4729  Mach = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
4730 
4731  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
4732  P_static /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
4733  T_static /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
4734 
4735  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
4736  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_static, T_static);
4737 
4738  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
4739  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
4740  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4741  Velocity_e[iDim] = Mach[iDim]*GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
4742  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
4743  }
4744  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
4745  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
4746  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
4747  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
4748  break;
4749 
4750  case STATIC_SUPERSONIC_INFLOW_PD:
4751 
4752  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
4753 
4754  if (gravity) P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
4755  else P_static = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
4756  Rho_static = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
4757  Mach = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
4758 
4759  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
4760  P_static /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
4761  Rho_static /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
4762 
4763  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
4764  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(P_static, Rho_static);
4765 
4766  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
4767  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
4768  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4769  Velocity_e[iDim] = Mach[iDim]*GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
4770  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
4771  }
4772  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
4773  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
4774  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
4775  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
4776  break;
4777 
4778  case DENSITY_VELOCITY:
4779 
4780  /*--- Retrieve the specified density and velocity magnitude ---*/
4781  Density_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
4782  VelMag_e = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
4783  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
4784 
4785  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
4786  Density_e /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
4787  VelMag_e /= config->GetVelocity_Ref();
4788 
4789  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4790  Velocity_e[iDim] = VelMag_e*Flow_Dir[iDim];
4791  Energy_e = Energy_i;
4792  break;
4793 
4794  case STATIC_PRESSURE:
4795 
4796  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
4797  Pressure_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
4798  Pressure_e /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
4799  Density_e = Density_i;
4800 
4801  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
4802  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
4803  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
4804  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
4805  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
4806  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
4807  }
4808  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
4809  break;
4810 
4811  default:
4812  SU2_MPI::Error("Invalid Riemann input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
4813  break;
4814  }
4815 
4816  /*--- Compute P (matrix of right eigenvectors) ---*/
4817  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix(&Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Enthalpy_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal, P_Tensor);
4818 
4819  /*--- Compute inverse P (matrix of left eigenvectors)---*/
4820  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix_inv(invP_Tensor, &Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal);
4821 
4822  /*--- eigenvalues contribution due to grid motion ---*/
4823  if (dynamic_grid) {
4824  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
4825 
4826  su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
4827  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4828  ProjGridVel += gridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
4829  ProjVelocity_i -= ProjGridVel;
4830  }
4831 
4832  /*--- Flow eigenvalues ---*/
4833  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4834  Lambda_i[iDim] = ProjVelocity_i;
4835  Lambda_i[nVar-2] = ProjVelocity_i + SoundSpeed_i;
4836  Lambda_i[nVar-1] = ProjVelocity_i - SoundSpeed_i;
4837 
4838  /*--- Compute the boundary state u_e ---*/
4839  u_e[0] = Density_e;
4840  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4841  u_e[iDim+1] = Velocity_e[iDim]*Density_e;
4842  u_e[nVar-1] = Energy_e*Density_e;
4843 
4844  /*--- Compute the boundary state u_i ---*/
4845  u_i[0] = Density_i;
4846  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4847  u_i[iDim+1] = Velocity_i[iDim]*Density_i;
4848  u_i[nVar-1] = Energy_i*Density_i;
4849 
4850  /*--- Compute the characteristic jumps ---*/
4851  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
4852  {
4853  dw[iVar] = 0;
4854  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
4855  dw[iVar] += invP_Tensor[iVar][jVar] * (u_e[jVar] - u_i[jVar]);
4856 
4857  }
4858 
4859  /*--- Compute the boundary state u_b using characteristics ---*/
4860  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
4861  {
4862  u_b[iVar] = u_i[iVar];
4863 
4864  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
4865  {
4866  if (Lambda_i[jVar] < 0)
4867  {
4868  u_b[iVar] += P_Tensor[iVar][jVar]*dw[jVar];
4869 
4870  }
4871  }
4872  }
4873 
4874 
4875  /*--- Compute the thermodynamic state in u_b ---*/
4876  Density_b = u_b[0];
4877  Velocity2_b = 0;
4878  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4879  {
4880  Velocity_b[iDim] = u_b[iDim+1]/Density_b;
4881  Velocity2_b += Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
4882  }
4883  Energy_b = u_b[nVar-1]/Density_b;
4884  StaticEnergy_b = Energy_b - 0.5*Velocity2_b;
4885  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_b, StaticEnergy_b);
4886  Pressure_b = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
4887  Temperature_b = GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
4888  Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
4889  Kappa_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_b;
4890  Chi_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_b * StaticEnergy_b;
4891 
4892  /*--- Compute the residuals ---*/
4893  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjFlux(&Density_b, Velocity_b, &Pressure_b, &Enthalpy_b, Normal, Residual);
4894 
4895  /*--- Residual contribution due to grid motion ---*/
4896  if (dynamic_grid) {
4897  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
4898  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
4899 
4900  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4901  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
4902  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
4903  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *(u_b[iVar]);
4904  }
4905 
4906  if (implicit) {
4907 
4908  Jacobian_b = new su2double*[nVar];
4909  DubDu = new su2double*[nVar];
4910  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
4911  {
4912  Jacobian_b[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
4913  DubDu[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
4914  }
4915 
4916  /*--- Initialize DubDu to unit matrix---*/
4917 
4918  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
4919  {
4920  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
4921  DubDu[iVar][jVar]= 0;
4922 
4923  DubDu[iVar][iVar]= 1;
4924  }
4925 
4926  /*--- Compute DubDu -= RNL---*/
4927  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
4928  {
4929  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
4930  {
4931  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++)
4932  {
4933  if (Lambda_i[kVar]<0)
4934  DubDu[iVar][jVar] -= P_Tensor[iVar][kVar] * invP_Tensor[kVar][jVar];
4935  }
4936  }
4937  }
4938 
4939  /*--- Compute flux Jacobian in state b ---*/
4940  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjJac(Velocity_b, &Enthalpy_b, &Chi_b, &Kappa_b, Normal, 1.0, Jacobian_b);
4941 
4942  /*--- Jacobian contribution due to grid motion ---*/
4943  if (dynamic_grid)
4944  {
4945  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
4946  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
4947  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4948  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
4949  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4950  Jacobian_b[iVar][iVar] -= projVelocity;
4951  }
4952 
4953  }
4954 
4955  /*--- initiate Jacobian_i to zero matrix ---*/
4956  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
4957  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
4958  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
4959 
4960  /*--- Compute numerical flux Jacobian at node i ---*/
4961  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++) {
4962  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++) {
4963  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++) {
4964  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] += Jacobian_b[iVar][kVar] * DubDu[kVar][jVar];
4965  }
4966  }
4967  }
4968 
4969  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4970  delete [] Jacobian_b[iVar];
4971  delete [] DubDu[iVar];
4972  }
4973  delete [] Jacobian_b;
4974  delete [] DubDu;
4975  }
4976 
4977  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
4978  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
4979 
4980  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
4981  if (implicit)
4982  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_i);
4983 
4984  /*--- Viscous contribution ---*/
4985 
4986  if (viscous) {
4987 
4988  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
4989 
4990  V_boundary[0] = Temperature_b;
4991  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
4992  V_boundary[iDim+1] = Velocity_b[iDim];
4993  V_boundary[nDim+1] = Pressure_b;
4994  V_boundary[nDim+2] = Density_b;
4995  V_boundary[nDim+3] = Enthalpy_b;
4996 
4997  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
4998 
4999  V_boundary[nDim+5] = GetFluidModel()->GetLaminarViscosity();
5000  V_boundary[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
5001  V_boundary[nDim+7] = GetFluidModel()->GetThermalConductivity();
5002  V_boundary[nDim+8] = GetFluidModel()->GetCp();
5003 
5004  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
5005 
5006  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
5007  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
5008  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
5009  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5010  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5011 
5012  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
5013 
5014  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
5015  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
5016 
5017  /*--- Secondary variables ---*/
5018 
5019  S_domain = nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint);
5020 
5021  /*--- Compute secondary thermodynamic properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5022 
5023  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
5024  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
5025 
5026  S_boundary[2]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTdrho_e();
5027  S_boundary[3]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTde_rho();
5028 
5029  /*--- Compute secondary thermo-physical properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5030 
5031  S_boundary[4]= GetFluidModel()->Getdmudrho_T();
5032  S_boundary[5]= GetFluidModel()->GetdmudT_rho();
5033 
5034  S_boundary[6]= GetFluidModel()->Getdktdrho_T();
5035  S_boundary[7]= GetFluidModel()->GetdktdT_rho();
5036 
5037  visc_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
5038 
5039  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
5040 
5041  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
5042  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
5043  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
5044 
5045  /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
5046 
5047  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
5048  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
5049 
5050  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
5051 
5052  if (implicit)
5053  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
5054 
5055  }
5056 
5057  }
5058  }
5059  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
5060 
5061  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
5062  delete [] Normal;
5063  delete [] Velocity_e;
5064  delete [] Velocity_b;
5065  delete [] Velocity_i;
5066  delete [] FlowDirMix;
5067 
5068  delete [] S_boundary;
5069  delete [] Lambda_i;
5070  delete [] u_i;
5071  delete [] u_e;
5072  delete [] u_b;
5073  delete [] dw;
5074 
5075  delete [] Residual;
5076 
5077  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5078  {
5079  delete [] P_Tensor[iVar];
5080  delete [] invP_Tensor[iVar];
5081  delete [] Jacobian_i[iVar];
5082  }
5083  delete [] P_Tensor;
5084  delete [] invP_Tensor;
5085  delete [] Jacobian_i;
5086 
5087 }
5088 
5089 
5090 void CEulerSolver::BC_TurboRiemann(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
5091  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
5092  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
5093 
5094  unsigned short iDim, iVar, jVar, kVar, iSpan;
5095  unsigned long iPoint, Point_Normal, oldVertex, iVertex;
5096  const su2double *Flow_Dir;
5097  su2double P_Total, T_Total;
5098  su2double *Velocity_b, Velocity2_b, Enthalpy_b, Energy_b, StaticEnergy_b, Density_b, Kappa_b, Chi_b, Pressure_b, Temperature_b;
5099  su2double *Velocity_e, Velocity2_e, Enthalpy_e, Entropy_e, Energy_e = 0.0, StaticEnthalpy_e, StaticEnergy_e, Density_e = 0.0, Pressure_e;
5100  su2double *Velocity_i, Velocity2_i, Enthalpy_i, Energy_i, StaticEnergy_i, Density_i, Kappa_i, Chi_i, Pressure_i, SoundSpeed_i;
5101  su2double ProjVelocity_i;
5102  su2double **P_Tensor, **invP_Tensor, *Lambda_i, **Jacobian_b, **Jacobian_i, **DubDu, *dw, *u_e, *u_i, *u_b;
5103  su2double *gridVel, *Residual;
5104  su2double *V_boundary, *V_domain, *S_boundary, *S_domain;
5105  su2double AverageEnthalpy, AverageEntropy;
5106  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
5107  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
5108  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
5109  unsigned short nSpanWiseSections = geometry->GetnSpanWiseSections(config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker));
5110  bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
5111  bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce());
5112  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
5113 
5114  su2double *Normal, *turboNormal, *UnitNormal, *FlowDirMix, FlowDirMixMag, *turboVelocity;
5115  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
5116  turboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5117  UnitNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5118 
5119  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
5120  Velocity_b = new su2double[nDim];
5121  Velocity_e = new su2double[nDim];
5122  turboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
5123  FlowDirMix = new su2double[nDim];
5124  Lambda_i = new su2double[nVar];
5125  u_i = new su2double[nVar];
5126  u_e = new su2double[nVar];
5127  u_b = new su2double[nVar];
5128  dw = new su2double[nVar];
5129 
5130  Residual = new su2double[nVar];
5131 
5132  S_boundary = new su2double[8];
5133 
5134  P_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
5135  invP_Tensor = new su2double*[nVar];
5136  Jacobian_i = new su2double*[nVar];
5137  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5138  {
5139  P_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5140  invP_Tensor[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5141  Jacobian_i[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5142  }
5143 
5144  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
5145  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections; iSpan++){
5146 
5147  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
5148  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(val_marker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
5149 
5150  /*--- using the other vertex information for retrieving some information ---*/
5151  oldVertex = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetOldVertex();
5152  V_boundary= GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, oldVertex);
5153 
5154  /*--- Index of the closest interior node ---*/
5155  Point_Normal = geometry->vertex[val_marker][oldVertex]->GetNormal_Neighbor();
5156 
5157  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention),
5158  * this normal is scaled with the area of the face of the element ---*/
5159  geometry->vertex[val_marker][oldVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
5160  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
5161  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
5162 
5163  /*--- find the node related to the vertex ---*/
5164  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
5165  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)){
5166 
5167  /*--- Normalize Normal vector for this vertex (already for outward convention) ---*/
5168  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
5169  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(turboNormal);
5170 
5171  /*--- Retrieve solution at this boundary node ---*/
5172  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
5173 
5174  /* --- Compute the internal state u_i --- */
5175  Velocity2_i = 0;
5176  for (iDim=0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5177  {
5178  Velocity_i[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
5179  Velocity2_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*Velocity_i[iDim];
5180  }
5181 
5182  Density_i = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
5183 
5184  Energy_i = nodes->GetEnergy(iPoint);
5185  StaticEnergy_i = Energy_i - 0.5*Velocity2_i;
5186 
5187  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_i, StaticEnergy_i);
5188 
5189  Pressure_i = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
5190  Enthalpy_i = Energy_i + Pressure_i/Density_i;
5191 
5192  SoundSpeed_i = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
5193 
5194  Kappa_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_i;
5195  Chi_i = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_i * StaticEnergy_i;
5196 
5197  ProjVelocity_i = 0.0;
5198  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5199  ProjVelocity_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
5200 
5201  /*--- Build the external state u_e from boundary data and internal node ---*/
5202 
5203  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Riemann(Marker_Tag))
5204  {
5205  //TODO(turbo), generilize for 3D case
5206  //TODO(turbo), generilize for Inlet and Outlet in for backflow treatment
5207  //TODO(turbo), implement not uniform inlet and radial equilibrium for the outlet
5208  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT:
5209 
5210  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this boundary. ---*/
5211  if (gravity) P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;/// check in which case is true (only freesurface?)
5212  else P_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5213  T_Total = config->GetRiemann_Var2(Marker_Tag);
5214  Flow_Dir = config->GetRiemann_FlowDir(Marker_Tag);
5215 
5216  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
5217  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5218  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
5219 
5220  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
5221  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_Total, T_Total);
5222  Enthalpy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy()+ GetFluidModel()->GetPressure()/GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5223  Entropy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
5224 
5225  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5226  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
5227  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5228  turboVelocity[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*Flow_Dir[iDim];
5229  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity,turboNormal, Velocity_e, config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker),config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
5230  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5231  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
5232  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5233  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
5234  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5235  if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
5236  break;
5237 
5238  case MIXING_IN:
5239 
5240  /* --- compute total averaged quantities ---*/
5241  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan], ExtAverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan]);
5242  AverageEnthalpy = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan]/ExtAverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan];
5243  AverageEntropy = GetFluidModel()->GetEntropy();
5244 
5245  FlowDirMixMag = 0;
5246  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5247  FlowDirMixMag += ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim]*ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim];
5248  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
5249  FlowDirMix[iDim] = ExtAverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][iDim]/sqrt(FlowDirMixMag);
5250  }
5251 
5252 
5253  /* --- Computes the total state --- */
5254  Enthalpy_e = AverageEnthalpy;
5255  Entropy_e = AverageEntropy;
5256 
5257  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5258  Velocity2_e = Velocity2_i;
5259  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
5260  turboVelocity[iDim] = sqrt(Velocity2_e)*FlowDirMix[iDim];
5261 
5262  }
5263  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity,turboNormal, Velocity_e, config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker),config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
5264 
5265  StaticEnthalpy_e = Enthalpy_e - 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5266  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_hs(StaticEnthalpy_e, Entropy_e);
5267  Density_e = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
5268  StaticEnergy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy();
5269  Energy_e = StaticEnergy_e + 0.5 * Velocity2_e;
5270  // if (tkeNeeded) Energy_e += GetTke_Inf();
5271  break;
5272 
5273 
5274  case MIXING_OUT:
5275 
5276  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
5277  Pressure_e = ExtAveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan];
5278  Density_e = Density_i;
5279 
5280  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5281  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
5282  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
5283  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5284  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
5285  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
5286  }
5287  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
5288  break;
5289 
5290  case STATIC_PRESSURE:
5291 
5292  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
5293  Pressure_e = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag);
5294  Pressure_e /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
5295  Density_e = Density_i;
5296 
5297  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5298  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
5299  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
5300  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5301  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
5302  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
5303  }
5304  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
5305  break;
5306 
5307 
5308  case RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM:
5309 
5310  /*--- Retrieve the static pressure for this boundary. ---*/
5311  Pressure_e = RadialEquilibriumPressure[val_marker][iSpan];
5312  Density_e = Density_i;
5313 
5314  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5315  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_e, Density_e);
5316  Velocity2_e = 0.0;
5317  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
5318  Velocity_e[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
5319  Velocity2_e += Velocity_e[iDim]*Velocity_e[iDim];
5320  }
5321  Energy_e = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_e;
5322  break;
5323 
5324  default:
5325  SU2_MPI::Error("Invalid Riemann input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
5326  break;
5327  }
5328 
5329  /*--- Compute P (matrix of right eigenvectors) ---*/
5330  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix(&Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Enthalpy_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal, P_Tensor);
5331 
5332  /*--- Compute inverse P (matrix of left eigenvectors)---*/
5333  conv_numerics->GetPMatrix_inv(invP_Tensor, &Density_i, Velocity_i, &SoundSpeed_i, &Chi_i, &Kappa_i, UnitNormal);
5334 
5335  /*--- eigenvalues contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5336  if (dynamic_grid){
5337  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5338 
5339  su2double ProjGridVel = 0.0;
5340  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5341  ProjGridVel += gridVel[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
5342  ProjVelocity_i -= ProjGridVel;
5343  }
5344 
5345  /*--- Flow eigenvalues ---*/
5346  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5347  Lambda_i[iDim] = ProjVelocity_i;
5348  Lambda_i[nVar-2] = ProjVelocity_i + SoundSpeed_i;
5349  Lambda_i[nVar-1] = ProjVelocity_i - SoundSpeed_i;
5350 
5351  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_e --- */
5352  u_e[0] = Density_e;
5353  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5354  u_e[iDim+1] = Velocity_e[iDim]*Density_e;
5355  u_e[nVar-1] = Energy_e*Density_e;
5356 
5357  /* --- Compute the boundary state u_i --- */
5358  u_i[0] = Density_i;
5359  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5360  u_i[iDim+1] = Velocity_i[iDim]*Density_i;
5361  u_i[nVar-1] = Energy_i*Density_i;
5362 
5363  /*--- Compute the characteristic jumps ---*/
5364  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5365  {
5366  dw[iVar] = 0;
5367  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5368  dw[iVar] += invP_Tensor[iVar][jVar] * (u_e[jVar] - u_i[jVar]);
5369 
5370  }
5371 
5372  /*--- Compute the boundary state u_b using characteristics ---*/
5373  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5374  {
5375  u_b[iVar] = u_i[iVar];
5376 
5377  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5378  {
5379  if (Lambda_i[jVar] < 0)
5380  {
5381  u_b[iVar] += P_Tensor[iVar][jVar]*dw[jVar];
5382 
5383  }
5384  }
5385  }
5386 
5387 
5388  /*--- Compute the thermodynamic state in u_b ---*/
5389  Density_b = u_b[0];
5390  Velocity2_b = 0;
5391  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5392  {
5393  Velocity_b[iDim] = u_b[iDim+1]/Density_b;
5394  Velocity2_b += Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
5395  }
5396  Energy_b = u_b[nVar-1]/Density_b;
5397  StaticEnergy_b = Energy_b - 0.5*Velocity2_b;
5398  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_rhoe(Density_b, StaticEnergy_b);
5399  Pressure_b = GetFluidModel()->GetPressure();
5400  Temperature_b = GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
5401  Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
5402  Kappa_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho() / Density_b;
5403  Chi_b = GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e() - Kappa_b * StaticEnergy_b;
5404 
5405  /*--- Compute the residuals ---*/
5406  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjFlux(&Density_b, Velocity_b, &Pressure_b, &Enthalpy_b, Normal, Residual);
5407 
5408  /*--- Residual contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5409  if (dynamic_grid) {
5410  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5411  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
5412 
5413  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5414  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
5415  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5416  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *(u_b[iVar]);
5417  }
5418 
5419  if (implicit) {
5420 
5421  Jacobian_b = new su2double*[nVar];
5422  DubDu = new su2double*[nVar];
5423  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5424  {
5425  Jacobian_b[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5426  DubDu[iVar] = new su2double[nVar];
5427  }
5428 
5429  /*--- Initialize DubDu to unit matrix---*/
5430 
5431  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5432  {
5433  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
5434  DubDu[iVar][jVar]= 0;
5435 
5436  DubDu[iVar][iVar]= 1;
5437  }
5438 
5439  /*--- Compute DubDu -= RNL---*/
5440  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
5441  {
5442  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
5443  {
5444  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++)
5445  {
5446  if (Lambda_i[kVar]<0)
5447  DubDu[iVar][jVar] -= P_Tensor[iVar][kVar] * invP_Tensor[kVar][jVar];
5448  }
5449  }
5450  }
5451 
5452  /*--- Compute flux Jacobian in state b ---*/
5453  conv_numerics->GetInviscidProjJac(Velocity_b, &Enthalpy_b, &Chi_b, &Kappa_b, Normal, 1.0, Jacobian_b);
5454 
5455  /*--- Jacobian contribution due to grid motion ---*/
5456  if (dynamic_grid)
5457  {
5458  gridVel = geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint);
5459  su2double projVelocity = 0.0;
5460  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5461  projVelocity += gridVel[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
5462  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++){
5463  Residual[iVar] -= projVelocity *(u_b[iVar]);
5464  Jacobian_b[iVar][iVar] -= projVelocity;
5465  }
5466 
5467  }
5468 
5469  /*--- initiate Jacobian_i to zero matrix ---*/
5470  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++)
5471  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++)
5472  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] = 0.0;
5473 
5474  /*--- Compute numerical flux Jacobian at node i ---*/
5475  for (iVar=0; iVar<nVar; iVar++) {
5476  for (jVar=0; jVar<nVar; jVar++) {
5477  for (kVar=0; kVar<nVar; kVar++) {
5478  Jacobian_i[iVar][jVar] += Jacobian_b[iVar][kVar] * DubDu[kVar][jVar];
5479  }
5480  }
5481  }
5482 
5483  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
5484  delete [] Jacobian_b[iVar];
5485  delete [] DubDu[iVar];
5486  }
5487  delete [] Jacobian_b;
5488  delete [] DubDu;
5489  }
5490 
5491  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
5492  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, Residual);
5493 
5494  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
5495  if (implicit)
5496  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, Jacobian_i);
5497 
5498  /*--- Viscous contribution ---*/
5499 
5500  if (viscous) {
5501 
5502  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
5503 
5504  V_boundary[0] = Temperature_b;
5505  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5506  V_boundary[iDim+1] = Velocity_b[iDim];
5507  V_boundary[nDim+1] = Pressure_b;
5508  V_boundary[nDim+2] = Density_b;
5509  V_boundary[nDim+3] = Enthalpy_b;
5510 
5511  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
5512 
5513  V_boundary[nDim+5] = GetFluidModel()->GetLaminarViscosity();
5514  V_boundary[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
5515  V_boundary[nDim+7] = GetFluidModel()->GetThermalConductivity();
5516  V_boundary[nDim+8] = GetFluidModel()->GetCp();
5517 
5518  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
5519 
5520  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
5521  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
5522  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
5523  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5524  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
5525 
5526  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
5527 
5528  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
5529  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
5530 
5531  /*--- Secondary variables ---*/
5532 
5533  S_domain = nodes->GetSecondary(iPoint);
5534 
5535  /*--- Compute secondary thermodynamic properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5536 
5537  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
5538  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
5539 
5540  S_boundary[2]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTdrho_e();
5541  S_boundary[3]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTde_rho();
5542 
5543  /*--- Compute secondary thermo-physical properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
5544 
5545  S_boundary[4]= GetFluidModel()->Getdmudrho_T();
5546  S_boundary[5]= GetFluidModel()->GetdmudT_rho();
5547 
5548  S_boundary[6]= GetFluidModel()->Getdktdrho_T();
5549  S_boundary[7]= GetFluidModel()->GetdktdT_rho();
5550 
5551  visc_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
5552 
5553  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
5554 
5555  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
5556  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
5557  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
5558 
5559  /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
5560 
5561  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
5562  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
5563 
5564  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
5565 
5566  if (implicit)
5567  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
5568 
5569  }
5570  }
5571  }
5572  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
5573  }
5574 
5575  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
5576  delete [] Normal;
5577  delete [] UnitNormal;
5578  delete [] turboNormal;
5579  delete [] turboVelocity;
5580  delete [] Velocity_e;
5581  delete [] Velocity_b;
5582  delete [] Velocity_i;
5583  delete [] FlowDirMix;
5584 
5585  delete [] S_boundary;
5586  delete [] Lambda_i;
5587  delete [] u_i;
5588  delete [] u_e;
5589  delete [] u_b;
5590  delete [] dw;
5591 
5592  delete [] Residual;
5593 
5594  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
5595  {
5596  delete [] P_Tensor[iVar];
5597  delete [] invP_Tensor[iVar];
5598  delete [] Jacobian_i[iVar];
5599  }
5600  delete [] P_Tensor;
5601  delete [] invP_Tensor;
5602  delete [] Jacobian_i;
5603 
5604 }

5606 void CEulerSolver::PreprocessBC_Giles(CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, CNumerics *conv_numerics, unsigned short marker_flag) {
5607  /* Implementation of Fuorier Transformations for non-regfelcting BC will come soon */
5608  su2double cj_inf,cj_out1, cj_out2, Density_i, Pressure_i, *turboNormal, *turboVelocity, *Velocity_i, AverageSoundSpeed;
5609  su2double *deltaprim, *cj, TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch, pitch, theta, deltaTheta;
5610  unsigned short iMarker, iSpan, iMarkerTP, iDim;
5611  unsigned long iPoint, kend_max, k, iVertex;
5612  long freq;
5613  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
5614  unsigned short nSpanWiseSections = geometry->GetnSpanWiseSections(marker_flag);
5615  turboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5616  turboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
5617  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
5618  deltaprim = new su2double[nVar];
5619  cj = new su2double[nVar];
5620  complex<su2double> I, expArg;
5621  static complex<su2double> cktemp_inf, cktemp_out1, cktemp_out2;
5622  I = complex<su2double>(0.0,1.0);
5623 
5624  kend_max = geometry->GetnFreqSpanMax(marker_flag);
5625  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections ; iSpan++){
5626  for(k=0; k < 2*kend_max+1; k++){
5627  freq = k - kend_max;
5628  SU2_OMP_MASTER
5629  {
5630  cktemp_inf = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5631  cktemp_out1 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5632  cktemp_out2 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5633  } END_SU2_OMP_MASTER
5634  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
5635  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
5636  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
5637  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
5638  complex<su2double> cktemp_inf_local{0.,0.},cktemp_out1_local{0.,0.}, cktemp_out2_local{0.,0.};
5639  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(roundUpDiv(geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan), 2*omp_get_max_threads()))
5640  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
5641 
5642  /*--- find the node related to the vertex ---*/
5643  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
5644 
5645  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(turboNormal);
5646  /*--- Compute the internal state _i ---*/
5647 
5648  Pressure_i = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
5649  Density_i = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
5650  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
5651  {
5652  Velocity_i[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
5653  }
5654  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity_i, turboNormal, turboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
5655 
5656  if(nDim ==2){
5657  deltaprim[0] = Density_i - AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
5658  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0];
5659  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][1];
5660  deltaprim[3] = Pressure_i - AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
5661  }
5662  else{
5663  //Here 3d
5664  deltaprim[0] = Density_i - AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
5665  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0];
5666  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][1];
5667  deltaprim[3] = turboVelocity[2] - AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][2]; //New char
5668  deltaprim[4] = Pressure_i - AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
5669  }
5670 
5671  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan], AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan]);
5672  AverageSoundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
5673  conv_numerics->GetCharJump(AverageSoundSpeed, AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan], deltaprim, cj);
5674 
5675  /*-----this is only valid 2D ----*/
5676  if(nDim ==2){
5677  cj_out1 = cj[1];
5678  cj_out2 = cj[2];
5679  cj_inf = cj[3];
5680  }
5681  else{
5682  //Here 3D
5683  cj_out1 = cj[1];
5684  cj_out2 = cj[3];
5685  cj_inf = cj[4];
5686  }
5687  pitch = geometry->GetMaxAngularCoord(iMarker, iSpan) - geometry->GetMinAngularCoord(iMarker,iSpan);
5688  theta = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetRelAngularCoord();
5689  deltaTheta = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetDeltaAngularCoord();
5690  TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch = 2*PI_NUMBER*freq*theta/pitch;
5691 
5692  expArg = complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)) - I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch));
5693  if (freq != 0){
5694  cktemp_out1_local += cj_out1*expArg*deltaTheta/pitch;
5695  cktemp_out2_local += cj_out2*expArg*deltaTheta/pitch;
5696  cktemp_inf_local += cj_inf*expArg*deltaTheta/pitch;
5697  }
5698  else{
5699  cktemp_inf_local += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5700  cktemp_out1_local += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5701  cktemp_out2_local += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5702  }
5703  }
5704  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
5705  SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
5706  {
5707  cktemp_inf += cktemp_inf_local;
5708  cktemp_out1 += cktemp_out1_local;
5709  cktemp_out2 += cktemp_out2_local;
5710  } END_SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
5711  }
5712  }
5713  }
5714  }
5715 
5716  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
5717  {
5718 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
5719  su2double MyRe_inf = cktemp_inf.real(); su2double Re_inf = 0.0;
5720  su2double MyIm_inf = cktemp_inf.imag(); su2double Im_inf = 0.0;
5721  cktemp_inf = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5722 
5723  su2double MyRe_out1 = cktemp_out1.real(); su2double Re_out1 = 0.0;
5724  su2double MyIm_out1 = cktemp_out1.imag(); su2double Im_out1 = 0.0;
5725  cktemp_out1 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5726 
5727  su2double MyRe_out2 = cktemp_out2.real(); su2double Re_out2 = 0.0;
5728  su2double MyIm_out2 = cktemp_out2.imag(); su2double Im_out2 = 0.0;
5729  cktemp_out2 = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
5730 
5731 
5732  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyRe_inf, &Re_inf, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
5733  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyIm_inf, &Im_inf, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
5734  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyRe_out1, &Re_out1, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
5735  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyIm_out1, &Im_out1, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
5736  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyRe_out2, &Re_out2, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
5737  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyIm_out2, &Im_out2, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
5738 
5739  cktemp_inf = complex<su2double>(Re_inf,Im_inf);
5740  cktemp_out1 = complex<su2double>(Re_out1,Im_out1);
5741  cktemp_out2 = complex<su2double>(Re_out2,Im_out2);
5742 #endif
5743 
5744  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
5745  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
5746  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
5747  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
5748  /*-----this is only valid 2D ----*/
5749  if (marker_flag == INFLOW){
5750  CkInflow[iMarker][iSpan][k]= cktemp_inf;
5751  }else{
5752  CkOutflow1[iMarker][iSpan][k]=cktemp_out1;
5753  CkOutflow2[iMarker][iSpan][k]=cktemp_out2;
5754  }
5755  }
5756  }
5757  }
5758  }
5759  } END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
5760  }
5761  }
5762 
5763  delete [] turboVelocity;
5764  delete [] turboNormal;
5765  delete [] Velocity_i;
5766  delete [] deltaprim;
5767  delete [] cj;
5768 
5769 }

5771 void CEulerSolver::BC_Giles(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics,
5772  CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
5773 
5774  unsigned short iDim, iVar, jVar, iSpan;
5775  unsigned long iPoint, Point_Normal, oldVertex, k, kend, kend_max, iVertex;
5776  su2double *UnitNormal, *turboVelocity, *turboNormal;
5777 
5778  su2double *Velocity_b, Velocity2_b, Enthalpy_b, Energy_b, Density_b, Pressure_b, Temperature_b;
5779  su2double *Velocity_i, Velocity2_i, Energy_i, StaticEnergy_i, Density_i, Pressure_i;
5780  su2double Pressure_e;

5783  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
5784  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);

5786  unsigned short nSpanWiseSections = geometry->GetnSpanWiseSections(config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker));
5787  su2double relfacAvgCfg = config->GetGiles_RelaxFactorAverage(Marker_Tag);
5788  su2double relfacFouCfg = config->GetGiles_RelaxFactorFourier(Marker_Tag);
5789  su2double *Normal;
5790  su2double TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch, pitch,theta;
5791  const su2double *SpanWiseValues = nullptr, *FlowDir;
5792  su2double spanPercent, extrarelfacAvg = 0.0, deltaSpan = 0.0, relfacAvg, relfacFou, coeffrelfacAvg = 0.0;
5793  unsigned short Turbo_Flag;
5794 
5795  Normal = new su2double[nDim];
5796  turboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5797  UnitNormal = new su2double[nDim];
5798  turboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
5799  Velocity_i = new su2double[nDim];
5800  Velocity_b = new su2double[nDim];
5801 
5802 
5803  su2double AverageSoundSpeed, *AverageTurboMach, AverageEntropy, AverageEnthalpy;
5804  AverageTurboMach = new su2double[nDim];
5805  S_boundary = new su2double[8];
5806 
5807  su2double AvgMach , *cj, GilesBeta, *delta_c, **R_Matrix, *deltaprim, **R_c_inv,**R_c, alphaIn_BC, gammaIn_BC = 0,
5808  P_Total, T_Total, Enthalpy_BC, Entropy_BC, *R, *c_avg,*dcjs, Beta_inf2, c2js_Re, c3js_Re, cOutjs_Re, avgVel2 =0.0;
5809 
5810  long freq;
5811

5838  /*--- Compute coeff for under relaxation of Avg and Fourier Coefficient for hub and shroud---*/
5839  if (nDim == 3){
5840  extrarelfacAvg = config->GetExtraRelFacGiles(0);
5841  spanPercent = config->GetExtraRelFacGiles(1);

5843  SpanWiseValues = geometry->GetSpanWiseValue(Turbo_Flag);
5844  deltaSpan = SpanWiseValues[nSpanWiseSections-1]*spanPercent;
5845  coeffrelfacAvg = (relfacAvgCfg - extrarelfacAvg)/deltaSpan;
5846  }

5852  relfacAvg = extrarelfacAvg + coeffrelfacAvg*(SpanWiseValues[iSpan] - SpanWiseValues[0]);
5853  relfacFou = 0.0;
5854  }
5855  else if(SpanWiseValues[iSpan] >= SpanWiseValues[nSpanWiseSections -1] - deltaSpan){
5856  relfacAvg = extrarelfacAvg - coeffrelfacAvg*(SpanWiseValues[iSpan] - SpanWiseValues[nSpanWiseSections -1]);
5857  relfacFou = 0.0;
5858  }
5859  else{
5860  relfacAvg = relfacAvgCfg;
5861  relfacFou = relfacFouCfg;
5862  }
5863  }
5864  else{
5865  {
5866  relfacAvg = relfacAvgCfg;
5867  relfacFou = relfacFouCfg;
5868  }
5869  }

5878  }

5939  }

6082  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6083 
6084  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
6085  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(val_marker,iSpan); iVertex++) {

6101  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
6102 
6103  /*--- Normalize Normal vector for this vertex (already for outward convention) ---*/
6104  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
6105  geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(turboNormal);

6108  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);

6112 
6113

6115  Velocity2_i = 0;
6116  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6117  {

6119  Velocity2_i += Velocity_i[iDim]*Velocity_i[iDim];
6120  }
6121

6124

6133  if (nDim == 2){
6134  deltaprim[0] = Density_i - AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan];
6135  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0];
6136  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1];
6137  deltaprim[3] = Pressure_i - AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan];
6138  }
6139  else{

6141  deltaprim[1] = turboVelocity[0] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0];
6142  deltaprim[2] = turboVelocity[1] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1];
6143  deltaprim[3] = turboVelocity[2] - AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][2];
