6150 
6151 
6152  pitch = geometry->GetMaxAngularCoord(val_marker, iSpan) - geometry->GetMinAngularCoord(val_marker,iSpan);
6153  theta = geometry->turbovertex[val_marker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetRelAngularCoord();
6154 
6155  switch(config->GetKind_Data_Giles(Marker_Tag))
6156  {
6157 
6158  //Done, generilize for 3D case
6159  //TODO(turbo), generilize for Inlet and Outlet in for backflow treatment
6160 
6161  case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT: case MIXING_IN:case TOTAL_CONDITIONS_PT_1D: case MIXING_IN_1D:
6162  if(config->GetSpatialFourier()){
6163  if (AvgMach <= 1.0){
6164  Beta_inf= I*complex<su2double>(sqrt(1.0 - AvgMach));
6165  c2js = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6166  c3js = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6167  for(k=0; k < 2*kend_max+1; k++){
6168  freq = k - kend_max;
6169  if(freq >= (long)(-kend) && freq <= (long)(kend) && AverageTurboMach[0] > config->GetAverageMachLimit()){
6170  TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch = 2*PI_NUMBER*freq*theta/pitch;
6171 
6172  c2ks = -CkInflow[val_marker][iSpan][k]*complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6173  c3ks = CkInflow[val_marker][iSpan][k]*complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6174  c3ks *= complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6175  c2js += c2ks*(complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch))+I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)));
6176  c3js += c3ks*(complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch))+I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)));
6177  }
6178  else{
6179  c2js += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6180  c3js += complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6181  }
6182  }
6183  c2js_Re = c2js.real();
6184  c3js_Re = c3js.real();
6185 
6186  if (nDim == 2){
6187  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6188  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6189  dcjs[2] = c3js_Re - cj[2];
6190  }else{
6191  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6192  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6193  dcjs[2] = 0.0 - cj[2];
6194  dcjs[3] = c3js_Re - cj[3];
6195  }
6196 
6197  }else{
6198  if (AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] >= 0.0){
6199  Beta_inf2= -sqrt(AvgMach - 1.0);
6200  }else{
6201  Beta_inf2= sqrt(AvgMach-1.0);
6202  }
6203  if (nDim == 2){
6204  c2js_Re = -cj[3]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6205  c3js_Re = cj[3]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6206  c3js_Re *= (Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6207  }else{
6208  c2js_Re = -cj[4]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6209  c3js_Re = cj[4]*(Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6210  c3js_Re *= (Beta_inf2 + AverageTurboMach[1])/( 1.0 + AverageTurboMach[0]);
6211  }
6212 
6213 
6214  if (nDim == 2){
6215  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6216  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6217  dcjs[2] = c3js_Re - cj[2];
6218  }else{
6219  dcjs[0] = 0.0 - cj[0];
6220  dcjs[1] = c2js_Re - cj[1];
6221  dcjs[2] = 0.0 - cj[2];
6222  dcjs[3] = c3js_Re - cj[3];
6223  }
6224  }
6225  }
6226  else{
6227  if (nDim == 2){
6228  dcjs[0] = 0.0;
6229  dcjs[1] = 0.0;
6230  dcjs[2] = 0.0;
6231  }else{
6232  dcjs[0] = 0.0;
6233  dcjs[1] = 0.0;
6234  dcjs[2] = 0.0;
6235  dcjs[3] = 0.0;
6236  }
6237  }
6238  /* --- Impose Inlet BC Reflecting--- */
6239  delta_c[0] = relfacAvg*c_avg[0] + relfacFou*dcjs[0];
6240  delta_c[1] = relfacAvg*c_avg[1] + relfacFou*dcjs[1];
6241  delta_c[2] = relfacAvg*c_avg[2] + relfacFou*dcjs[2];
6242  if (nDim == 2){
6243  delta_c[3] = cj[3];
6244  }else{
6245  delta_c[3] = relfacAvg*c_avg[3] + relfacFou*dcjs[3];
6246  delta_c[4] = cj[4];
6247  }
6248  break;
6249 
6250 
6251  case STATIC_PRESSURE:case STATIC_PRESSURE_1D:case MIXING_OUT:case RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM:case MIXING_OUT_1D:
6252 
6253  /* --- implementation of Giles BC---*/
6254  if(config->GetSpatialFourier()){
6255  if (AvgMach > 1.0){
6256  /* --- supersonic Giles implementation ---*/
6257  if (AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] >= 0.0){
6258  GilesBeta= -sqrt(AvgMach - 1.0);
6259 
6260  }else{
6261  GilesBeta= sqrt(AvgMach - 1.0);
6262  }
6263  if(nDim == 2){
6264  cOutjs_Re= (2.0 * AverageTurboMach[0])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[1] - (GilesBeta + AverageTurboMach[1])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[2];
6265  }
6266  else{
6267  cOutjs_Re= (2.0 * AverageTurboMach[0])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[1] - (GilesBeta + AverageTurboMach[1])/(GilesBeta - AverageTurboMach[1])*cj[3];
6268  }
6269  if (nDim == 2){
6270  dcjs[3] = cOutjs_Re - cj[3];
6271  }
6272  else{
6273  dcjs[4] = cOutjs_Re - cj[4];
6274  }
6275  }else{
6276 
6277  /* --- subsonic Giles implementation ---*/
6278  Beta_inf= I*complex<su2double>(sqrt(1.0 - AvgMach));
6279  cOutjs = complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6280  for(k=0; k < 2*kend_max+1; k++){
6281  freq = k - kend_max;
6282  if(freq >= (long)(-kend) && freq <= (long)(kend) && AverageTurboMach[0] > config->GetAverageMachLimit()){
6283  TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch = 2*PI_NUMBER*freq*theta/pitch;
6284  cOutks = complex<su2double>(2.0 * AverageTurboMach[0])/complex<su2double>(Beta_inf - AverageTurboMach[1])*CkOutflow1[val_marker][iSpan][k];
6285  cOutks -= complex<su2double>(Beta_inf + AverageTurboMach[1])/complex<su2double>(Beta_inf - AverageTurboMach[1])*CkOutflow2[val_marker][iSpan][k];
6286 
6287  cOutjs += cOutks*(complex<su2double>(cos(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)) + I*complex<su2double>(sin(TwoPiThetaFreq_Pitch)));
6288  }
6289  else{
6290  cOutjs +=complex<su2double>(0.0,0.0);
6291  }
6292  }
6293  cOutjs_Re = cOutjs.real();
6294 
6295  if (nDim == 2){
6296  dcjs[3] = cOutjs_Re - cj[3];
6297  }
6298  else{
6299  dcjs[4] = cOutjs_Re - cj[4];
6300  }
6301  }
6302  }
6303  else{
6304  if (nDim == 2){
6305  dcjs[3] = 0.0;
6306  }
6307  else{
6308  dcjs[4] = 0.0;
6309  }
6310  }
6311  /* --- Impose Outlet BC Non-Reflecting --- */
6312  delta_c[0] = cj[0];
6313  delta_c[1] = cj[1];
6314  delta_c[2] = cj[2];
6315  if (nDim == 2){
6316  delta_c[3] = relfacAvg*c_avg[3] + relfacFou*dcjs[3];
6317  }
6318  else{
6319  delta_c[3] = cj[3];
6320  delta_c[4] = relfacAvg*c_avg[4] + relfacFou*dcjs[4];
6321  }
6322 
6323 
6324  /*--- Automatically impose supersonic autoflow ---*/
6325  if (abs(AverageTurboMach[0]) > 1.0000){
6326  delta_c[0] = 0.0;
6327  delta_c[1] = 0.0;
6328  delta_c[2] = 0.0;
6329  delta_c[2] = 0.0;
6330  if (nDim == 3)delta_c[4] = 0.0;
6331  }
6332 
6333  break;
6334 
6335  default:
6336  SU2_MPI::Error("Invalid Giles input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
6337  break;
6338  }
6339 
6340  /*--- Compute primitive jump from characteristic variables ---*/
6341  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6342  {
6343  deltaprim[iVar]=0.0;
6344  for (jVar = 0; jVar < nVar; jVar++)
6345  {
6346  deltaprim[iVar] += R_Matrix[iVar][jVar]*delta_c[jVar];
6347  }
6348  }
6349 
6350  /*--- retrieve boundary variables ---*/
6351  Density_b = AverageDensity[val_marker][iSpan] + deltaprim[0];
6352  turboVelocity[0] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][0] + deltaprim[1];
6353  turboVelocity[1] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][1] + deltaprim[2];
6354  if(nDim == 2){
6355  Pressure_b = AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan] + deltaprim[3];
6356  }
6357  else{
6358  turboVelocity[2] = AverageTurboVelocity[val_marker][iSpan][2] + deltaprim[3];
6359  Pressure_b = AveragePressure[val_marker][iSpan] + deltaprim[4];
6360  }
6361 
6362 
6363  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity, turboNormal, Velocity_b, config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(val_marker), config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
6364  Velocity2_b = 0.0;
6365  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6366  Velocity2_b+= Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
6367  }
6368 
6369  if(Pressure_b <= 0.0 || Density_b <= 0.0 ){
6370  Pressure_b = Pressure_i;
6371  Density_b = Density_i;
6372  Velocity2_b = 0.0;
6373  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6374  Velocity_b[iDim] = Velocity_i[iDim];
6375  Velocity2_b+= Velocity_b[iDim]*Velocity_b[iDim];
6376  }
6377  }
6378 
6379  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_b, Density_b);
6380  Energy_b = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + 0.5*Velocity2_b;
6381  Temperature_b= GetFluidModel()->GetTemperature();
6382  Enthalpy_b = Energy_b + Pressure_b/Density_b;
6383 
6384  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
6385  V_boundary[0] = Temperature_b;
6386  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6387  V_boundary[iDim+1] = Velocity_b[iDim];
6388  V_boundary[nDim+1] = Pressure_b;
6389  V_boundary[nDim+2] = Density_b;
6390  V_boundary[nDim+3] = Enthalpy_b;
6391 
6392  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
6393  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
6394 
6395 
6396 
6397  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
6398 
6399  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
6400  conv_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
6401 
6402 
6403  if (dynamic_grid)
6404  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
6405 
6406  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
6407 
6408  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6409 
6410  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
6411  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
6412 
6413  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
6414  if (implicit)
6415  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
6416 
6417  /*--- Viscous contribution ---*/
6418 
6419  if (viscous) {
6420 
6421  /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
6422 
6423  V_boundary[nDim+5] = GetFluidModel()->GetLaminarViscosity();
6424  V_boundary[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
6425  V_boundary[nDim+7] = GetFluidModel()->GetThermalConductivity();
6426  V_boundary[nDim+8] = GetFluidModel()->GetCp();
6427 
6428  /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
6429 
6430  visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6431  su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
6432  GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
6433  geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6434  visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6435 
6436  /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
6437 
6438  visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_boundary);
6439  visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
6440 
6441 
6442  /*--- Compute secondary thermodynamic properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
6443 
6444  S_boundary[0]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPdrho_e();
6445  S_boundary[1]= GetFluidModel()->GetdPde_rho();
6446 
6447  S_boundary[2]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTdrho_e();
6448  S_boundary[3]= GetFluidModel()->GetdTde_rho();
6449 
6450  /*--- Compute secondary thermo-physical properties (partial derivatives...) ---*/
6451 
6452  S_boundary[4]= GetFluidModel()->Getdmudrho_T();
6453  S_boundary[5]= GetFluidModel()->GetdmudT_rho();
6454 
6455  S_boundary[6]= GetFluidModel()->Getdktdrho_T();
6456  S_boundary[7]= GetFluidModel()->GetdktdT_rho();
6457 
6458  visc_numerics->SetSecondary(S_domain, S_boundary);
6459 
6460  /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
6461 
6462  if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
6463  visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
6464  solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
6465 
6466  /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
6467 
6468  auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6469  LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
6470 
6471  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
6472 
6473  if (implicit)
6474  Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
6475 
6476  }
6477 
6478  }
6479  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
6480  }
6481 
6482  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
6483  delete [] Normal;
6484 
6485  delete [] Velocity_b;
6486  delete [] Velocity_i;
6487 
6488  delete [] S_boundary;
6489  delete [] delta_c;
6490  delete [] deltaprim;
6491  delete [] cj;
6492  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++)
6493  {
6494  delete [] R_Matrix[iVar];
6495  }
6496  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar-1; iVar++)
6497  {
6498  delete [] R_c_inv[iVar];
6499  delete [] R_c[iVar];
6500  }
6501  delete [] R_Matrix;
6502  delete [] R_c;
6503  delete [] R_c_inv;
6504  delete [] R;
6505  delete [] c_avg;
6506  delete [] dcjs;
6507 
6508  delete [] AverageTurboMach;
6509  delete [] UnitNormal;
6510  delete [] turboNormal;
6511  delete [] turboVelocity;
6512 }
6513 
6514 void CEulerSolver::BC_Inlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
6515  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
6516  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
6517  unsigned short iDim;
6518  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
6519  su2double P_Total, T_Total, Velocity[MAXNDIM], Velocity2, H_Total, Temperature, Riemann,
6520  Pressure, Density, Energy, Flow_Dir[MAXNDIM], Mach2, SoundSpeed2, SoundSpeed_Total2, Vel_Mag,
6521  alpha, aa, bb, cc, dd, Area, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM], Normal[MAXNDIM];
6522  su2double *V_inlet, *V_domain;
6523 
6524  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
6525  const su2double Two_Gamma_M1 = 2.0 / Gamma_Minus_One;
6526  const su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
6527  const auto Kind_Inlet = config->GetKind_Inlet();
6528  const auto Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
6529  const bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
6530 
6531  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6532 
6533  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
6534  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
6535 
6536  /*--- Allocate the value at the inlet ---*/
6537 
6538  V_inlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
6539 
6540  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6541 
6542  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
6543 
6544  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
6545 
6546  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
6547 
6548  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
6549  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
6550  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6551 
6552  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
6553  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6554  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
6555 
6556  /*--- Retrieve solution at this boundary node ---*/
6557 
6558  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
6559 
6560  /*--- Build the fictitious intlet state based on characteristics ---*/
6561 
6562 
6563  /*--- Subsonic inflow: there is one outgoing characteristic (u-c),
6564  therefore we can specify all but one state variable at the inlet.
6565  The outgoing Riemann invariant provides the final piece of info.
6566  Adapted from an original implementation in the Stanford University
6567  multi-block (SUmb) solver in the routine bcSubsonicInflow.f90
6568  written by Edwin van der Weide, last modified 04-20-2009. ---*/
6569 
6570  switch (Kind_Inlet) {
6571 
6572  /*--- Total properties have been specified at the inlet. ---*/
6573 
6574  case INLET_TYPE::TOTAL_CONDITIONS: {
6575 
6576  /*--- Retrieve the specified total conditions for this inlet. ---*/
6577 
6578  P_Total = Inlet_Ptotal[val_marker][iVertex];
6579  T_Total = Inlet_Ttotal[val_marker][iVertex];
6580  const su2double* dir = Inlet_FlowDir[val_marker][iVertex];
6581  const su2double mag = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, dir);
6582  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6583  Flow_Dir[iDim] = dir[iDim] / mag;
6584  }
6585 
6586  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
6587 
6588  P_Total /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
6589  T_Total /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
6590 
6591  /*--- Store primitives and set some variables for clarity. ---*/
6592 
6593  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
6594  Velocity2 = 0.0;
6595  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6596  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
6597  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
6598  }
6599  Energy = V_domain[nDim+3] - V_domain[nDim+1]/V_domain[nDim+2];
6600  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
6601  H_Total = (Gamma*Gas_Constant/Gamma_Minus_One)*T_Total;
6602  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/Density;
6603 
6604  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
6605  from the domain interior. ---*/
6606 
6607  Riemann = 2.0*sqrt(SoundSpeed2)/Gamma_Minus_One;
6608  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6609  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6610 
6611  /*--- Total speed of sound ---*/
6612 
6613  SoundSpeed_Total2 = Gamma_Minus_One*(H_Total - (Energy + Pressure/Density)+0.5*Velocity2) + SoundSpeed2;
6614 
6615  /*--- Dot product of normal and flow direction. This should
6616  be negative due to outward facing boundary normal convention. ---*/
6617 
6618  alpha = 0.0;
6619  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6620  alpha += UnitNormal[iDim]*Flow_Dir[iDim];
6621 
6622  /*--- Coefficients in the quadratic equation for the velocity ---*/
6623 
6624  aa = 1.0 + 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*alpha;
6625  bb = -1.0*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*Riemann;
6626  cc = 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Riemann*Riemann
6627  -2.0*SoundSpeed_Total2/Gamma_Minus_One;
6628 
6629  /*--- Solve quadratic equation for velocity magnitude. Value must
6630  be positive, so the choice of root is clear. ---*/
6631 
6632  dd = bb*bb - 4.0*aa*cc;
6633  dd = sqrt(max(0.0, dd));
6634  Vel_Mag = (-bb + dd)/(2.0*aa);
6635  Vel_Mag = max(0.0, Vel_Mag);
6636  Velocity2 = Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
6637 
6638  /*--- Compute speed of sound from total speed of sound eqn. ---*/
6639 
6640  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
6641 
6642  /*--- Mach squared (cut between 0-1), use to adapt velocity ---*/
6643 
6644  Mach2 = Velocity2/SoundSpeed2;
6645  Mach2 = min(1.0, Mach2);
6646  Velocity2 = Mach2*SoundSpeed2;
6647  Vel_Mag = sqrt(Velocity2);
6648  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
6649 
6650  /*--- Compute new velocity vector at the inlet ---*/
6651 
6652  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6653  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
6654 
6655  /*--- Static temperature from the speed of sound relation ---*/
6656 
6657  Temperature = SoundSpeed2/(Gamma*Gas_Constant);
6658 
6659  /*--- Static pressure using isentropic relation at a point ---*/
6660 
6661  Pressure = P_Total*pow((Temperature/T_Total), Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
6662 
6663  /*--- Density at the inlet from the gas law ---*/
6664 
6665  Density = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Temperature);
6666 
6667  /*--- Using pressure, density, & velocity, compute the energy ---*/
6668 
6669  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
6670  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
6671 
6672  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
6673 
6674  V_inlet[0] = Temperature;
6675  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6676  V_inlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
6677  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
6678  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
6679  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
6680 
6681  break;
6682  }
6683  /*--- Mass flow has been specified at the inlet. ---*/
6684 
6685  case INLET_TYPE::MASS_FLOW: {
6686 
6687  /*--- Retrieve the specified mass flow for the inlet. ---*/
6688 
6689  Density = Inlet_Ttotal[val_marker][iVertex];
6690  Vel_Mag = Inlet_Ptotal[val_marker][iVertex];
6691  const su2double* dir = Inlet_FlowDir[val_marker][iVertex];
6692  const su2double mag = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, dir);
6693  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6694  Flow_Dir[iDim] = dir[iDim] / mag;
6695  }
6696 
6697  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
6698 
6699  Density /= config->GetDensity_Ref();
6700  Vel_Mag /= config->GetVelocity_Ref();
6701 
6702  /*--- Get primitives from current inlet state. ---*/
6703 
6704  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6705  Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
6706  Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
6707  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/V_domain[nDim+2];
6708 
6709  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
6710  from the domain interior. ---*/
6711 
6712  Riemann = Two_Gamma_M1*sqrt(SoundSpeed2);
6713  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6714  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6715 
6716  /*--- Speed of sound squared for fictitious inlet state ---*/
6717 
6718  SoundSpeed2 = Riemann;
6719  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6720  SoundSpeed2 -= Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6721 
6722  SoundSpeed2 = max(0.0,0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*SoundSpeed2);
6723  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed2*SoundSpeed2;
6724 
6725  /*--- Pressure for the fictitious inlet state ---*/
6726 
6727  Pressure = SoundSpeed2*Density/Gamma;
6728 
6729  /*--- Energy for the fictitious inlet state ---*/
6730 
6731  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
6732  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
6733 
6734  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
6735 
6736  V_inlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
6737  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6738  V_inlet[iDim+1] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
6739  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
6740  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
6741  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
6742 
6743  break;
6744  }
6745  default:
6746  SU2_MPI::Error("Unsupported INLET_TYPE.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
6747  break;
6748  }
6749 
6750  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
6751 
6752  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
6753 
6754  if (dynamic_grid)
6755  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
6756 
6757  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
6758 
6759  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6760 
6761  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
6762 
6763  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
6764 
6765  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
6766 
6767  if (implicit)
6768  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
6769 
6770 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
6771 //
6772 // if (viscous) {
6773 //
6774 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
6775 //
6776 // V_inlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
6777 // V_inlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
6778 //
6779 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
6780 //
6781 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6782 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
6783 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
6784 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6785 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6786 //
6787 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
6788 //
6789 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
6790 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
6791 //
6792 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
6793 //
6794 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
6795 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
6796 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
6797 //
6798 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
6799 //
6800 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6801 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
6802 //
6803 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
6804 //
6805 // if (implicit)
6806 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
6807 //
6808 // }
6809 
6810  }
6811  }
6812  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
6813 
6814 }
6815 
6816 void CEulerSolver::BC_Outlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
6817  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
6818  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
6819  unsigned short iVar, iDim;
6820  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
6821  su2double Pressure, P_Exit, Velocity[3],
6822  Velocity2, Entropy, Density, Energy, Riemann, Vn, SoundSpeed, Mach_Exit, Vn_Exit,
6823  Area, UnitNormal[3];
6824  su2double *V_outlet, *V_domain;
6825 
6826  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
6827  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
6828  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
6829  bool gravity = (config->GetGravityForce());
6830  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
6831 
6832  su2double *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
6833 
6834  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
6835 
6836  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
6837  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
6838 
6839  /*--- Allocate the value at the outlet ---*/
6840  V_outlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
6841 
6842  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6843 
6844  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
6845  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
6846 
6847  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
6848  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
6849  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
6850  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6851 
6852  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
6853  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6854  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
6855 
6856  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
6857  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
6858 
6859  /*--- Build the fictitious inlet state based on characteristics ---*/
6860 
6861  /*--- Retrieve the specified back pressure for this outlet. ---*/
6862  if (gravity) P_Exit = config->GetOutlet_Pressure(Marker_Tag) - geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, nDim-1)*STANDARD_GRAVITY;
6863  else P_Exit = config->GetOutlet_Pressure(Marker_Tag);
6864 
6865  /*--- Non-dim. the inputs if necessary. ---*/
6866  P_Exit = P_Exit/config->GetPressure_Ref();
6867 
6868  /*--- Check whether the flow is supersonic at the exit. The type
6869  of boundary update depends on this. ---*/
6870  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
6871  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
6872  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6873  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
6874  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
6875  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
6876  }
6877  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
6878  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
6879  Mach_Exit = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
6880 
6881  if (Mach_Exit >= 1.0) {
6882 
6883  /*--- Supersonic exit flow: there are no incoming characteristics,
6884  so no boundary condition is necessary. Set outlet state to current
6885  state so that upwinding handles the direction of propagation. ---*/
6886  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nPrimVar; iVar++) V_outlet[iVar] = V_domain[iVar];
6887 
6888  } else {
6889 
6890  /*--- Subsonic exit flow: there is one incoming characteristic,
6891  therefore one variable can be specified (back pressure) and is used
6892  to update the conservative variables. Compute the entropy and the
6893  acoustic Riemann variable. These invariants, as well as the
6894  tangential velocity components, are extrapolated. Adapted from an
6895  original implementation in the Stanford University multi-block
6896  (SUmb) solver in the routine bcSubsonicOutflow.f90 by Edwin van
6897  der Weide, last modified 09-10-2007. ---*/
6898 
6899  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
6900  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
6901 
6902  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
6903  Density = pow(P_Exit/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
6904  Pressure = P_Exit;
6905  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*P_Exit/Density);
6906  Vn_Exit = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
6907  Velocity2 = 0.0;
6908  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6909  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Exit-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
6910  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
6911  }
6912  Energy = P_Exit/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
6913  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
6914 
6915  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
6916  V_outlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
6917  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
6918  V_outlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
6919  V_outlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
6920  V_outlet[nDim+2] = Density;
6921  V_outlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
6922 
6923  }
6924 
6925  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
6926  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
6927 
6928  if (dynamic_grid)
6929  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
6930 
6931  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
6932 
6933  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6934 
6935  /*--- Add Residuals and Jacobians ---*/
6936 
6937  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
6938  if (implicit)
6939  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
6940 
6941 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
6942 //
6943 // if (viscous) {
6944 //
6945 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
6946 //
6947 // V_outlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
6948 // V_outlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
6949 //
6950 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
6951 //
6952 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
6953 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
6954 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
6955 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6956 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
6957 //
6958 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
6959 //
6960 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
6961 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
6962 //
6963 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
6964 //
6965 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
6966 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
6967 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
6968 //
6969 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
6970 //
6971 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
6972 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
6973 //
6974 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
6975 //
6976 // if (implicit)
6977 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.acobian_i);
6978 //
6979 // }
6980 
6981  }
6982  }
6983  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
6984 
6985  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
6986  delete [] Normal;
6987 
6988 }
6989 
6990 void CEulerSolver::BC_Supersonic_Inlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
6991  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
6992  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
6993  const su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
6994  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
6995  const auto Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
6996  const bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
6997 
6998  /*--- Supersonic inlet flow: there are no outgoing characteristics,
6999  so all flow variables can be imposed at the inlet.
7000  First, retrieve the specified values for the primitive variables. ---*/
7001 
7002  const su2double Temperature = config->GetInlet_Temperature(Marker_Tag) / config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7003  const su2double Pressure = config->GetInlet_Pressure(Marker_Tag) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
7004  const auto* Vel = config->GetInlet_Velocity(Marker_Tag);
7005 
7006  su2double Velocity[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
7007  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7008  Velocity[iDim] = Vel[iDim] / config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7009 
7010  /*--- Density at the inlet from the gas law ---*/
7011 
7012  const su2double Density = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Temperature);
7013 
7014  /*--- Compute the energy from the specified state ---*/
7015 
7016  const su2double Velocity2 = GeometryToolbox::SquaredNorm(int(MAXNDIM), Velocity);
7017  su2double Energy = Pressure / (Density * Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5 * Velocity2;
7018  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7019 
7020  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7021 
7022  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7023  for (auto iVertex = 0ul; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7024  const auto iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7025 
7026  if (!geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) continue;
7027 
7028  /*--- Allocate the value at the inlet ---*/
7029 
7030  auto* V_inlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7031 
7032  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7033 
7034  V_inlet[prim_idx.Temperature()] = Temperature;
7035  V_inlet[prim_idx.Pressure()] = Pressure;
7036  V_inlet[prim_idx.Density()] = Density;
7037  V_inlet[prim_idx.Enthalpy()] = Energy + Pressure / Density;
7038  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7039  V_inlet[iDim+prim_idx.Velocity()] = Velocity[iDim];
7040 
7041  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7042 
7043  auto* V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7044 
7045  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7046 
7047  su2double Normal[MAXNDIM] = {0.0};
7048  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7049  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7050 
7051  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7052 
7053  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7054  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
7055 
7056  if (dynamic_grid)
7057  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
7058  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7059 
7060  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7061 
7062  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7063 
7064  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7065 
7066  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7067 
7068  if (implicit)
7069  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7070 
7071  /*--- Viscous contribution, omited to improve convergence. ---*/
7072 
7073  }
7074  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7075 
7076 }
7077 
7078 void CEulerSolver::BC_Supersonic_Outlet(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container,
7079  CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
7080  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7081  unsigned short iDim;
7082  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7083  su2double *V_outlet, *V_domain;
7084 
7085  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7086  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7087 
7088  su2double *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7089 
7090  /*--- Supersonic outlet flow: there are no ingoing characteristics,
7091  so all flow variables can should be interpolated from the domain. ---*/
7092 
7093  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7094 
7095  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7096  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7097 
7098  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7099 
7100  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
7101 
7102  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
7103 
7104  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7105 
7106  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7107 
7108  /*--- Allocate the value at the outlet ---*/
7109 
7110  V_outlet = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7111

7113

7116  V_outlet[iDim+1] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7117  V_outlet[nDim+1] = V_domain[nDim+1];
7118  V_outlet[nDim+2] = V_domain[nDim+2];
7119  V_outlet[nDim+3] = V_domain[nDim+3];
7120 
7121  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7122 
7123  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);

7129 
7130  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7131 
7132  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7133  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
7134 
7135  if (dynamic_grid)
7136  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint),
7137  geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7138 
7139  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7140 
7141  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7142 
7143  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7144 
7145  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7146 
7147  if (implicit)
7148  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7149 
7150 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7151 //
7152 // if (viscous) {
7153 //
7154 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7155 //
7156 // V_outlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7157 // V_outlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7158 //
7159 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7160 //
7161 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7162 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7163 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7164 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7165 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7166 //
7167 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7168 //
7169 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
7170 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
7171 //
7172 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7173 //
7174 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
7175 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
7176 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
7177 //
7178 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7179 //
7180 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7181 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
7182 //
7183 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7184 //
7185 // if (implicit)
7186 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7187 // }
7188

7190  }
7191  END_SU2_OMP_FOR

7198 
7199 void CEulerSolver::BC_Engine_Inflow(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7200 
7201  unsigned short iDim;
7202  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7203  su2double Pressure, Inflow_Pressure = 0.0, Velocity[3], Velocity2, Entropy, Target_Inflow_MassFlow = 0.0, Target_Inflow_Mach = 0.0, Density, Energy,
7204  Riemann, Area, UnitNormal[3], Vn, SoundSpeed, Vn_Exit, Inflow_Pressure_inc, Inflow_Pressure_old, Inflow_Mach_old, Inflow_MassFlow_old;
7205  su2double *V_inflow, *V_domain;
7206 
7207  su2double DampingFactor = config->GetDamp_Engine_Inflow();
7208  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7209  unsigned short Kind_Engine_Inflow = config->GetKind_Engine_Inflow();
7210  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7211  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7212  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
7213  su2double Baseline_Press = 0.75 * config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
7214  bool Engine_HalfModel = config->GetEngine_HalfModel();
7215 
7216  su2double *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7217 
7218 
7219  if (Kind_Engine_Inflow == FAN_FACE_MACH) {
7220 
7221  /*--- Retrieve the specified target fan face mach at the nacelle. ---*/
7222 
7223  Target_Inflow_Mach = config->GetEngineInflow_Target(Marker_Tag);
7224 
7225  /*--- Retrieve the old fan face pressure and mach number in the nacelle (this has been computed in a preprocessing). ---*/
7226 
7227  Inflow_Pressure_old = config->GetInflow_Pressure(Marker_Tag); // Note that has been computed by the code (non-dimensional).
7228  Inflow_Mach_old = config->GetInflow_Mach(Marker_Tag);
7229 
7230  /*--- Compute the pressure increment (note that increasing pressure decreases flow speed) ---*/
7231 
7232  Inflow_Pressure_inc = - (1.0 - (Inflow_Mach_old/Target_Inflow_Mach)) * Baseline_Press;
7233 
7234  /*--- Estimate the new fan face pressure ---*/
7235 
7236  Inflow_Pressure = (1.0 - DampingFactor)*Inflow_Pressure_old + DampingFactor * (Inflow_Pressure_old + Inflow_Pressure_inc);
7237 
7238  }
7239 
7240  if (Kind_Engine_Inflow == FAN_FACE_MDOT) {
7241 
7242  /*--- Retrieve the specified target mass flow (non-dimensional) at the nacelle. ---*/
7243 
7244  Target_Inflow_MassFlow = config->GetEngineInflow_Target(Marker_Tag) / (config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref());
7245 
7246  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Target_Inflow_MassFlow /= 32.174;
7247 
7248  if (Engine_HalfModel) Target_Inflow_MassFlow /= 2.0;
7249 
7250  /*--- Retrieve the old fan face pressure and mach number in the nacelle (this has been computed in a preprocessing). ---*/
7251 
7252  Inflow_Pressure_old = config->GetInflow_Pressure(Marker_Tag); // Note that has been computed by the code (non-dimensional).
7253  Inflow_MassFlow_old = config->GetInflow_MassFlow(Marker_Tag); // same here... it is a non dimensional value
7254 
7255  /*--- Compute the pressure increment (note that increasing pressure decreases flow speed) ---*/
7256 
7257  Inflow_Pressure_inc = - (1.0 - (Inflow_MassFlow_old/Target_Inflow_MassFlow)) * Baseline_Press;
7258 
7259  /*--- Estimate the new fan face pressure ---*/
7260 
7261  Inflow_Pressure = (1.0 - DampingFactor)*Inflow_Pressure_old + DampingFactor * (Inflow_Pressure_old + Inflow_Pressure_inc);
7262 
7263  }
7264 
7265  /*--- No iterative scheme if we provide the static pressure ---*/
7266 
7267  if (Kind_Engine_Inflow == FAN_FACE_PRESSURE) {
7268 
7269  /*--- Retrieve the specified pressure (non-dimensional) at the nacelle. ---*/
7270 
7271  Inflow_Pressure = config->GetEngineInflow_Target(Marker_Tag) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
7272 
7273  }
7274 
7275 
7276  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7277 
7278  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7279  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7280 
7281  /*--- Allocate the value at the outlet ---*/
7282 
7283  V_inflow = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7284 
7285  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7286 
7287  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
7288 
7289  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
7290 
7291  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7292 
7293  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7294  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7295 
7296  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
7297  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7298  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7299 
7300  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7301 
7302  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7303 
7304  /*--- Subsonic nacelle inflow: there is one incoming characteristic,
7305  therefore one variable can be specified (back pressure) and is used
7306  to update the conservative variables.
7307 
7308  Compute the entropy and the acoustic variable. These
7309  riemann invariants, as well as the tangential velocity components,
7310  are extrapolated. ---*/
7311 
7312  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
7313  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
7314  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7315  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7316  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7317  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7318  }
7319  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
7320  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
7321  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
7322  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7323 
7324  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
7325 
7326  Density = pow(Inflow_Pressure/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
7327  Pressure = Inflow_Pressure;
7328  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Inflow_Pressure/Density);
7329  Vn_Exit = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7330  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7331  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7332  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Exit-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
7333  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7334  }
7335 
7336  Energy = Inflow_Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7337  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7338 
7339  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7340 
7341  V_inflow[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
7342  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7343  V_inflow[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7344  V_inflow[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7345  V_inflow[nDim+2] = Density;
7346  V_inflow[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7347  V_inflow[nDim+4] = SoundSpeed;
7348 
7349  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7350 
7351  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7352  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inflow);
7353 
7354  /*--- Set grid movement ---*/
7355 
7356  if (dynamic_grid)
7357  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7358 
7359  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7360 
7361  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7362 
7363  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7364 
7365  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7366 
7367  if (implicit)
7368  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7369 
7370 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7371 //
7372 // if (viscous) {
7373 //
7374 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7375 //
7376 // V_inflow[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7377 // V_inflow[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7378 //
7379 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7380 //
7381 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7382 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7383 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7384 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7385 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7386 //
7387 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7388 //
7389 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inflow);
7390 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
7391 //
7392 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7393 //
7394 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
7395 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
7396 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
7397 //
7398 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7399 //
7400 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7401 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
7402 //
7403 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7404 //
7405 // if (implicit)
7406 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7407 //
7408 // }
7409 
7410  }
7411  }
7412  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7413 
7414  delete [] Normal;
7415 
7416 }
7417 
7418 void CEulerSolver::BC_Engine_Exhaust(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker) {
7419 
7420  unsigned short iDim;
7421  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
7422  su2double Exhaust_Pressure, Exhaust_Temperature, Velocity[3], Velocity2, H_Exhaust, Temperature, Riemann, Area, UnitNormal[3], Pressure, Density, Energy, Mach2, SoundSpeed2, SoundSpeed_Exhaust2, Vel_Mag, alpha, aa, bb, cc, dd, Flow_Dir[3];
7423  su2double *V_exhaust, *V_domain, Target_Exhaust_Pressure, Exhaust_Pressure_old, Exhaust_Pressure_inc;
7424 
7425  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7426  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7427  string Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(val_marker);
7428  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
7429  su2double DampingFactor = config->GetDamp_Engine_Exhaust();
7430  su2double Baseline_Press = 0.75 * config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
7431 
7432  su2double *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7433 
7434  /*--- Retrieve the specified exhaust pressure in the engine (non-dimensional). ---*/
7435 
7436  Target_Exhaust_Pressure = config->GetExhaust_Pressure_Target(Marker_Tag) / config->GetPressure_Ref();
7437 
7438  /*--- Retrieve the old exhaust pressure in the engine exhaust (this has been computed in a preprocessing). ---*/
7439 
7440  Exhaust_Pressure_old = config->GetExhaust_Pressure(Marker_Tag);
7441 
7442  /*--- Compute the Pressure increment ---*/
7443 
7444  Exhaust_Pressure_inc = (1.0 - (Exhaust_Pressure_old/Target_Exhaust_Pressure)) * Baseline_Press;
7445 
7446  /*--- Estimate the new exhaust pressure ---*/
7447 
7448  Exhaust_Pressure = (1.0 - DampingFactor) * Exhaust_Pressure_old + DampingFactor * (Exhaust_Pressure_old + Exhaust_Pressure_inc);
7449 
7450  /*--- The temperature is given (no iteration is required) ---*/
7451 
7452  Exhaust_Temperature = config->GetExhaust_Temperature_Target(Marker_Tag);
7453  Exhaust_Temperature /= config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7454 
7455  /*--- The pressure is given (no iteration is required) ---*/
7456 
7457  Exhaust_Pressure = config->GetExhaust_Pressure_Target(Marker_Tag);
7458  Exhaust_Pressure /= config->GetPressure_Ref();
7459 
7460  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7461 
7462  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7463  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7464 
7465  /*--- Allocate the value at the exhaust ---*/
7466 
7467  V_exhaust = GetCharacPrimVar(val_marker, iVertex);
7468 
7469  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7470 
7471  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e, not a halo node) ---*/
7472 
7473  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
7474 
7475  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
7476 
7477  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7478  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7479 
7480  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
7481  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7482  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7483 
7484  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node ---*/
7485 
7486  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7487 
7488  /*--- Subsonic inflow: there is one outgoing characteristic (u-c),
7489  therefore we can specify all but one state variable at the inlet.
7490  The outgoing Riemann invariant provides the final piece of info. ---*/
7491 
7492  /*--- Store primitives and set some variables for clarity. ---*/
7493 
7494  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
7495  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7496  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7497  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7498  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7499  }
7500  Energy = V_domain[nDim+3] - V_domain[nDim+1]/V_domain[nDim+2];
7501  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
7502  H_Exhaust = (Gamma*Gas_Constant/Gamma_Minus_One)*Exhaust_Temperature;
7503  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/Density;
7504 
7505  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
7506  from the domain interior. ---*/
7507 
7508  Riemann = 2.0*sqrt(SoundSpeed2)/Gamma_Minus_One;
7509  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7510  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7511 
7512  /*--- Total speed of sound ---*/
7513 
7514  SoundSpeed_Exhaust2 = Gamma_Minus_One*(H_Exhaust - (Energy + Pressure/Density)+0.5*Velocity2) + SoundSpeed2;
7515 
7516  /*--- The flow direction is defined by the surface normal ---*/
7517 
7518  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7519  Flow_Dir[iDim] = -UnitNormal[iDim];
7520 
7521  /*--- Dot product of normal and flow direction. This should
7522  be negative due to outward facing boundary normal convention. ---*/
7523 
7524  alpha = 0.0;
7525  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7526  alpha += UnitNormal[iDim]*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7527 
7528  /*--- Coefficients in the quadratic equation for the velocity ---*/
7529 
7530  aa = 1.0 + 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*alpha;
7531  bb = -1.0*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*Riemann;
7532  cc = 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Riemann*Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Exhaust2/Gamma_Minus_One;
7533 
7534  /*--- Solve quadratic equation for velocity magnitude. Value must
7535  be positive, so the choice of root is clear. ---*/
7536 
7537  dd = bb*bb - 4.0*aa*cc;
7538  dd = sqrt(max(0.0, dd));
7539  Vel_Mag = (-bb + dd)/(2.0*aa);
7540 
7541  if (Vel_Mag >= 0.0) {
7542 
7543  Velocity2 = Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
7544 
7545  /*--- Compute speed of sound from total speed of sound eqn. ---*/
7546 
7547  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Exhaust2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7548  Mach2 = Velocity2/SoundSpeed2;
7549  Velocity2 = Mach2*SoundSpeed2;
7550  Vel_Mag = sqrt(Velocity2);
7551  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Exhaust2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7552 
7553  /*--- Compute new velocity vector at the inlet ---*/
7554 
7555  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7556  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7557 
7558  /*--- Static temperature from the speed of sound relation ---*/
7559 
7560  Temperature = SoundSpeed2/(Gamma*Gas_Constant);
7561 
7562  /*--- Static pressure using isentropic relation at a point ---*/
7563 
7564  Pressure = Exhaust_Pressure*pow((Temperature/Exhaust_Temperature), Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
7565 
7566  /*--- Density at the exhaust from the gas law ---*/
7567 
7568  Density = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Temperature);
7569 
7570  /*--- Using pressure, density, & velocity, compute the energy ---*/
7571 
7572  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7573  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7574 
7575  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7576 
7577  V_exhaust[0] = Temperature;
7578  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7579  V_exhaust[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7580  V_exhaust[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7581  V_exhaust[nDim+2] = Density;
7582  V_exhaust[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7583  V_exhaust[nDim+4] = sqrt(SoundSpeed2);
7584 
7585  }
7586  /*--- The flow goes in the wrong direction ---*/
7587 
7588  else {
7589 
7590  V_exhaust[0] = V_domain[0];
7591  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7592  V_exhaust[iDim+1] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7593  V_exhaust[nDim+1] = V_domain[nDim+1];
7594  V_exhaust[nDim+2] = V_domain[nDim+2];
7595  V_exhaust[nDim+3] = V_domain[nDim+3];
7596  V_exhaust[nDim+4] = V_domain[nDim+4];
7597 
7598  }
7599 
7600  /*--- Set various quantities in the solver class ---*/
7601 
7602  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7603  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_exhaust);
7604 
7605  /*--- Set grid movement ---*/
7606 
7607  if (dynamic_grid)
7608  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
7609 
7610  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
7611 
7612  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
7613 
7614  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
7615 
7616  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7617 
7618  if (implicit)
7619  Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7620 
7621 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
7622 //
7623 // if (viscous) {
7624 //
7625 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
7626 //
7627 // V_exhaust[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
7628 // V_exhaust[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
7629 //
7630 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
7631 //
7632 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7633 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
7634 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
7635 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7636 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
7637 //
7638 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
7639 //
7640 // visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_exhaust);
7641 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
7642 //
7643 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
7644 //
7645 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
7646 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
7647 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
7648 //
7649 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
7650 //
7651 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config)
7652 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
7653 //
7654 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
7655 //
7656 // if (implicit)
7657 // Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
7658 //
7659 // }
7660 
7661  }
7662  }
7663  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
7664 
7665  delete [] Normal;
7666 
7667 }
