7697 void CEulerSolver::BC_ActDisk(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
7698  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker, bool val_inlet_surface) {
7699 
7700  unsigned short iDim;
7701  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, GlobalIndex_donor, GlobalIndex;
7702  su2double Pressure, Velocity[3], Target_Press_Jump, Target_Temp_Jump,
7703  Velocity2, Entropy, Density, Energy, Riemann, Vn, SoundSpeed, Vn_Inlet, Mach_Outlet,
7704  Area, UnitNormal[3], *V_outlet, *V_domain, *V_inlet, P_Total, T_Total, H_Total, Temperature,
7705  Mach2, SoundSpeed2, SoundSpeed_Total2, Vel_Mag, alpha, aa, bb, cc, dd;
7706  su2double Factor, P_static, T_static, SoS_outlet, Rho_outlet, Rho_inlet;
7707  su2double Vel_normal_inlet[3], Vel_tangent_inlet[3], Vel_inlet[3];
7708  su2double Vel_normal_outlet[3], Vel_tangent_outlet[3], Vel_outlet[3];
7709  su2double Vel_normal_inlet_, Vel_tangent_inlet_, Vel_inlet_;
7710  su2double Vel_normal_outlet_, Vel_outlet_;
7711 
7712  su2double Pressure_out, Density_out, SoundSpeed_out, Velocity2_out,
7713  Mach_out, Pressure_in, Density_in, SoundSpeed_in, Velocity2_in,
7714  Mach_in, PressureAdj, TemperatureAdj;
7715 
7716  bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
7717  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
7718  bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
7719  bool ratio = (config->GetActDisk_Jump() == RATIO);
7720  su2double SecondaryFlow = config->GetSecondaryFlow_ActDisk();
7721 
7722  su2double *Normal = new su2double[nDim];
7723  su2double *Flow_Dir = new su2double[nDim];
7724 
7725  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker ---*/
7726 
7727  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
7728  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
7729 
7730  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
7731  GlobalIndex = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint);
7732  GlobalIndex_donor = GetDonorGlobalIndex(val_marker, iVertex);
7733 
7734  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
7735 
7736  if ((geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) &&
7737  (GlobalIndex != GlobalIndex_donor)) {
7738 
7739  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negative for outward convention) ---*/
7740 
7741  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
7742  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
7743  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
7744 
7745  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
7746  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7747  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
7748 
7749  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node and jumps values ---*/
7750 
7751  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7752  Target_Press_Jump = ActDisk_DeltaP[val_marker][iVertex];
7753  Target_Temp_Jump = ActDisk_DeltaT[val_marker][iVertex];
7754 
7755  if (val_inlet_surface) {
7756  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7757  V_outlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];
7758 
7759  Pressure_out = V_outlet[nDim+1];
7760  Density_out = V_outlet[nDim+2];
7761  SoundSpeed_out = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_out/Density_out);
7762 
7763  Pressure_in = V_inlet[nDim+1];
7764  Density_in = V_inlet[nDim+2];
7765  SoundSpeed_in = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_in/Density_in);
7766 
7767  Velocity2_out = 0.0; Velocity2_in = 0.0;
7768  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7769  Velocity2_out += V_outlet[iDim+1]*V_outlet[iDim+1];
7770  Velocity2_in += V_inlet[iDim+1]*V_inlet[iDim+1];
7771  }
7772 
7773  PressureAdj = 1.0; TemperatureAdj = 1.0;
7774  if ((Velocity2_out > 0.0) && (Velocity2_in > 0.0)) {
7775 
7776  Mach_out = sqrt(Velocity2_out)/SoundSpeed_out;
7777  Mach_in = sqrt(Velocity2_in)/SoundSpeed_in;
7778 
7779  PressureAdj = pow( 1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0)) /
7780  pow( 1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
7781  TemperatureAdj = (1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0)) /
7782  (1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
7783 
7784  }
7785 
7786  if (ratio) {
7787  P_static = V_outlet[nDim+1] / (Target_Press_Jump/PressureAdj);
7788  T_static = V_outlet[0] / (Target_Temp_Jump/TemperatureAdj);
7789  }
7790  else { P_static = V_outlet[nDim+1] - Target_Press_Jump; T_static = V_outlet[0] - Target_Temp_Jump; }
7791  }
7792  else {
7793  V_outlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
7794  V_inlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];
7795 
7796  Pressure_out = V_outlet[nDim+1];
7797  Density_out = V_outlet[nDim+2];
7798  SoundSpeed_out = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_out/Density_out);
7799 
7800  Pressure_in = V_inlet[nDim+1];
7801  Density_in = V_inlet[nDim+2];
7802  SoundSpeed_in = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure_in/Density_in);
7803 
7804  Velocity2_out = 0.0; Velocity2_in = 0.0;
7805  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7806  Velocity2_out += V_outlet[iDim+1]*V_outlet[iDim+1];
7807  Velocity2_in += V_inlet[iDim+1]*V_inlet[iDim+1];
7808  }
7809 
7810  PressureAdj = 1.0; TemperatureAdj = 1.0;
7811  if ((Velocity2_out > 0.0) && (Velocity2_in > 0.0)) {
7812 
7813  Mach_out = sqrt(Velocity2_out)/SoundSpeed_out;
7814  Mach_in = sqrt(Velocity2_in)/SoundSpeed_in;
7815 
7816  PressureAdj = pow( 1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0)) /
7817  pow( 1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
7818  TemperatureAdj = (1.0 + Mach_out * Mach_out * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0)) /
7819  (1.0 + Mach_in * Mach_in * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
7820  }
7821 
7822  if (ratio) {
7823  P_static = V_inlet[nDim+1] * (Target_Press_Jump/PressureAdj);
7824  T_static = V_inlet[0] * (Target_Temp_Jump/TemperatureAdj);
7825  }
7826  else { P_static = V_inlet[nDim+1] + Target_Press_Jump; T_static = V_inlet[0] + Target_Temp_Jump; }
7827  }
7828 
7829  /*--- Subsonic inlet ---*/
7830 
7831  if (val_inlet_surface) {
7832 
7833  /*--- Build the fictitious intlet state based on characteristics.
7834  Retrieve the specified back pressure for this inlet ---*/
7835 
7836  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
7837  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
7838  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7839  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7840  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7841  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7842  }
7843  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
7844  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
7845 
7846  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
7847  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7848 
7849  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
7850 
7851  Pressure = P_static;
7852  Density = pow(Pressure/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
7853  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
7854  Vn_Inlet = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
7855 
7856  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7857  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7858  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Inlet-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
7859  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7860  }
7861  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
7862  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
7863 
7864  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
7865 
7866  V_inlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
7867  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7868  V_inlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
7869  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
7870  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
7871  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
7872  V_inlet[nDim+4] = SoundSpeed;
7873  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
7874 
7875  }
7876 
7877  /*--- Subsonic outlet ---*/
7878 
7879  else {
7880 
7881  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_PT(P_static, T_static);
7882  SoS_outlet = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
7883  Rho_outlet = GetFluidModel()->GetDensity();
7884 
7885  /*--- We use the velocity and the density from the flow inlet
7886  to evaluate flow direction and mass flow ---*/
7887 
7888  Rho_inlet = V_inlet[nDim+2];
7889  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7890  Vel_inlet[iDim] = V_inlet[iDim+1];
7891 
7892  Vel_normal_inlet_ = 0.0; Vel_inlet_ = 0.0;
7893  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7894  Vel_normal_inlet[iDim] = -Vel_inlet[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7895  Vel_normal_inlet_ += Vel_normal_inlet[iDim]*Vel_normal_inlet[iDim];
7896  Vel_inlet_+= Vel_inlet[iDim]*Vel_inlet[iDim];
7897  }
7898  Vel_inlet_ = sqrt(Vel_inlet_);
7899  Vel_normal_inlet_ = sqrt(Vel_normal_inlet_);
7900 
7901  Vel_tangent_inlet_ = 0.0;
7902  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7903  Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim] = Vel_inlet[iDim] - Vel_normal_inlet[iDim];
7904  Vel_tangent_inlet_ += Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim]*Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim];
7905  }
7906  Vel_tangent_inlet_ = sqrt(Vel_tangent_inlet_);
7907 
7908  /*--- Mass flow conservation (normal direction) and
7909  no jump in the tangential velocity ---*/
7910 
7911  Vel_normal_outlet_ = (1.0-SecondaryFlow/100.0)*(Rho_inlet*Vel_normal_inlet_)/Rho_outlet;
7912 
7913  Vel_outlet_ = 0.0;
7914  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7915  Vel_normal_outlet[iDim] = -Vel_normal_outlet_*UnitNormal[iDim];
7916  Vel_tangent_outlet[iDim] = Vel_tangent_inlet[iDim];
7917  Vel_outlet[iDim] = Vel_normal_outlet[iDim] + Vel_tangent_outlet[iDim];
7918  Vel_outlet_ += Vel_outlet[iDim]*Vel_outlet[iDim];
7919  }
7920  Vel_outlet_ = sqrt(Vel_outlet_);
7921 
7922  Mach_Outlet = min(Vel_outlet_/SoS_outlet, 1.0);
7923 
7924  /*--- Reevaluate the Total Pressure and Total Temperature using the
7925  Fan Face Mach number and the static values from the jum condition ---*/
7926 
7927  Factor = 1.0 + 0.5*Mach_Outlet*Mach_Outlet*Gamma_Minus_One;
7928  P_Total = P_static * pow(Factor, Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
7929  T_Total = T_static * Factor;
7930 
7931  /*--- Flow direction using the velocity direction at the outlet ---*/
7932 
7933  if (Vel_outlet_ != 0.0) {
7934  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Flow_Dir[iDim] = Vel_outlet[iDim]/Vel_outlet_;
7935  }
7936  else {
7937  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Flow_Dir[iDim] = 0.0;
7938  }
7939 
7940  /*--- Store primitives and set some variables for clarity. ---*/
7941 
7942  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
7943  Velocity2 = 0.0;
7944  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
7945  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
7946  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
7947  }
7948  Energy = V_domain[nDim+3] - V_domain[nDim+1]/V_domain[nDim+2];
7949  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
7950  H_Total = (Gamma*Gas_Constant/Gamma_Minus_One)*T_Total;
7951  SoundSpeed2 = Gamma*Pressure/Density;
7952 
7953  /*--- Compute the acoustic Riemann invariant that is extrapolated
7954  from the domain interior. ---*/
7955 
7956  Riemann = 2.0*sqrt(SoundSpeed2)/Gamma_Minus_One;
7957  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7958  Riemann += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
7959 
7960  /*--- Total speed of sound ---*/
7961 
7962  SoundSpeed_Total2 = Gamma_Minus_One*(H_Total - (Energy + Pressure/Density)+0.5*Velocity2) + SoundSpeed2;
7963 
7964  /*--- Dot product of normal and flow direction. This should
7965  be negative due to outward facing boundary normal convention. ---*/
7966 
7967  alpha = 0.0;
7968  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
7969  alpha += UnitNormal[iDim]*Flow_Dir[iDim];
7970 
7971  /*--- Coefficients in the quadratic equation for the velocity ---*/
7972 
7973  aa = 1.0 + 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*alpha;
7974  bb = -1.0*Gamma_Minus_One*alpha*Riemann;
7975  cc = 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Riemann*Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed_Total2/Gamma_Minus_One;
7976 
7977  /*--- Solve quadratic equation for velocity magnitude. Value must
7978  be positive, so the choice of root is clear. ---*/
7979 
7980  dd = bb*bb - 4.0*aa*cc;
7981  dd = sqrt(max(0.0, dd));
7982  Vel_Mag = (-bb + dd)/(2.0*aa);
7983  Vel_Mag = max(0.0, Vel_Mag);
7984  Velocity2 = Vel_Mag*Vel_Mag;
7985 
7986  /*--- Compute speed of sound from total speed of sound eqn. ---*/
7987 
7988  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7989 
7990  /*--- Mach squared (cut between 0-1), use to adapt velocity ---*/
7991 
7992  Mach2 = min(1.0, Velocity2/SoundSpeed2);
7993  Velocity2 = Mach2*SoundSpeed2;
7994  Vel_Mag = sqrt(Velocity2);
7995  SoundSpeed2 = SoundSpeed_Total2 - 0.5*Gamma_Minus_One*Velocity2;
7996 
7997  /*--- Compute new velocity vector at the exit ---*/
7998 
7999  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8000  Velocity[iDim] = Vel_Mag*Flow_Dir[iDim];
8001 
8002  /*--- Static temperature from the speed of sound relation ---*/
8003 
8004  Temperature = SoundSpeed2/(Gamma*Gas_Constant);
8005 
8006  /*--- Static pressure using isentropic relation at a point ---*/
8007 
8008  Pressure = P_Total*pow((Temperature/T_Total), Gamma/Gamma_Minus_One);
8009 
8010  /*--- Density at the inlet from the gas law ---*/
8011 
8012  Density = Pressure/(Gas_Constant*Temperature);
8013 
8014  /*--- Using pressure, density, & velocity, compute the energy ---*/
8015 
8016  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
8017  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
8018 
8019  /*--- Primitive variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
8020 
8021  V_outlet[0] = Temperature;
8022  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8023  V_outlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
8024  V_outlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
8025  V_outlet[nDim+2] = Density;
8026  V_outlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
8027  V_outlet[nDim+4] = sqrt(SoundSpeed2);
8028  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
8029 
8030  }
8031 
8032  /*--- Grid Movement ---*/
8033 
8034  if (dynamic_grid)
8035  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
8036 
8037  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
8038 
8039  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
8040 
8041  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
8042 
8043  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
8044 
8045  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
8046 
8047  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
8048 
8049 // /*--- Viscous contribution, commented out because serious convergence problems ---*/
8050 //
8051 // if (viscous) {
8052 //
8053 // /*--- Set laminar and eddy viscosity at the infinity ---*/
8054 //
8055 // if (val_inlet_surface) {
8056 // V_inlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
8057 // V_inlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
8058 // }
8059 // else {
8060 // V_outlet[nDim+5] = nodes->GetLaminarViscosity(iPoint);
8061 // V_outlet[nDim+6] = nodes->GetEddyViscosity(iPoint);
8062 // }
8063 //
8064 // /*--- Set the normal vector and the coordinates ---*/
8065 //
8066 // visc_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
8067 // su2double Coord_Reflected[MAXNDIM];
8068 // GeometryToolbox::PointPointReflect(nDim, geometry->nodes->GetCoord(Point_Normal),
8069 // geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
8070 // visc_numerics->SetCoord(geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint), Coord_Reflected);
8071 //
8072 // /*--- Primitive variables, and gradient ---*/
8073 //
8074 // if (val_inlet_surface) visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
8075 // else visc_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
8076 //
8077 // visc_numerics->SetPrimVarGradient(nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint), nodes->GetGradient_Primitive(iPoint));
8078 //
8079 // /*--- Turbulent kinetic energy ---*/
8080 //
8081 // if (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST)
8082 // visc_numerics->SetTurbKineticEnergy(solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0),
8083 // solver_container[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0));
8084 //
8085 // /*--- Compute and update residual ---*/
8086 //
8087 // auto residual = visc_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
8088 // LinSysRes.SubtractBlock(iPoint, residual);
8089 //
8090 // /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
8091 //
8092 // if (implicit) Jacobian.SubtractBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
8093 //
8094 // }
8095 
8096  }
8097 
8098  }
8099  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
8100 
8101  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
8102 
8103  delete [] Normal;
8104  delete [] Flow_Dir;
8105 
8106 }
8107 
8108 void CEulerSolver::BC_ActDisk_VariableLoad(CGeometry *geometry, CSolver **solver_container, CNumerics *conv_numerics, CNumerics *visc_numerics,
8109  CConfig *config, unsigned short val_marker, bool val_inlet_surface) {
8110 
8111  /*!
8112  * \function BC_ActDisk_VariableLoad
8113  * \brief Actuator disk model with variable load along disk radius.
8114  * \author: E. Saetta, L. Russo, R. Tognaccini (GitHub references EttoreSaetta, lorenzorusso07, rtogna).
8115  * Theoretical and Applied Aerodynamics Research Group (TAARG), University of Naples Federico II.
8116  * First release date : July 1st 2020
8117  * modified on:
8118  *
8119  * Force coefficients distribution given in an input file. Actuator disk data initialized in function SetActDisk_BCThrust.
8120  * Entropy, acoustic Riemann invariant R+ and tangential velocity extrapolated from upstream flow;
8121  * acoustic Riemann invariant R- is extrapolated from downstream.
8122  * Hovering condition simulation not available yet: freestream velocity must be different than zero.
8123  */
8124 
8125  unsigned short iDim;
8126  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, GlobalIndex_donor, GlobalIndex;
8127  su2double Pressure, Velocity[MAXNDIM],
8128  Velocity2, Entropy, Density, Energy, Riemann, Vn, SoundSpeed, Vn_Inlet,
8129  Area, UnitNormal[MAXNDIM] = {0.0}, *V_outlet, *V_domain, *V_inlet;
8130 
8131  su2double Pressure_out, Density_out,
8132  Pressure_in, Density_in;
8133 
8134  su2double Prop_Axis[MAXNDIM];
8135  su2double Fa, Fx, Fy, Fz;
8136  su2double u_in, v_in, w_in, u_out, v_out, w_out, uJ, vJ, wJ;
8137  su2double Temperature_out, H_in, H_out;
8138  su2double FQ, Q_out, Density_Disk;
8139  su2double SoSextr, Vnextr[MAXNDIM], Vnextr_, RiemannExtr, QdMnorm[MAXNDIM], QdMnorm2, appo2, SoS_out;
8140  su2double Normal[MAXNDIM];
8141 
8142  const bool implicit = (config->GetKind_TimeIntScheme() == EULER_IMPLICIT);
8143  const auto Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
8144  const bool tkeNeeded = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
8145 
8146  /*--- Get the actuator disk center and axis coordinates for the current marker. ---*/
8147  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
8148  Prop_Axis[iDim] = ActDisk_Axis(val_marker, iDim);
8149  }
8150 
8151  /*--- Loop over all the vertices on this boundary marker. ---*/
8152  SU2_OMP_FOR_DYN(OMP_MIN_SIZE)
8153  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[val_marker]; iVertex++) {
8154 
8155  iPoint = geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNode();
8156  GlobalIndex = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(iPoint);
8157  GlobalIndex_donor = GetDonorGlobalIndex(val_marker, iVertex);
8158 
8159  /*--- Check if the node belongs to the domain (i.e., not a halo node) ---*/
8160 
8161  if ((geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) &&
8162  (GlobalIndex != GlobalIndex_donor)) {
8163 
8164  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negative for outward convention) ---*/
8165 
8166  geometry->vertex[val_marker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Normal);
8167  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Normal[iDim] = -Normal[iDim];
8168  conv_numerics->SetNormal(Normal);
8169 
8170  Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
8171  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8172  UnitNormal[iDim] = Normal[iDim]/Area;
8173 
8174  /*--- Current solution at this boundary node. ---*/
8175 
8176  V_domain = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8177 
8178  /*--- Get the values of Fa (axial force per unit area), Fx, Fy and Fz (x, y and z components of the tangential and
8179  radial forces per unit area resultant). ---*/
8180  Fa = ActDisk_Fa[val_marker][iVertex];
8181  Fx = ActDisk_Fx[val_marker][iVertex];
8182  Fy = ActDisk_Fy[val_marker][iVertex];
8183  Fz = ActDisk_Fz[val_marker][iVertex];
8184 
8185  /*--- Get the primitive variables and the extrapolated variables. ---*/
8186  if (val_inlet_surface){
8187  V_inlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8188  V_outlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];}
8189  else{
8190  V_outlet = nodes->GetPrimitive(iPoint);
8191  V_inlet = DonorPrimVar[val_marker][iVertex];}
8192 
8193  /*--- u, v and w are the three momentum components. ---*/
8194  Pressure_out = V_outlet[nDim+1];
8195  Density_out = V_outlet[nDim+2];
8196  u_out = V_outlet[1]*V_outlet[nDim+2];
8197  v_out = V_outlet[2]*V_outlet[nDim+2];
8198  w_out = V_outlet[3]*V_outlet[nDim+2];
8199 
8200  Pressure_in = V_inlet[nDim+1];
8201  Density_in = V_inlet[nDim+2];
8202  u_in = V_inlet[1]*Density_in;
8203  v_in = V_inlet[2]*Density_in;
8204  w_in = V_inlet[3]*Density_in;
8205  H_in = V_inlet[nDim+3]*Density_in;
8206 
8207  /*--- Density on the disk is computed as an everage value between the inlet and outlet values. ---*/
8208  Density_Disk = 0.5*(Density_in + Density_out);
8209 
8210  /*--- Computation of the normal momentum flowing through the disk. ---*/
8211  Q_out = 0.5*((u_in + u_out)*Prop_Axis[0] + (v_in + v_out)*Prop_Axis[1] + (w_in + w_out)*Prop_Axis[2]);
8212 
8213  FQ = Q_out/Density_Disk;
8214 
8215  /*--- Computation of the momentum jumps due to the tnagential and radial forces per unit area. ---*/
8216  if (FQ < EPS){
8217  uJ = 0.0;
8218  vJ = 0.0;
8219  wJ = 0.0;}
8220  else{
8221  uJ = Fx/FQ;
8222  vJ = Fy/FQ;
8223  wJ = Fz/FQ;}
8224 
8225  if (val_inlet_surface) {
8226  /*--- Build the fictitious intlet state based on characteristics.
8227  Retrieve the specified back pressure for this inlet ---*/
8228 
8229  Density = V_domain[nDim+2];
8230  Velocity2 = 0.0; Vn = 0.0;
8231  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8232  Velocity[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1];
8233  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8234  Vn += Velocity[iDim]*UnitNormal[iDim];
8235  }
8236  Pressure = V_domain[nDim+1];
8237  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
8238 
8239  Entropy = Pressure*pow(1.0/Density, Gamma);
8240  Riemann = Vn + 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
8241 
8242  /*--- Compute the new fictious state at the outlet ---*/
8243 
8244  Pressure = Pressure_out - Fa;
8245  Density = pow(Pressure/Entropy,1.0/Gamma);
8246  SoundSpeed = sqrt(Gamma*Pressure/Density);
8247  Vn_Inlet = Riemann - 2.0*SoundSpeed/Gamma_Minus_One;
8248 
8249  Velocity2 = 0.0;
8250  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8251  Velocity[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] + (Vn_Inlet-Vn)*UnitNormal[iDim];
8252  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8253  }
8254  Energy = Pressure/(Density*Gamma_Minus_One) + 0.5*Velocity2;
8255  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
8256 
8257  /*--- Conservative variables, using the derived quantities ---*/
8258 
8259  V_inlet[0] = Pressure / ( Gas_Constant * Density);
8260  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) V_inlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim];
8261  V_inlet[nDim+1] = Pressure;
8262  V_inlet[nDim+2] = Density;
8263  V_inlet[nDim+3] = Energy + Pressure/Density;
8264  V_inlet[nDim+4] = SoundSpeed;
8265  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_inlet);
8266  }
8267  else {
8268  /*--- Acoustic Riemann invariant extrapolation form the interior domain. ---*/
8269  SoSextr = V_domain[nDim+4];
8270 
8271  Vnextr_ = 0.0;
8272  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++){
8273  Vnextr[iDim] = V_domain[iDim+1]*Prop_Axis[iDim];
8274  Vnextr_ += Vnextr[iDim]*Vnextr[iDim];
8275  }
8276  Vnextr_ = sqrt(max(0.0,Vnextr_));
8277  RiemannExtr = Vnextr_ - ((2*SoSextr)/(Gamma_Minus_One));
8278 
8279  /*--- Assigning the momentum in tangential direction jump and the pressure jump. ---*/
8280  Velocity[0] = u_in + uJ;
8281  Velocity[1] = v_in + vJ;
8282  Velocity[2] = w_in + wJ;
8283  Pressure_out = Pressure_in + Fa;
8284 
8285  /*--- Computation of the momentum normal to the disk plane. ---*/
8286  QdMnorm[0] = u_in*Prop_Axis[0];
8287  QdMnorm[1] = v_in*Prop_Axis[1];
8288  QdMnorm[2] = w_in*Prop_Axis[2];
8289 
8290  QdMnorm2 = 0.0;
8291  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) QdMnorm2 += QdMnorm[iDim]*QdMnorm[iDim];
8292 
8293  /*--- Resolving the second grade equation for the density. ---*/
8294  appo2 = -((2*sqrt(QdMnorm2)*RiemannExtr)+((4*Gamma*Pressure_out)/(pow(Gamma_Minus_One,2))));
8295  Density_out = (-appo2+sqrt(max(0.0,pow(appo2,2)-4*QdMnorm2*pow(RiemannExtr,2))))/(2*pow(RiemannExtr,2));
8296 
8297  Velocity2 = 0;
8298  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) Velocity2 += (Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim]);
8299 
8300  /*--- Computation of the enthalpy, total energy, temperature and speed of sound. ---*/
8301  H_out = H_in/Density_in + Fa/Density_out;
8302  Energy = H_out - Pressure_out/Density_out;
8303  if (tkeNeeded) Energy += GetTke_Inf();
8304  Temperature_out = (Energy-0.5*Velocity2/(pow(Density_out,2)))*(Gamma_Minus_One/Gas_Constant);
8305 
8306  SoS_out = sqrt(Gamma*Gas_Constant*Temperature_out);
8307 
8308  /*--- Set the primitive variables. ---*/
8309  V_outlet[0] = Temperature_out;
8310  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8311  V_outlet[iDim+1] = Velocity[iDim]/Density_out;
8312  V_outlet[nDim+1] = Pressure_out;
8313  V_outlet[nDim+2] = Density_out;
8314  V_outlet[nDim+3] = H_out;
8315  V_outlet[nDim+4] = SoS_out;
8316  conv_numerics->SetPrimitive(V_domain, V_outlet);
8317  }
8318 
8319  /*--- Grid Movement (NOT TESTED!)---*/
8320 
8321  if (dynamic_grid)
8322  conv_numerics->SetGridVel(geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint), geometry->nodes->GetGridVel(iPoint));
8323 
8324  /*--- Compute the residual using an upwind scheme ---*/
8325 
8326  auto residual = conv_numerics->ComputeResidual(config);
8327 
8328  /*--- Update residual value ---*/
8329 
8330  LinSysRes.AddBlock(iPoint, residual);
8331 
8332  /*--- Jacobian contribution for implicit integration ---*/
8333 
8334  if (implicit) Jacobian.AddBlock2Diag(iPoint, residual.jacobian_i);
8335  }
8336  }
8337  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
8338 }

8341

8378 void CEulerSolver::SetFreeStream_Solution(const CConfig *config) {
8379 
8380  unsigned long iPoint;
8381  unsigned short iDim;
8382 
8383  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(omp_chunk_size)
8384  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
8385  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,0, Density_Inf);
8386  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8387  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,iDim+1, Density_Inf*Velocity_Inf[iDim]);
8388  }
8389  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,nVar-1, Density_Inf*Energy_Inf);
8390  }

8394 void CEulerSolver::SetFreeStream_TurboSolution(CConfig *config) {
8395 
8396  unsigned long iPoint;
8397  unsigned short iDim;
8398  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
8399  su2double *turboVelocity, *cartVelocity;
8400 
8401  su2double Alpha = config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0;
8402  su2double Mach = config->GetMach();
8403  su2double SoundSpeed;
8404 
8405  turboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8406  cartVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8407 
8408  auto turboNormal = config->GetFreeStreamTurboNormal();
8409 
8410  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(Pressure_Inf, Density_Inf);
8411  SoundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
8412 
8413  /*--- Compute the Free Stream velocity, using the Mach number ---*/
8414  turboVelocity[0] = cos(Alpha)*Mach*SoundSpeed;
8415  turboVelocity[1] = sin(Alpha)*Mach*SoundSpeed;
8416 
8417 
8418  if (nDim == 3) {
8419  turboVelocity[2] = 0.0;
8420  }
8421 
8422  ComputeBackVelocity(turboVelocity, turboNormal, cartVelocity, INFLOW, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8423 
8424  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPoint; iPoint++) {
8425  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,0, Density_Inf);
8426  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8427  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,iDim+1, Density_Inf*cartVelocity[iDim]);
8428  }
8429  nodes->SetSolution(iPoint,nVar-1, Density_Inf*Energy_Inf);
8430 
8431  nodes->SetPrimVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
8432  nodes->SetSecondaryVar(iPoint, GetFluidModel());
8433  }
8434 
8435  delete [] turboVelocity;
8436  delete [] cartVelocity;
8437 
8438 
8439 }

8441 void CEulerSolver::PreprocessAverage(CSolver **solver, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short marker_flag) {
8442 
8443  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
8444  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, iMarkerTP, iSpan;
8445  su2double Pressure = 0.0, Density = 0.0, *Velocity = nullptr, *TurboVelocity,
8446  Area, TotalArea, TotalAreaPressure, TotalAreaDensity, *TotalAreaVelocity, *UnitNormal, *TurboNormal;
8447  string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
8448  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
8449  const su2double *AverageTurboNormal;
8450  su2double VelSq;
8451 
8452  /*-- Variables declaration and allocation ---*/
8453  Velocity = new su2double[nDim];
8454  UnitNormal = new su2double[nDim];
8455  TurboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
8456  TurboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8457  TotalAreaVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8458 
8459  const auto nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanWiseSections();
8460 
8461  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections; iSpan++){
8462 
8463  for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++) {
8464  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] = 0.0;
8465  }
8466 
8467  TotalAreaPressure = 0.0;
8468  TotalAreaDensity = 0.0;
8469 
8470  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8471  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8472  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8473  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8474 
8475  /*--- Retrieve Old Solution ---*/
8476 
8477  /*--- Loop over the vertices to sum all the quantities pithc-wise ---*/
8478  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
8479  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
8480  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)){
8481  /*--- Compute the integral fluxes for the boundaries ---*/
8482 
8483  Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
8484  Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
8485 
8486  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
8487  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
8488  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(TurboNormal);
8489  Area = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetArea();
8490 
8491  VelSq = 0.0;
8492  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8493  Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
8494  VelSq += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8495  }
8496 
8497  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity, TurboNormal , TurboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8498 
8499  /*--- Compute different integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8500 
8501  TotalAreaPressure += Area*Pressure;
8502  TotalAreaDensity += Area*Density;
8503  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8504  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] += Area*Velocity[iDim];
8505  }
8506  }
8507  }
8508  }
8509  }
8510  }
8511 
8512 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
8513 
8514  /*--- Add information using all the nodes ---*/
8515 
8516  su2double MyTotalAreaDensity = TotalAreaDensity;
8517  su2double MyTotalAreaPressure = TotalAreaPressure;
8518 
8519  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotalAreaDensity, &TotalAreaDensity, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8520  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyTotalAreaPressure, &TotalAreaPressure, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8521 
8522  su2double* MyTotalAreaVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8523 
8524  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8525  MyTotalAreaVelocity[iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim];
8526  }
8527 
8528  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(MyTotalAreaVelocity, TotalAreaVelocity, nDim, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8529 
8530  delete [] MyTotalAreaVelocity;
8531 
8532 #endif
8533 
8534  /*--- initialize spanwise average quantities ---*/
8535 
8536 
8537  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8538  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8539  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8540  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8541 
8542  TotalArea = geometry->GetSpanArea(iMarker,iSpan);
8543  AverageTurboNormal = geometry->GetAverageTurboNormal(iMarker,iSpan);
8544 
8545  /*--- Compute the averaged value for the boundary of interest for the span of interest ---*/
8546 
8547  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
8548  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
8549  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8550  AverageVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
8551 
8552  /* --- compute static averaged quantities ---*/
8553  ComputeTurboVelocity(AverageVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8554 
8555  OldAverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
8556  OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
8557  for(iDim = 0; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
8558  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim];
8559 
8560  }
8561  }
8562  }
8563  }
8564  }
8565 
8566  /*--- initialize 1D average quantities ---*/
8567 
8568  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8569  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8570  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8571  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8572 
8573  AverageTurboNormal = geometry->GetAverageTurboNormal(iMarker,nSpanWiseSections);
8574 
8575  /*--- Compute the averaged value for the boundary of interest for the span of interest ---*/
8576 
8577  AverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2];
8578  AveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2];
8579  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8580  AverageVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections][iDim] = AverageVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2][iDim];
8581 
8582  /* --- compute static averaged quantities ---*/
8583  ComputeTurboVelocity(AverageVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections], AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8584 
8585  OldAverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AverageDensity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections];
8586  OldAveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections] = AveragePressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections];
8587  for(iDim = 0; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
8588  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections][iDim] = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections][iDim];
8589 
8590  }
8591  }
8592  }
8593  }
8594 
8595 
8596  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
8597  delete [] Velocity;
8598  delete [] UnitNormal;
8599  delete [] TurboNormal;
8600  delete [] TurboVelocity;
8601  delete [] TotalAreaVelocity;
8602 
8603 }

8606 void CEulerSolver::TurboAverageProcess(CSolver **solver, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned short marker_flag) {
8607 
8608  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, nVert;
8609  unsigned short iDim, iVar, iMarker, iMarkerTP, iSpan, jSpan;
8610  unsigned short average_process = config->GetKind_AverageProcess();
8611  unsigned short performance_average_process = config->GetKind_PerformanceAverageProcess();
8612  su2double Pressure = 0.0, Density = 0.0, Enthalpy = 0.0, *Velocity = nullptr, *TurboVelocity,
8613  Area, TotalArea, Radius1, Radius2, Vt2, TotalAreaPressure, TotalAreaDensity, *TotalAreaVelocity, *UnitNormal, *TurboNormal,
8614  TotalMassPressure, TotalMassDensity, *TotalMassVelocity;
8615  string Marker_Tag, Monitoring_Tag;
8616  su2double val_init_pressure;
8617  unsigned short iZone = config->GetiZone();
8618  su2double TotalDensity, TotalPressure, *TotalVelocity, *TotalFluxes;
8619  const su2double *AverageTurboNormal;
8620  su2double TotalNu, TotalOmega, TotalKine, TotalMassNu, TotalMassOmega, TotalMassKine, TotalAreaNu, TotalAreaOmega, TotalAreaKine;
8621  su2double Nu, Kine, Omega;
8622  su2double MachTest, soundSpeed;
8623  bool turbulent = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() != TURB_MODEL::NONE);
8624  bool spalart_allmaras = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SA);
8625  bool menter_sst = (config->GetKind_Turb_Model() == TURB_MODEL::SST);
8626 
8627  /*-- Variables declaration and allocation ---*/
8628  Velocity = new su2double[nDim];
8629  UnitNormal = new su2double[nDim];
8630  TurboNormal = new su2double[nDim];
8631  TurboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8632  TotalVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8633  TotalAreaVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8634  TotalMassVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8635  TotalFluxes = new su2double[nVar];
8636 
8637  su2double avgDensity, *avgVelocity, avgPressure, avgKine, avgOmega, avgNu, avgAreaDensity, *avgAreaVelocity, avgAreaPressure,
8638  avgAreaKine, avgAreaOmega, avgAreaNu, avgMassDensity, *avgMassVelocity, avgMassPressure, avgMassKine, avgMassOmega, avgMassNu,
8639  avgMixDensity, *avgMixVelocity, *avgMixTurboVelocity, avgMixPressure, avgMixKine, avgMixOmega, avgMixNu;
8640 
8641  avgVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8642  avgAreaVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8643  avgMassVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8644  avgMixVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8645  avgMixTurboVelocity = new su2double[nDim];
8646 
8647  const auto nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanWiseSections();
8648 
8649  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections + 1; iSpan++){
8650 
8651  /*--- Forces initialization for contenitors ---*/
8652  for (iVar=0;iVar<nVar;iVar++)
8653  TotalFluxes[iVar]= 0.0;
8654  for (iDim=0; iDim<nDim; iDim++) {
8655  TotalVelocity[iDim] = 0.0;
8656  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] = 0.0;
8657  TotalMassVelocity[iDim] = 0.0;
8658  }
8659 
8660  TotalDensity = 0.0;
8661  TotalPressure = 0.0;
8662  TotalAreaPressure = 0.0;
8663  TotalAreaDensity = 0.0;
8664  TotalMassPressure = 0.0;
8665  TotalMassDensity = 0.0;
8666  TotalNu = 0.0;
8667  TotalOmega = 0.0;
8668  TotalKine = 0.0;
8669  TotalMassNu = 0.0;
8670  TotalMassOmega = 0.0;
8671  TotalMassKine = 0.0;
8672  TotalAreaNu = 0.0;
8673  TotalAreaOmega = 0.0;
8674  TotalAreaKine = 0.0;
8675 
8676  Nu = 0.0;
8677  Omega = 0.0;
8678  Kine = 0.0;
8679 
8680  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8681  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8682  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8683  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8684 
8685  /*--- Retrieve Old Solution ---*/
8686 
8687  /*--- Loop over the vertices to sum all the quantities pithc-wise ---*/
8688  if(iSpan < nSpanWiseSections){
8689  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan); iVertex++) {
8690  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
8691 
8692  /*--- Compute the integral fluxes for the boundaries ---*/
8693  Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
8694  Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
8695  Enthalpy = nodes->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
8696 
8697  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
8698  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
8699  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(TurboNormal);
8700  Area = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][iSpan][iVertex]->GetArea();
8701  su2double VelNormal = 0.0, VelSq = 0.0;
8702 
8703  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8704  Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
8705  VelNormal += UnitNormal[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8706  VelSq += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8707  }
8708 
8709  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity, TurboNormal , TurboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8710 
8711  /*--- Compute different integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8712 
8713  TotalDensity += Density;
8714  TotalPressure += Pressure;
8715  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8716  TotalVelocity[iDim] += Velocity[iDim];
8717 
8718  TotalAreaPressure += Area*Pressure;
8719  TotalAreaDensity += Area*Density;
8720  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8721  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] += Area*Velocity[iDim];
8722 
8723  TotalMassPressure += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Pressure;
8724  TotalMassDensity += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Density;
8725  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8726  TotalMassVelocity[iDim] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Velocity[iDim];
8727 
8728  TotalFluxes[0] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]);
8729  TotalFluxes[1] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*TurboVelocity[0] + Pressure);
8730  for (iDim = 2; iDim < nDim+1; iDim++)
8731  TotalFluxes[iDim] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*TurboVelocity[iDim -1]);
8732  TotalFluxes[nDim+1] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*Enthalpy);
8733 
8734 
8735  /*--- Compute turbulent integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8736 
8737  if(turbulent){
8738  if(menter_sst){
8739  Kine = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
8740  Omega = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,1);
8741  }
8742  if(spalart_allmaras){
8743  Nu = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
8744  }
8745 
8746  TotalKine += Kine;
8747  TotalOmega += Omega;
8748  TotalNu += Nu;
8749 
8750  TotalAreaKine += Area*Kine;
8751  TotalAreaOmega += Area*Omega;
8752  TotalAreaNu += Area*Nu;
8753 
8754  TotalMassKine += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Kine;
8755  TotalMassOmega += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Omega;
8756  TotalMassNu += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Nu;
8757 
8758 
8759  }
8760  }
8761  }
8762  else{
8763  for (jSpan= 0; jSpan < nSpanWiseSections; jSpan++){
8764  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertexSpan(iMarker,jSpan); iVertex++) {
8765  iPoint = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][jSpan][iVertex]->GetNode();
8766 
8767  /*--- Compute the integral fluxes for the boundaries ---*/
8768  Pressure = nodes->GetPressure(iPoint);
8769  Density = nodes->GetDensity(iPoint);
8770  Enthalpy = nodes->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
8771 
8772  /*--- Normal vector for this vertex (negate for outward convention) ---*/
8773  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][jSpan][iVertex]->GetNormal(UnitNormal);
8774  geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][jSpan][iVertex]->GetTurboNormal(TurboNormal);
8775  Area = geometry->turbovertex[iMarker][jSpan][iVertex]->GetArea();
8776  su2double VelNormal = 0.0, VelSq = 0.0;
8777 
8778  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
8779  Velocity[iDim] = nodes->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
8780  VelNormal += UnitNormal[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8781  VelSq += Velocity[iDim]*Velocity[iDim];
8782  }
8783 
8784  ComputeTurboVelocity(Velocity, TurboNormal , TurboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8785 
8786  /*--- Compute different integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8787 
8788  TotalDensity += Density;
8789  TotalPressure += Pressure;
8790  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8791  TotalVelocity[iDim] += Velocity[iDim];
8792 
8793  TotalAreaPressure += Area*Pressure;
8794  TotalAreaDensity += Area*Density;
8795  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8796  TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] += Area*Velocity[iDim];
8797 
8798  TotalMassPressure += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Pressure;
8799  TotalMassDensity += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Density;
8800  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8801  TotalMassVelocity[iDim] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Velocity[iDim];
8802 
8803  TotalFluxes[0] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]);
8804  TotalFluxes[1] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*TurboVelocity[0] + Pressure);
8805  for (iDim = 2; iDim < nDim+1; iDim++)
8806  TotalFluxes[iDim] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*TurboVelocity[iDim -1]);
8807  TotalFluxes[nDim+1] += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0]*Enthalpy);
8808 
8809 
8810  /*--- Compute turbulent integral quantities for the boundary of interest ---*/
8811 
8812  if(turbulent){
8813  if(menter_sst){
8814  Kine = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
8815  Omega = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,1);
8816  }
8817  if(spalart_allmaras){
8818  Nu = solver[TURB_SOL]->GetNodes()->GetSolution(iPoint,0);
8819  }
8820 
8821  TotalKine += Kine;
8822  TotalOmega += Omega;
8823  TotalNu += Nu;
8824 
8825  TotalAreaKine += Area*Kine;
8826  TotalAreaOmega += Area*Omega;
8827  TotalAreaNu += Area*Nu;
8828 
8829  TotalMassKine += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Kine;
8830  TotalMassOmega += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Omega;
8831  TotalMassNu += Area*(Density*TurboVelocity[0] )*Nu;
8832 
8833  }
8834  }
8835  }
8836  }
8837  }
8838  }
8839  }
8840  }
8841 
8842 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
8843 
8844  /*--- Add information using all the nodes ---*/
8845 
8846  auto Allreduce = [](su2double x) {
8847  su2double tmp = x; x = 0.0;
8848  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &x, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8849  return x;
8850  };
8851 
8852  TotalDensity = Allreduce(TotalDensity);
8853  TotalPressure = Allreduce(TotalPressure);
8854  TotalAreaDensity = Allreduce(TotalAreaDensity);
8855  TotalAreaPressure = Allreduce(TotalAreaPressure);
8856  TotalMassDensity = Allreduce(TotalMassDensity);
8857  TotalMassPressure = Allreduce(TotalMassPressure);
8858 
8859  TotalNu = Allreduce(TotalNu);
8860  TotalKine = Allreduce(TotalKine);
8861  TotalOmega = Allreduce(TotalOmega);
8862  TotalAreaNu = Allreduce(TotalAreaNu);
8863  TotalAreaKine = Allreduce(TotalAreaKine);
8864  TotalAreaOmega = Allreduce(TotalAreaOmega);
8865 
8866  TotalMassNu = Allreduce(TotalMassNu);
8867  TotalMassKine = Allreduce(TotalMassKine);
8868  TotalMassOmega = Allreduce(TotalMassOmega);
8869 
8870  su2double* buffer = new su2double[max(nVar,nDim)];
8871 
8872  auto Allreduce_inplace = [buffer](int size, su2double* x) {
8873  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(x, buffer, size, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
8874  for(int i=0; i<size; ++i) x[i] = buffer[i];
8875  };
8876 
8877  Allreduce_inplace(nVar, TotalFluxes);
8878  Allreduce_inplace(nDim, TotalVelocity);
8879  Allreduce_inplace(nDim, TotalAreaVelocity);
8880  Allreduce_inplace(nDim, TotalMassVelocity);
8881 
8882  delete [] buffer;
8883 
8884 #endif
8885 
8886  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
8887  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
8888  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
8889  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
8890 
8891  TotalArea = geometry->GetSpanArea(iMarker,iSpan);
8892  AverageTurboNormal = geometry->GetAverageTurboNormal(iMarker,iSpan);
8893  nVert = geometry->GetnTotVertexSpan(iMarker,iSpan);
8894 
8895  /*--- compute normal Mach number as a check for massflow average and mixedout average ---*/
8896  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(TotalAreaPressure/TotalArea, TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea);
8897  soundSpeed = GetFluidModel()->GetSoundSpeed();
8898  MachTest = TotalFluxes[0]/(TotalAreaDensity*soundSpeed);
8899 
8900  /*--- Compute the averaged value for the boundary of interest for the span of interest ---*/
8901 
8902  /*--- compute algebraic average ---*/
8903  avgDensity = TotalDensity / nVert;
8904  avgPressure = TotalPressure / nVert;
8905  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgVelocity[iDim] = TotalVelocity[iDim] / nVert;
8906  avgKine = TotalKine/nVert;
8907  avgOmega = TotalOmega/nVert;
8908  avgNu = TotalNu/nVert;
8909 
8910  /*--- compute area average ---*/
8911  avgAreaDensity = TotalAreaDensity / TotalArea;
8912  avgAreaPressure = TotalAreaPressure / TotalArea;
8913  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgAreaVelocity[iDim] = TotalAreaVelocity[iDim] / TotalArea;
8914  avgAreaKine = TotalAreaKine / TotalArea;
8915  avgAreaOmega = TotalAreaOmega / TotalArea;
8916  avgAreaNu = TotalAreaNu / TotalArea;
8917 
8918  /*--- compute mass-flow average ---*/
8919  if (abs(MachTest)< config->GetAverageMachLimit()) {
8920  avgMassDensity = avgAreaDensity;
8921  avgMassPressure = avgAreaPressure;
8922  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgMassVelocity[iDim] = avgAreaVelocity[iDim];
8923  avgMassKine = avgAreaKine;
8924  avgMassOmega = avgAreaOmega;
8925  avgMassNu = avgAreaNu;
8926  }else{
8927  avgMassDensity = TotalMassDensity / TotalFluxes[0];
8928  avgMassPressure = TotalMassPressure / TotalFluxes[0];
8929  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) avgMassVelocity[iDim] = TotalMassVelocity[iDim] / TotalFluxes[0];
8930  avgMassKine = TotalMassKine / TotalFluxes[0];
8931  avgMassOmega = TotalMassOmega / TotalFluxes[0];
8932  avgMassNu = TotalMassNu / TotalFluxes[0];
8933  }
8934  /*--- compute mixed-out average ---*/
8935  for (iVar = 0; iVar<nVar; iVar++){
8936  AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iVar] = TotalFluxes[iVar]/TotalArea;
8937  SpanTotalFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iVar] = TotalFluxes[iVar];
8938  }
8939  val_init_pressure = OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
8940 
8941  if (abs(MachTest)< config->GetAverageMachLimit()) {
8942  avgMixDensity = avgAreaDensity;
8943  avgMixPressure = avgAreaPressure;
8944  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
8945  avgMixVelocity[iDim] = avgAreaVelocity[iDim];
8946  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgMixVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , avgMixTurboVelocity, marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8947  avgMixKine = avgAreaKine;
8948  avgMixOmega = avgAreaOmega;
8949  avgMixNu = avgAreaNu;
8950  }else {
8951  MixedOut_Average (config, val_init_pressure, AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal, avgMixPressure, avgMixDensity);
8952  avgMixTurboVelocity[0] = ( AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][1] - avgMixPressure) / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
8953  for (iDim = 2; iDim < nDim +1;iDim++)
8954  avgMixTurboVelocity[iDim-1] = AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
8955 
8956  if (avgMixDensity!= avgMixDensity || avgMixPressure!= avgMixPressure || avgMixPressure < 0.0 || avgMixDensity < 0.0 ){
8957  val_init_pressure = avgAreaPressure;
8958  MixedOut_Average (config, val_init_pressure, AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal, avgMixPressure, avgMixDensity);
8959  avgMixTurboVelocity[0] = ( AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][1] - avgMixPressure) / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
8960  for (iDim = 2; iDim < nDim +1;iDim++)
8961  avgMixTurboVelocity[iDim-1] = AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] / AverageFlux[iMarker][iSpan][0];
8962  }
8963  avgMixKine = avgMassKine;
8964  avgMixOmega = avgMassOmega;
8965  avgMixNu = avgMassNu;
8966  }
8967 
8968  /*--- Store averaged value for the selected average method ---*/
8969  switch(average_process){
8970  case ALGEBRAIC:
8971  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = avgDensity;
8972  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = avgPressure;
8973  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8974  AverageKine[iMarker][iSpan] = avgKine;
8975  AverageOmega[iMarker][iSpan] = avgOmega;
8976  AverageNu[iMarker][iSpan] = avgNu;
8977  break;
8978 
8979  case AREA:
8980  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = avgAreaDensity;
8981  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = avgAreaPressure;
8982  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgAreaVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8983  AverageKine[iMarker][iSpan] = avgAreaKine;
8984  AverageOmega[iMarker][iSpan] = avgAreaOmega;
8985  AverageNu[iMarker][iSpan] = avgAreaNu;
8986  break;
8987 
8988  case MASSFLUX:
8989  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMassDensity;
8990  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMassPressure;
8991  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgAreaVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
8992  AverageKine[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMassKine;
8993  AverageOmega[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMassOmega;
8994  AverageNu[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMassNu;
8995  break;
8996 
8997  case MIXEDOUT:
8998  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMixDensity;
8999  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMixPressure;
9000  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = avgMixTurboVelocity[iDim];
9001  AverageKine[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMixKine;
9002  AverageOmega[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMixOmega;
9003  AverageNu[iMarker][iSpan] = avgMixNu;
9004  break;
9005 
9006  default:
9007  SU2_MPI::Error(" Invalid AVERAGE PROCESS input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
9008  break;
9009  }
9010 
9011  /* --- check if averaged quantities are correct otherwise reset the old quantities ---*/
9012  if (AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan]!= AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] || AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan]!= AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan]){
9013  cout<<"nan in mixing process routine for iSpan: " << iSpan<< " in marker " << config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker)<< endl;
9014  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = OldAverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
9015  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9016  for(iDim = 0; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
9017  AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim];
9018  }
9019 
9020 
9021  if (AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] < 0.0 || AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] < 0.0){
9022  cout << " negative density or pressure in mixing process routine for iSpan: " << iSpan<< " in marker " << config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker)<< endl;
9023  AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = OldAverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
9024  AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9025  for(iDim = 0; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
9026  AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim];
9027  }
9028 
9029  /* --- update old average solution ---*/
9030  OldAverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan] = AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan];
9031  OldAveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan] = AveragePressure[iMarker][iSpan];
9032  for(iDim = 0; iDim < nDim;iDim++)
9033  OldAverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][iDim];
9034 
9035  /*--- to avoid back flow ---*/
9036  if (AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0] < 0.0){
9037  AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan][0] = soundSpeed*config->GetAverageMachLimit();
9038  }
9039 
9040  /*--- compute cartesian average Velocity ---*/
9041  ComputeBackVelocity(AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], AverageTurboNormal , AverageVelocity[iMarker][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9042 
9043 
9044  /*--- Store averaged performance value for the selected average method ---*/
9045  switch(performance_average_process){
9046  case ALGEBRAIC:
9047  if(marker_flag == INFLOW){
9048  DensityIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgDensity;
9049  PressureIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgPressure;
9050  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9051  KineIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgKine;
9052  OmegaIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgOmega;
9053  NuIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgNu;
9054  }
9055  else{
9056  DensityOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgDensity;
9057  PressureOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgPressure;
9058  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9059  KineOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgKine;
9060  OmegaOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgOmega;
9061  NuOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgNu;
9062  }
9063 
9064  break;
9065  case AREA:
9066  if(marker_flag == INFLOW){
9067  DensityIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaDensity;
9068  PressureIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaPressure;
9069  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgAreaVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9070  KineIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaKine;
9071  OmegaIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaOmega;
9072  NuIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaNu;
9073  }
9074  else{
9075  DensityOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaDensity;
9076  PressureOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaPressure;
9077  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgAreaVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9078  KineOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaKine;
9079  OmegaOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaOmega;
9080  NuOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgAreaNu/TotalArea;
9081  }
9082  break;
9083 
9084  case MASSFLUX:
9085  if(marker_flag == INFLOW){
9086  DensityIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassDensity;
9087  PressureIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassPressure;
9088  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgMassVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9089  KineIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassKine;
9090  OmegaIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassOmega;
9091  NuIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassNu;
9092  }
9093  else{
9094  DensityOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassDensity;
9095  PressureOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassPressure;
9096  ComputeTurboVelocity(avgMassVelocity, AverageTurboNormal , TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan], marker_flag, config->GetKind_TurboMachinery(iZone));
9097  KineOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassKine;
9098  OmegaOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassOmega;
9099  NuOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMassNu;
9100  }
9101 
9102  break;
9103 
9104  case MIXEDOUT:
9105  if (marker_flag == INFLOW){
9106  DensityIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixDensity;
9107  PressureIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixPressure;
9108  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][iDim] = avgMixTurboVelocity[iDim];
9109  KineIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixKine;
9110  OmegaIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixOmega;
9111  NuIn[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixNu;
9112  }
9113  else{
9114  DensityOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixDensity;
9115  PressureOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixPressure;
9116  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][iDim] = avgMixTurboVelocity[iDim];
9117  KineOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixKine;
9118  OmegaOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixOmega;
9119  NuOut[iMarkerTP - 1][iSpan] = avgMixNu;
9120  }
9121  break;
9122 
9123  default:
9124  SU2_MPI::Error(" Invalid MIXING_PROCESS input!", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
9125  break;
9126  }
9127  }
9128  }
9129  }
9130  }
9131  }
9132 
9133  /*--- Compute Outlet Static Pressure if Radial equilibrium is imposed ---*/
9134 
9135  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
9136  for (iMarkerTP=1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
9137  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
9138  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == marker_flag){
9139  Marker_Tag = config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker);
9140  if(config->GetBoolGiles() || config->GetBoolRiemann()){
9141  if(config->GetBoolRiemann()){
9142  if(config->GetKind_Data_Riemann(Marker_Tag) == RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM){
9143  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2] = config->GetRiemann_Var1(Marker_Tag)/config->GetPressure_Ref();
9144  for (iSpan= nSpanWiseSections/2; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections-1; iSpan++){
9145  Radius2 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan+1);
9146  Radius1 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan);
9147  Vt2 = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan +1][1]*AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan +1][1];
9148  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan +1] = RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan] + AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan +1]*Vt2/Radius2*(Radius2 - Radius1);
9149  }
9150  for (iSpan= nSpanWiseSections/2; iSpan > 0; iSpan--){
9151  Radius2 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan);
9152  Radius1 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan-1);
9153  Vt2 = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan - 1][1]*AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan - 1][1];
9154  Radius1 = (Radius1 > EPS)? Radius1 : Radius2;
9155  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan -1] = RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan] - AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan -1]*Vt2/Radius1*(Radius2 - Radius1);
9156  }
9157  }
9158  }
9159  else{
9160  if(config->GetKind_Data_Giles(Marker_Tag) == RADIAL_EQUILIBRIUM){
9161  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][nSpanWiseSections/2] = config->GetGiles_Var1(Marker_Tag)/config->GetPressure_Ref();
9162  for (iSpan= nSpanWiseSections/2; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections-1; iSpan++){
9163  Radius2 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan+1);
9164  Radius1 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan);
9165  Vt2 = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan +1][1]*AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan +1][1];
9166  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan +1] = RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan] + AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan +1]*Vt2/Radius2*(Radius2 - Radius1);
9167  }
9168  for (iSpan= nSpanWiseSections/2; iSpan > 0; iSpan--){
9169  Radius2 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan);
9170  Radius1 = geometry->GetTurboRadius(iMarker,iSpan-1);
9171  Vt2 = AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan -1][1]*AverageTurboVelocity[iMarker][iSpan - 1][1];
9172  Radius1 = (Radius1 > EPS)? Radius1 : Radius2;
9173  RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan -1] = RadialEquilibriumPressure[iMarker][iSpan] - AverageDensity[iMarker][iSpan -1]*Vt2/Radius1*(Radius2 - Radius1);
9174  }
9175  }
9176  }
9177  }
9178  }
9179  }
9180  }
9181  }
9182 
9183  /*--- Free locally allocated memory ---*/
9184  delete [] Velocity;
9185  delete [] UnitNormal;
9186  delete [] TurboNormal;
9187  delete [] TurboVelocity;
9188  delete [] TotalVelocity;
9189  delete [] TotalAreaVelocity;
9190  delete [] TotalFluxes;
9191  delete [] TotalMassVelocity;
9192  delete [] avgVelocity;
9193  delete [] avgAreaVelocity;
9194  delete [] avgMassVelocity;
9195  delete [] avgMixVelocity;
9196  delete [] avgMixTurboVelocity;
9197 
9198 }
9199 
9200 void CEulerSolver::MixedOut_Average (CConfig *config, su2double val_init_pressure, const su2double *val_Averaged_Flux,
9201  const su2double *val_normal, su2double& pressure_mix, su2double& density_mix) {
9202 
9203  su2double dx, f, df, resdl = 1.0E+05;
9204  unsigned short iter = 0, iDim;
9205  su2double relax_factor = config->GetMixedout_Coeff(0);
9206  su2double toll = config->GetMixedout_Coeff(1);
9207  unsigned short maxiter = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetMixedout_Coeff(2));
9208  su2double dhdP, dhdrho, enthalpy_mix, velsq, *vel;
9209 
9210  vel = new su2double[nDim];
9211 
9212  pressure_mix = val_init_pressure;
9213 
9214  /*--- Newton-Raphson's method with central difference formula ---*/
9215 
9216  while ( iter <= maxiter ) {
9217 
9218  density_mix = val_Averaged_Flux[0]*val_Averaged_Flux[0]/(val_Averaged_Flux[1] - pressure_mix);
9219  GetFluidModel()->SetTDState_Prho(pressure_mix, density_mix);
9220  enthalpy_mix = GetFluidModel()->GetStaticEnergy() + (pressure_mix)/(density_mix);
9221 
9222  GetFluidModel()->ComputeDerivativeNRBC_Prho(pressure_mix, density_mix);
9223  dhdP = GetFluidModel()->GetdhdP_rho();
9224  dhdrho = GetFluidModel()->Getdhdrho_P();
9225 
9226  vel[0] = (val_Averaged_Flux[1] - pressure_mix) / val_Averaged_Flux[0];
9227  for (iDim = 1; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
9228  vel[iDim] = val_Averaged_Flux[iDim+1] / val_Averaged_Flux[0];
9229  }
9230 
9231  velsq = 0.0;
9232  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
9233  velsq += vel[iDim]*vel[iDim];
9234  }
9235  f = val_Averaged_Flux[nDim+1] - val_Averaged_Flux[0]*(enthalpy_mix + velsq/2);
9236  df = -val_Averaged_Flux[0]*(dhdP - 1/density_mix) - dhdrho*density_mix*density_mix/val_Averaged_Flux[0];
9237  dx = -f/df;
9238  resdl = dx/val_init_pressure;
9239  pressure_mix += relax_factor*dx;
9240 
9241  iter += 1;
9242  if ( abs(resdl) <= toll ) {
9243  break;
9244  }
9245 
9246  }
9247 
9248  density_mix = val_Averaged_Flux[0]*val_Averaged_Flux[0]/(val_Averaged_Flux[1] - pressure_mix);
9249 
9250  delete [] vel;
9251 
9252 }
9253 
9254 void CEulerSolver::GatherInOutAverageValues(CConfig *config, CGeometry *geometry){
9255 
9256  unsigned short iMarker, iMarkerTP;
9257  unsigned short iSpan;
9258  int markerTP;
9259  su2double densityIn, pressureIn, normalVelocityIn, tangVelocityIn, radialVelocityIn;
9260  su2double densityOut, pressureOut, normalVelocityOut, tangVelocityOut, radialVelocityOut;
9261  su2double kineIn, omegaIn, nuIn, kineOut, omegaOut, nuOut;
9262  //TODO (turbo) implement interpolation so that Inflow and Outflow spanwise section can be different
9263 
9264  const auto nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanWiseSections();
9265 
9266  for (iSpan= 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections + 1 ; iSpan++) {
9267 
9268 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
9269  unsigned short i, n1, n2, n1t,n2t;
9270  su2double *TurbPerfIn= NULL,*TurbPerfOut= NULL;
9271  su2double *TotTurbPerfIn = NULL,*TotTurbPerfOut = NULL;
9272  int *TotMarkerTP = NULL;
9273 
9274  n1 = 8;
9275  n2 = 8;
9276  n1t = n1*size;
9277  n2t = n2*size;
9278  TurbPerfIn = new su2double[n1];
9279  TurbPerfOut = new su2double[n2];
9280 
9281  for (i=0;i<n1;i++)
9282  TurbPerfIn[i] = -1.0;
9283  for (i=0;i<n2;i++)
9284  TurbPerfOut[i] = -1.0;
9285 #endif
9286 
9287  densityIn = -1.0;
9288  pressureIn = -1.0;
9289  normalVelocityIn = -1.0;
9290  tangVelocityIn = -1.0;
9291  radialVelocityIn = -1.0;
9292  densityOut = -1.0;
9293  pressureOut = -1.0;
9294  normalVelocityOut = -1.0;
9295  tangVelocityOut = -1.0;
9296  radialVelocityOut = -1.0;
9297  kineIn = -1.0;
9298  omegaIn = -1.0;
9299  nuIn = -1.0;
9300  kineOut = -1.0;
9301  omegaOut = -1.0;
9302  nuOut = -1.0;
9303 
9304  markerTP = -1;
9305 
9306  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++){
9307  for (iMarkerTP = 1; iMarkerTP < config->GetnMarker_Turbomachinery()+1; iMarkerTP++){
9308  if (config->GetMarker_All_Turbomachinery(iMarker) == iMarkerTP){
9309  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == INFLOW){
9310  markerTP = iMarkerTP;
9311  densityIn = DensityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9312  pressureIn = PressureIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9313  normalVelocityIn = TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][0];
9314  tangVelocityIn = TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][1];
9315  if (nDim ==3){
9316  radialVelocityIn = TurboVelocityIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][2];
9317  }
9318  kineIn = KineIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9319  omegaIn = OmegaIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9320  nuIn = NuIn[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9321 
9322 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
9323  TurbPerfIn[0] = densityIn;
9324  TurbPerfIn[1] = pressureIn;
9325  TurbPerfIn[2] = normalVelocityIn;
9326  TurbPerfIn[3] = tangVelocityIn;
9327  TurbPerfIn[4] = radialVelocityIn;
9328  TurbPerfIn[5] = kineIn;
9329  TurbPerfIn[6] = omegaIn;
9330  TurbPerfIn[7] = nuIn;
9331 #endif
9332  }
9333 
9334  /*--- retrieve outlet information ---*/
9335  if (config->GetMarker_All_TurbomachineryFlag(iMarker) == OUTFLOW){
9336  densityOut = DensityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9337  pressureOut = PressureOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9338  normalVelocityOut = TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][0];
9339  tangVelocityOut = TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][1];
9340  if (nDim ==3){
9341  radialVelocityOut = TurboVelocityOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan][2];
9342  }
9343  kineOut = KineOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9344  omegaOut = OmegaOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9345  nuOut = NuOut[iMarkerTP -1][iSpan];
9346 
9347 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
9348  TurbPerfOut[0] = densityOut;
9349  TurbPerfOut[1] = pressureOut;
9350  TurbPerfOut[2] = normalVelocityOut;
9351  TurbPerfOut[3] = tangVelocityOut;
9352  TurbPerfOut[4] = radialVelocityOut;
9353  TurbPerfOut[5] = kineOut;
9354  TurbPerfOut[6] = omegaOut;
9355  TurbPerfOut[7] = nuOut;
9356 #endif
9357  }
9358  }
9359  }
9360  }
9361 
9362 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
9363  if (rank == MASTER_NODE){
9364  TotTurbPerfIn = new su2double[n1t];
9365  TotTurbPerfOut = new su2double[n2t];
9366  for (i=0;i<n1t;i++)
9367  TotTurbPerfIn[i] = -1.0;
9368  for (i=0;i<n2t;i++)
9369  TotTurbPerfOut[i] = -1.0;
9370  TotMarkerTP = new int[size];
9371  for(int i=0; i<size; i++){
9372  TotMarkerTP[i] = -1;
9373  }
9374  }
9375  SU2_MPI::Gather(TurbPerfIn, n1, MPI_DOUBLE, TotTurbPerfIn, n1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
9376  SU2_MPI::Gather(TurbPerfOut, n2, MPI_DOUBLE,TotTurbPerfOut, n2, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
9377  SU2_MPI::Gather(&markerTP, 1, MPI_INT,TotMarkerTP, 1, MPI_INT, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
9378  if (rank == MASTER_NODE){
9379  delete [] TurbPerfIn, delete [] TurbPerfOut;
9380  }
9381 
9382  if (rank == MASTER_NODE){
9383  for (int i=0;i<size;i++){
9384  if(TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i] > 0.0){
9385  densityIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i];
9386  pressureIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i+1];
9387  normalVelocityIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i+2];
9388  tangVelocityIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i+3];
9389  radialVelocityIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i+4];
9390  kineIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i+5];
9391  omegaIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i+6];
9392  nuIn = TotTurbPerfIn[n1*i+7];
9393  markerTP = TotMarkerTP[i];
9394  }
9395 
9396  if(TotTurbPerfOut[n2*i] > 0.0){
9397  densityOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i];
9398  pressureOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i+1];
9399  normalVelocityOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i+2];
9400  tangVelocityOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i+3];
9401  radialVelocityOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i+4];
9402  kineOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i+5];
9403  omegaOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i+6];
9404  nuOut = TotTurbPerfOut[n1*i+7];
9405  }
9406  }
9407 
9408  delete [] TotTurbPerfIn, delete [] TotTurbPerfOut; delete [] TotMarkerTP;
9409  }
9410 
9411 #endif
9412 
9413  if (rank == MASTER_NODE && markerTP > -1){
9414  /*----Quantities needed for computing the turbomachinery performance -----*/
9415  DensityIn[markerTP -1][iSpan] = densityIn;
9416  PressureIn[markerTP -1][iSpan] = pressureIn;
9417  TurboVelocityIn[markerTP -1][iSpan][0] = normalVelocityIn;
9418  TurboVelocityIn[markerTP -1][iSpan][1] = tangVelocityIn;
9419  if (nDim == 3)
9420  TurboVelocityIn[markerTP -1][iSpan][2] = radialVelocityIn;
9421  KineIn[markerTP -1][iSpan] = kineIn;
9422  OmegaIn[markerTP -1][iSpan] = omegaIn;
9423  NuIn[markerTP -1][iSpan] = nuIn;
9424 
9425  DensityOut[markerTP -1][iSpan] = densityOut;
9426  PressureOut[markerTP -1][iSpan] = pressureOut;
9427  TurboVelocityOut[markerTP -1][iSpan][0] = normalVelocityOut;
9428  TurboVelocityOut[markerTP -1][iSpan][1] = tangVelocityOut;
9429  if (nDim == 3)
9430  TurboVelocityOut[markerTP -1][iSpan][2] = radialVelocityOut;
9431  KineOut[markerTP -1][iSpan] = kineOut;
9432  OmegaOut[markerTP -1][iSpan] = omegaOut;
9433  NuOut[markerTP -1][iSpan] = nuOut;
9434  }
9435  }
9436 }
